{"metadata": {"team_id": "attract", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1001", "run_id": "attract-biological"}, "responses": [{"text": "Geoffrey Hinton is known as the \"godfather of AI\" for his work on neural networks.", "citations": {"28a083d6-e397-4b10-96c8-683ddd70ae01_452338678": 1.0}}, {"text": "He invented neural network technology in 2012, significantly contributing to AI development.", "citations": {"d0d53bd7-a835-4e68-9f88-55c12fd01693_296881079": 1.0}}, {"text": "Hinton received the 2018 Turing Award for his influential work on AI development.", "citations": {"d0d53bd7-a835-4e68-9f88-55c12fd01693_296881079": 1.0}}, {"text": "Hinton has expressed concerns that AI may become smarter than humans and pose an existential threat.", "citations": {"3afb956b-40d5-4ecb-8918-2675d6b68006_521301684": 1.0}}, {"text": "He believes AI development is unregulated and risky, potentially leading to catastrophic consequences.", "citations": {"d0d53bd7-a835-4e68-9f88-55c12fd01693_296881079": 1.0}}, {"text": "Hinton's warnings have made headlines, echoing concerns also expressed by Elon Musk and other experts about AI's potential risks.", "citations": {"e1466ebf-84b4-41ed-8497-d39fc984abd1_304858450": 1.0}}, {"text": "The European Parliament has called for a summit to discuss AI control and regulation.", "citations": {"d490c53b-a3c0-4442-9a80-1a11110c988f_899870942": 1.0}}, {"text": "Hinton left Google to speak freely about AI risks without company constraints.", "citations": {"3afb956b-40d5-4ecb-8918-2675d6b68006_779126512": 1.0}}, {"text": "He wants to warn the public about the potential dangers of AI.", "citations": {"3afb956b-40d5-4ecb-8918-2675d6b68006_521301684": 1.0}}, {"text": "Hinton's warnings have sparked a debate about the need for more regulation over AI development.", "citations": {"9f2305a4-5741-4eef-9e53-fd05af571cdf_241409653": 1.0}}, {"text": "The public should be aware that unregulated AI development could have severe societal consequences.", "citations": {"9f2305a4-5741-4eef-9e53-fd05af571cdf_241409653": 1.0}}, {"text": "Experts like Hinton can raise awareness about AI risks by speaking out.", "citations": {"eb2b1c5a-6402-4fc8-98d3-a91481c6902d_20427601": 1.0}}, {"text": "Developing AI requires balancing benefits and risks to prioritize human safety and well-being.", "citations": {"eec5e074-3566-4b62-a2e7-65d0579c4f71_924627484": 1.0}}, {"text": "Hinton's warnings highlight the need for careful AI regulation.", "citations": {"eb2b1c5a-6402-4fc8-98d3-a91481c6902d_20427601": 1.0}}, {"text": "The EU is making progress on its AI law, which requires prior permission for generative AI systems, but more work is needed to address global AI risks.", "citations": {"c8c2554b-88e0-4c10-9e4e-6f1ff6fe565f_458865132": 1.0}}, {"text": "International cooperation is necessary for effective AI regulation due to its global impacts.", "citations": {"ebe7ded0-fa3a-4a28-8aa9-d59753c55c50_954123709": 1.0}}, {"text": "Experts warn that unchecked AI development poses risks due to a lack of global regulatory consensus.", "citations": {"f8ac333a-df70-4537-8689-122137e47402_161850291": 1.0}}, {"text": "Governments and regulators should ensure AI systems are developed and used responsibly by introducing safety protocols and assessing their risks and benefits.", "citations": {"f8ac333a-df70-4537-8689-122137e47402_161850291": 1.0}}, {"text": "Geoffrey Hinton's warnings about AI's dangers highlight the need for a nuanced discussion on its potential consequences and risks.", "citations": {"2dd164a6-0781-4d60-93cd-ed77f5d0419b_204409654": 1.0}}], "references": ["c8c2554b-88e0-4c10-9e4e-6f1ff6fe565f_458865132", "e1466ebf-84b4-41ed-8497-d39fc984abd1_304858450", "3afb956b-40d5-4ecb-8918-2675d6b68006_521301684", "d490c53b-a3c0-4442-9a80-1a11110c988f_899870942", "2dd164a6-0781-4d60-93cd-ed77f5d0419b_204409654", "eec5e074-3566-4b62-a2e7-65d0579c4f71_924627484", "eb2b1c5a-6402-4fc8-98d3-a91481c6902d_20427601", "ebe7ded0-fa3a-4a28-8aa9-d59753c55c50_954123709", "9f2305a4-5741-4eef-9e53-fd05af571cdf_241409653", "f8ac333a-df70-4537-8689-122137e47402_161850291", "d0d53bd7-a835-4e68-9f88-55c12fd01693_296881079", "3afb956b-40d5-4ecb-8918-2675d6b68006_779126512", "28a083d6-e397-4b10-96c8-683ddd70ae01_452338678"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "attract", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1002", "run_id": "attract-biological"}, "responses": [{"text": "Geoffrey Hinton is a pioneer in artificial intelligence, known for his work on neural networks and deep learning.", "citations": {"09887dcf-8df7-4f1e-b60b-875b3d1bd775_245465706": 1.0}}, {"text": "He is known as the \"godfather of AI\" for his work on neural networks.", "citations": {"28a083d6-e397-4b10-96c8-683ddd70ae01_452338678": 1.0}}, {"text": "Hinton warns that AI could surpass human abilities in 5-20 years and potentially lead to human extinction if not carefully managed.", "citations": {"28a083d6-e397-4b10-96c8-683ddd70ae01_452338678": 1.0}}, {"text": "His concerns highlight the need for AI systems to prioritize human values and ethics, with human oversight ensuring safety.", "citations": {"083b97e1-a8d9-4cc5-905d-a6d6e4854e20_272472017": 1.0}}, {"text": "Generative AI requires reliable development to prevent harm to humans.", "citations": {"083b97e1-a8d9-4cc5-905d-a6d6e4854e20_272472017": 1.0}}, {"text": "AI development requires clear responsibility, value alignment, and an accountability system to ensure human values are incorporated.", "citations": {"083b97e1-a8d9-4cc5-905d-a6d6e4854e20_272472017": 1.0}}, {"text": "Experts suggest that independent auditing and human oversight can help reduce AI risks.", "citations": {"14190bf2-5114-4846-bdc2-bca381772686_999456816": 1.0}}, {"text": "The alignment problem arises because current AI systems lack coherent internal models of the world, leading to unintended consequences.", "citations": {"fef386f3-1c37-4c3a-a68a-cc8adf65acec_466597609": 1.0}}, {"text": "Regulation and watermarking of AI-generated content can help prevent harm and distinguish it from reality.", "citations": {"fef386f3-1c37-4c3a-a68a-cc8adf65acec_466597609": 1.0}}, {"text": "Experts warn that AI systems may become superintelligent and exceed human capabilities.", "citations": {"14190bf2-5114-4846-bdc2-bca381772686_999456816": 1.0}}, {"text": "The public should know that AI systems, even without superintelligence, can cause serious harm and generate targeted propaganda.", "citations": {"fef386f3-1c37-4c3a-a68a-cc8adf65acec_466597609": 1.0}}, {"text": "AI development must consider data bias, ethics, and security to prevent defamatory statements about individuals.", "citations": {"083b97e1-a8d9-4cc5-905d-a6d6e4854e20_272472017": 1.0}}, {"text": "Human oversight is necessary for AI decision-making, especially in high-risk areas like medical diagnosis.", "citations": {"0eae6acb-e781-461b-9653-45d775cafe3e_26976493": 1.0}}, {"text": "The \"human in the loop\" and \"Society in the loop\" models include human participation to develop AI with human values.", "citations": {"f7988aaf-2f34-4e93-8c33-82e9656fe894_888603043": 1.0}}, {"text": "The EU prioritizes machine ethics and experts call for safeguards against AI dangers.", "citations": {"bbb85d81-54b7-49e0-89bb-36cc6e6f50f1_1020959450": 1.0}}, {"text": "Diverse training data is necessary for AI development to prevent algorithmic bias.", "citations": {"f7988aaf-2f34-4e93-8c33-82e9656fe894_888603043": 1.0}}, {"text": "Technical safety requires optimization and agile assessment of AI ethical and technical safety.", "citations": {"e889250a-5187-49a1-be02-e527ef961201_560980157": 1.0}}, {"text": "Experts like Geoffrey Hinton warn that AI development requires careful consideration of human values and ethics, as well as human oversight and accountability.", "citations": {"083b97e1-a8d9-4cc5-905d-a6d6e4854e20_272472017": 1.0}}, {"text": "Developing AI that learns from rewards and punishments and avoids harming humans is crucial for AI safety.", "citations": {"4fabbeed-bc7a-47b2-b72e-a771e364cb8a_964093177": 1.0}}, {"text": "Human and machine laws can conflict, and the lack of uniformity in human laws makes AI development challenging.", "citations": {"b54ed508-bcca-4c98-ad80-12ff0f8d6adb_133256521": 1.0}}, {"text": "Experts call for safeguards and aligned AI goals to protect humanity.", "citations": {"bbb85d81-54b7-49e0-89bb-36cc6e6f50f1_1020959450": 1.0}}, {"text": "The UAE government and council promote ethical AI use and develop technical standards, including explainable AI.", "citations": {"bbb85d81-54b7-49e0-89bb-36cc6e6f50f1_1020959450": 1.0}}, {"text": "The National Science Council promotes AI research with human oversight, using \"human in the loop\" and \"Society in the loop\" models.", "citations": {"f7988aaf-2f34-4e93-8c33-82e9656fe894_888603043": 1.0}}, {"text": "The EU prioritizes machine ethics, AI safety, and diverse training data for trustworthy generative AI.", "citations": {"f7988aaf-2f34-4e93-8c33-82e9656fe894_888603043": 1.0}}, {"text": "AI development requires balancing ethics and growth, as current systems can cause harm and spread disinformation even without superintelligence.", "citations": {"fef386f3-1c37-4c3a-a68a-cc8adf65acec_466597609": 1.0}}, {"text": "Regulation and watermarking can help prevent harm from AI-generated fake content.", "citations": {"fef386f3-1c37-4c3a-a68a-cc8adf65acec_466597609": 1.0}}, {"text": "Artificial general intelligence could be the most consequential event in human history, with experts warning it can generate targeted propaganda and false statements.", "citations": {"fef386f3-1c37-4c3a-a68a-cc8adf65acec_466597609": 1.0}}, {"text": "The US government and seven tech giants have agreed to regulate AI development for security and safety.", "citations": {"0a14ae6a-c873-450a-a681-13c26f1ddc99_956540449": 1.0}}, {"text": "Companies will develop watermark systems for AI-generated content.", "citations": {"0a14ae6a-c873-450a-a681-13c26f1ddc99_956540449": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Biden administration has met with tech leaders to discuss AI safety, with companies adhering to \"safety, security, and trust\" principles.", "citations": {"0a14ae6a-c873-450a-a681-13c26f1ddc99_956540449": 1.0}}, {"text": "US regulation lags behind the European Union's AI efforts, which include proposed artificial intelligence bills.", "citations": {"0a14ae6a-c873-450a-a681-13c26f1ddc99_956540449": 1.0}}, {"text": "The US Congress is considering a bill for AI disclosure in political ads, seen as a positive step towards AI regulation.", "citations": {"0a14ae6a-c873-450a-a681-13c26f1ddc99_956540449": 1.0}}, {"text": "OpenAI CEO Sam Altman supports an international AI regulatory agency.", "citations": {"2054b987-da58-422d-847d-4be8eb1e09fb_69548996": 1.0}}, {"text": "The US and China will hold high-level talks on AI regulation, while states like Colorado and Connecticut have introduced related legislation.", "citations": {"2054b987-da58-422d-847d-4be8eb1e09fb_69548996": 1.0}}, {"text": "Connecticut's AI regulation efforts collapsed due to a veto threat from the Governor.", "citations": {"2054b987-da58-422d-847d-4be8eb1e09fb_69548996": 1.0}}, {"text": "The US government has launched AI regulatory policy formulation, with the NTIA holding a 60-day public consultation.", "citations": {"36d44317-3b10-40eb-bf03-aa8e4f8b899e_240528531": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Biden administration and OpenAI support innovation, security, and AI regulation.", "citations": {"36d44317-3b10-40eb-bf03-aa8e4f8b899e_240528531": 1.0}}, {"text": "Seven tech companies have pledged to make AI safer by watermarking AI-generated content and rigorously testing AI systems before release.", "citations": {"3a66cb71-ba4f-44fe-a503-8ab0503e7468_404705472": 1.0}}, {"text": "The UK government will fund a \u00a3100m AI taskforce to ensure AI is free of discrimination and bias.", "citations": {"3a66cb71-ba4f-44fe-a503-8ab0503e7468_404705472": 1.0}}, {"text": "The US government regulates emerging AI tech with companies' help to reduce cybersecurity risks.", "citations": {"3a66cb71-ba4f-44fe-a503-8ab0503e7468_404705472": 1.0}}, {"text": "OpenAI CEO warns US Congress of unsafe AI rules as it seeks consensus on regulation.", "citations": {"65e7f246-fa07-4329-b79b-9c666c9abedf_684361690": 1.0}}, {"text": "AI's impact on elections and jobs is a concern that requires regulatory measures.", "citations": {"65e7f246-fa07-4329-b79b-9c666c9abedf_684361690": 1.0}}, {"text": "AI systems could spread misinformation and excessive concentration of the technology is a concern.", "citations": {"65e7f246-fa07-4329-b79b-9c666c9abedf_684361690": 1.0}}, {"text": "The US and 16 countries have pledged to make AI safe by design, while 18 nations agreed to develop it safely.", "citations": {"6b03628a-c1c2-45d1-b112-3b177ced06ea_590963782": 1.0}}, {"text": "The US and Europe are working to establish AI regulations, with Europe taking the lead.", "citations": {"6b03628a-c1c2-45d1-b112-3b177ced06ea_590963782": 1.0}}, {"text": "President Biden ordered AI companies to conduct regular security tests.", "citations": {"6b03628a-c1c2-45d1-b112-3b177ced06ea_590963782": 1.0}}, {"text": "Research companies must look for vulnerabilities, outlined in a 20-page AI safety agreement.", "citations": {"6b03628a-c1c2-45d1-b112-3b177ced06ea_590963782": 1.0}}, {"text": "The international agreement aims for a safety-first AI development approach to prevent misuse.", "citations": {"6b03628a-c1c2-45d1-b112-3b177ced06ea_590963782": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Biden administration is preparing an executive order for AI safety.", "citations": {"83bbea91-c2df-4082-945e-1368d11f7426_306400091": 1.0}}, {"text": "Congress aims to regulate AI, with companies committing to transparency and security.", "citations": {"83bbea91-c2df-4082-945e-1368d11f7426_306400091": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Senate Majority Leader plans AI legislation, including labeling AI-generated content.", "citations": {"83bbea91-c2df-4082-945e-1368d11f7426_306400091": 1.0}}, {"text": "Companies share best practices and allow third-party vulnerability reporting.", "citations": {"83bbea91-c2df-4082-945e-1368d11f7426_306400091": 1.0}}, {"text": "Microsoft and the White House work with the National Science Foundation and Congress on AI safety and regulation.", "citations": {"83bbea91-c2df-4082-945e-1368d11f7426_306400091": 1.0}}, {"text": "AI funding should prioritize safety and ethics, but broad-based regulations on AI safety are lacking.", "citations": {"8978275e-dacc-4f00-b401-4eaaf0896a14_18205639": 1.0}}, {"text": "The EU's first AI safety law is pending, holding companies liable for AI-related harms.", "citations": {"8978275e-dacc-4f00-b401-4eaaf0896a14_18205639": 1.0}}, {"text": "Top researchers call for increased investment in AI safety due to the power of recent AI models.", "citations": {"8978275e-dacc-4f00-b401-4eaaf0896a14_18205639": 1.0}}, {"text": "AI progress is outpacing precautions, with some companies opposing regulations due to costs.", "citations": {"8978275e-dacc-4f00-b401-4eaaf0896a14_18205639": 1.0}}, {"text": "Regulation does not stifle innovation, with more rules applying to sandwich shops than AI companies.", "citations": {"8978275e-dacc-4f00-b401-4eaaf0896a14_18205639": 1.0}}, {"text": "The US President has ordered companies to share AI safety test results with the government.", "citations": {"b0450267-ba05-439e-b8e6-60a956b8c70e_746468890": 1.0}}, {"text": "AI standards for safety and watermarking guidelines will be developed.", "citations": {"b0450267-ba05-439e-b8e6-60a956b8c70e_746468890": 1.0}}, {"text": "The administration aims to protect privacy and prevent discrimination through international AI frameworks.", "citations": {"b0450267-ba05-439e-b8e6-60a956b8c70e_746468890": 1.0}}, {"text": "The government will build the National AI Research Resource and fund privacy-protecting technology research.", "citations": {"b0450267-ba05-439e-b8e6-60a956b8c70e_746468890": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Department of Justice will compile best practices to prevent AI discrimination.", "citations": {"b0450267-ba05-439e-b8e6-60a956b8c70e_746468890": 1.0}}, {"text": "US lacks legislative action on AI regulation amid varying global efforts.", "citations": {"d4e73003-b32a-4dc9-b362-1f8f14d0e09b_830101714": 1.0}}, {"text": "The EU and UN are working on AI regulations focusing on transparency, security, and accountability.", "citations": {"d4e73003-b32a-4dc9-b362-1f8f14d0e09b_830101714": 1.0}}, {"text": "Japan takes a hands-off approach to AI regulation, and governments must regulate AI to prevent misuse.", "citations": {"d4e73003-b32a-4dc9-b362-1f8f14d0e09b_830101714": 1.0}}, {"text": "Time is running out for governments to regulate AI, which can be used for both cybersecurity and malicious activities.", "citations": {"d4e73003-b32a-4dc9-b362-1f8f14d0e09b_830101714": 1.0}}, {"text": "AI regulation requires guidance on permissible uses and responsible development.", "citations": {"d4e73003-b32a-4dc9-b362-1f8f14d0e09b_830101714": 1.0}}, {"text": "The UK government has announced AI safety commitments from 16 companies, including OpenAI, Google DeepMind, and Anthropic.", "citations": {"d8b508fa-75e1-4edf-8bba-a4b61e992cca_425339": 1.0}}, {"text": "Companies must identify and mitigate AI security risks before the 2025 France AI summit.", "citations": {"d8b508fa-75e1-4edf-8bba-a4b61e992cca_425339": 1.0}}, {"text": "The summit will discuss AI innovation, research, and expansion at universities.", "citations": {"d8b508fa-75e1-4edf-8bba-a4b61e992cca_425339": 1.0}}, {"text": "AI regulation lacks global consensus, requiring flexible government policies.", "citations": {"f8ac333a-df70-4537-8689-122137e47402_161850291": 1.0}}, {"text": "Unchecked AI development can lead to job replacements, and authorities should cover AI risks and benefits.", "citations": {"f8ac333a-df70-4537-8689-122137e47402_161850291": 1.0}}, {"text": "Poor", "citations": {}}], "references": ["0eae6acb-e781-461b-9653-45d775cafe3e_26976493", "d4e73003-b32a-4dc9-b362-1f8f14d0e09b_830101714", "b54ed508-bcca-4c98-ad80-12ff0f8d6adb_133256521", "6b03628a-c1c2-45d1-b112-3b177ced06ea_590963782", "4fabbeed-bc7a-47b2-b72e-a771e364cb8a_964093177", "fef386f3-1c37-4c3a-a68a-cc8adf65acec_466597609", "36d44317-3b10-40eb-bf03-aa8e4f8b899e_240528531", "bbb85d81-54b7-49e0-89bb-36cc6e6f50f1_1020959450", "2054b987-da58-422d-847d-4be8eb1e09fb_69548996", "d8b508fa-75e1-4edf-8bba-a4b61e992cca_425339", "14190bf2-5114-4846-bdc2-bca381772686_999456816", "09887dcf-8df7-4f1e-b60b-875b3d1bd775_245465706", "3a66cb71-ba4f-44fe-a503-8ab0503e7468_404705472", "083b97e1-a8d9-4cc5-905d-a6d6e4854e20_272472017", "83bbea91-c2df-4082-945e-1368d11f7426_306400091", "b0450267-ba05-439e-b8e6-60a956b8c70e_746468890", "65e7f246-fa07-4329-b79b-9c666c9abedf_684361690", "28a083d6-e397-4b10-96c8-683ddd70ae01_452338678", "0a14ae6a-c873-450a-a681-13c26f1ddc99_956540449", "8978275e-dacc-4f00-b401-4eaaf0896a14_18205639", "e889250a-5187-49a1-be02-e527ef961201_560980157", "f8ac333a-df70-4537-8689-122137e47402_161850291", "f7988aaf-2f34-4e93-8c33-82e9656fe894_888603043"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "attract", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1003", "run_id": "attract-biological"}, "responses": [{"text": "The digital nomad lifestyle involves working remotely from anywhere, using a laptop and stable network, to travel and work from various destinations.", "citations": {"f2d39679-7714-4818-8520-3a94256d29a9_256892267": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads, often in IT and software development, work remotely and travel globally, with 35 million worldwide identifying as such.", "citations": {"72836102-23df-4f82-b338-56a356464891_682732748": 1.0}}, {"text": "The digital nomad lifestyle combines work and travel, allowing individuals to experience new cultures while maintaining a career.", "citations": {"72836102-23df-4f82-b338-56a356464891_682732748": 1.0}}, {"text": "Chiang Mai, Bali, and Lisbon are popular digital nomad destinations due to their low costs, good quality of life, and reliable infrastructure.", "citations": {"72836102-23df-4f82-b338-56a356464891_682732748": 1.0}}, {"text": "Countries like Malta, Croatia, and Estonia offer visas to digital nomads, recognizing the benefits of remote work and its potential to innovate the tourism industry.", "citations": {"fd58cfb9-f01b-4078-86a9-871fc3f6410e_322621379": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads use tools like high-speed internet and shared workspaces, and participate in online communities to stay connected and productive.", "citations": {"fd58cfb9-f01b-4078-86a9-871fc3f6410e_322621379": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads face challenges in maintaining relationships and building a community, which can be eased by co-working spaces and social activities.", "citations": {"491e1e95-4ffe-4fe3-b435-06b9fcde7b7e_929014990": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads may face challenges like loneliness and burnout, but can mitigate them by balancing work and leisure.", "citations": {"66a58391-3a62-480f-be64-9b2280bbe834_951964714": 1.0}}, {"text": "A digital nomad visa allows longer stays in countries, costing between $72 and $1000 depending on the country.", "citations": {"72836102-23df-4f82-b338-56a356464891_682732748": 1.0}}, {"text": "Countries like Japan offer digital nomad visas that require private health insurance and a minimum income.", "citations": {"b67b7441-6604-4229-82d6-e410e0419e0b_1051067344": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads can stay for weeks, months, or years, and 50 countries, including Dubai and Iceland, offer specific visas for them.", "citations": {"ea90bb4e-0607-4636-afd5-5e325bcbfef8_77576442": 1.0}}, {"text": "Online teaching, design, and e-commerce are common remote work jobs, and digital nomads use online resources to find affordable accommodations and food, often forming communities with like-minded people.", "citations": {"f2d39679-7714-4818-8520-3a94256d29a9_256892267": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads face challenges like cultural and language barriers, with 63% of Russians feeling shy speaking foreign languages abroad and only 34% speaking English while traveling.", "citations": {"a5ddeca3-9f58-43dc-8605-c9147e6d4bf8_921476251": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads boost local economies and are expected to reach 1 billion by 2035, driven by high-speed internet and freelancing.", "citations": {"ea90bb4e-0607-4636-afd5-5e325bcbfef8_77576442": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads prioritize freedom and openness, bringing creativity and economic growth to the countries they visit.", "citations": {"15e8540b-5ba4-4152-9f0a-a15471c6bcb8_847147219": 1.0}}], "references": ["66a58391-3a62-480f-be64-9b2280bbe834_951964714", "72836102-23df-4f82-b338-56a356464891_682732748", "15e8540b-5ba4-4152-9f0a-a15471c6bcb8_847147219", "491e1e95-4ffe-4fe3-b435-06b9fcde7b7e_929014990", "b67b7441-6604-4229-82d6-e410e0419e0b_1051067344", "ea90bb4e-0607-4636-afd5-5e325bcbfef8_77576442", "fd58cfb9-f01b-4078-86a9-871fc3f6410e_322621379", "f2d39679-7714-4818-8520-3a94256d29a9_256892267", "a5ddeca3-9f58-43dc-8605-c9147e6d4bf8_921476251"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "attract", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1004", "run_id": "attract-biological"}, "responses": [{"text": "About 35 million people worldwide identify as digital nomads, working remotely while traveling and exploring new destinations.", "citations": {"72836102-23df-4f82-b338-56a356464891_682732748": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads can work in fields like programming, writing, and designing, with over 40 countries offering visas that may include tax exemptions.", "citations": {"f2d39679-7714-4818-8520-3a94256d29a9_262065431": 1.0}}, {"text": "Japan requires a minimum annual income of over 10 million yen and private health insurance for a digital nomad visa.", "citations": {"15e8540b-5ba4-4152-9f0a-a15471c6bcb8_847147219": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads must carefully manage their finances and often use multi-currency debit cards to avoid fees.", "citations": {"a3c70681-f2b9-494d-bb98-7de9c98f52da_736721641": 1.0}}, {"text": "They must research local prices, costs, and tax requirements, which may include proof of income or work experience.", "citations": {"a3c70681-f2b9-494d-bb98-7de9c98f52da_736721641": 1.0, "db019ab6-b296-4293-83c7-9abde9a9b8e0_856576344": 0.5}}, {"text": "Digital nomads typically need international health insurance, although some countries like Malta and Taiwan have well-established healthcare systems for expatriates.", "citations": {"db019ab6-b296-4293-83c7-9abde9a9b8e0_856576344": 1.0}}, {"text": "The OECD is developing tax amendments for digital nomads and reviewing global tax rules for remote employment.", "citations": {"87e78f2b-1ff8-47de-bab1-77eb4ca73e80_332625905": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads may face tax issues in multiple countries based on the number of days they stay.", "citations": {"f2d39679-7714-4818-8520-3a94256d29a9_262065431": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads can use budgeting apps and a \"base camp\" to manage their finances and provide stability.", "citations": {"a3c70681-f2b9-494d-bb98-7de9c98f52da_736721641": 1.0}}, {"text": "Countries like Germany and Norway offer visas for remote workers, ranging from two to three years.", "citations": {"db019ab6-b296-4293-83c7-9abde9a9b8e0_856576344": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads can utilize over 26,000 coworking spaces and online communities by 2025 to share tips and experiences.", "citations": {"72836102-23df-4f82-b338-56a356464891_682732748": 1.0}}, {"text": "Russian IT specialists abroad are taxed at 13-15% regardless of tax residency.", "citations": {"22007e11-e905-4961-a00b-afd858aa8348_945646981": 1.0}}, {"text": "Russia has a uniform tax rate for IT specialists abroad to prevent employee outflow.", "citations": {"22007e11-e905-4961-a00b-afd858aa8348_945646981": 1.0}}, {"text": "Russian non-residents are taxed at 30%, except for IT specialists working abroad, who are taxed at 13-15%.", "citations": {"22007e11-e905-4961-a00b-afd858aa8348_945646981": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Ministry of Finance proposes a single tax rate for residents and non-residents to simplify tax obligations for Russian IT specialists abroad.", "citations": {"2a5fa946-d348-4a44-b8af-bae47890dd30_595670943": 1.0}}, {"text": "Russian IT specialists abroad may lose tax resident status but can still use a single tax rate.", "citations": {"2a5fa946-d348-4a44-b8af-bae47890dd30_595670943": 1.0}}, {"text": "Russian IT specialists abroad can minimize tax liabilities using employer-paid insurance premiums, which are nearly halved for them.", "citations": {"0b66dd45-6a86-465c-9419-f8f71d442682_941024495": 1.0}}, {"text": "Russian IT companies with 90% of income from software sales qualify for a 3% income tax rate.", "citations": {"0b66dd45-6a86-465c-9419-f8f71d442682_941024495": 1.0}}, {"text": "Russian IT specialists abroad can benefit from tax strategies like claiming work-related expense deductions.", "citations": {"2ec94e79-be7d-4bbd-bbda-d553fb44e0b0_711412342": 1.0}}, {"text": "Russia has drafted a tax law to address remote worker taxation and prevent labor and tax losses.", "citations": {"2a5fa946-d348-4a44-b8af-bae47890dd30_595670943": 1.0}}, {"text": "Foreign companies must register and pay a 13% or 15% tax rate for Russian employees.", "citations": {"2ec94e79-be7d-4bbd-bbda-d553fb44e0b0_711412342": 1.0}}, {"text": "Russian IT specialists abroad may face increased taxes and canceled benefits due to new legislation.", "citations": {"45171739-fa19-4c9c-b960-c8821a65e515_540909178": 1.0}}, {"text": "Russia proposes a 30% tax on income for expats working abroad online.", "citations": {"847086b9-159b-44fe-ba81-bc2142ed1f52_37638786": 1.0}}, {"text": "Russian IT specialists abroad can benefit from a 13-15% tax rate if considered tax residents.", "citations": {"847086b9-159b-44fe-ba81-bc2142ed1f52_37638786": 1.0}}, {"text": "Employers must tax foreign income payments and Russian bank account holders are subject to the new rules.", "citations": {"847086b9-159b-44fe-ba81-bc2142ed1f52_37638786": 1.0}}, {"text": "Russian citizens abroad must pay taxes in Russia on income from Russian sources.", "citations": {"8d4e0568-da7f-48a1-9538-f65d6b4a2bf8_679684297": 1.0}}, {"text": "Remote employees and students under 24 may be eligible for tax-free compensation or deductions on equipment and materials.", "citations": {"afc80be8-c7ce-4266-99f6-fcc74c860e3c_493958532": 1.0}}, {"text": "Taxpayers can claim deductions for caring for dependents and acquiring property rights.", "citations": {"afc80be8-c7ce-4266-99f6-fcc74c860e3c_493958532": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads can protect their data while working remotely by using a VPN.", "citations": {"10d650ff-df9d-4ba7-9210-c2feb74e46a9_760698826": 1.0}}, {"text": "A VPN creates a secure connection, providing an extra layer of privacy by making web traffic and IP addresses untrackable.", "citations": {"10d650ff-df9d-4ba7-9210-c2feb74e46a9_760698826": 1.0}}, {"text": "NordVPN, Surfshark, and ExpressVPN are recommended paid VPNs, while TunnelBear and NewNode VPN are recommended for free.", "citations": {"10d650ff-df9d-4ba7-9210-c2feb74e46a9_760698826": 1.0}}, {"text": "Secure messengers like Signal, WhatsApp, and Threema offer end-to-end encryption for private communication.", "citations": {"10d650ff-df9d-4ba7-9210-c2feb74e46a9_760698826": 1.0}}, {"text": "Using a VPN, secure messenger, and two-factor authentication, and regularly cleaning internet history, provides strong online security.", "citations": {"10d650ff-df9d-4ba7-9210-c2feb74e46a9_760698826": 1.0}}, {"text": "Storing documents on cloud services or hidden albums protects personal data.", "citations": {"10d650ff-df9d-4ba7-9210-c2feb74e46a9_760698826": 1.0}}, {"text": "Antivirus software is essential for digital nomads, protecting computers from cyber threats and online scams.", "citations": {"1cb6441c-71a8-4fd8-b960-f32890823c19_881333352": 1.0}}, {"text": "Paid antivirus programs offer more features and better protection than free versions.", "citations": {"1cb6441c-71a8-4fd8-b960-f32890823c19_881333352": 1.0}}, {"text": "Top-rated free antiviruses like AVG offer excellent protection against spyware and additional features.", "citations": {"1cb6441c-71a8-4fd8-b960-f32890823c19_881333352": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads should consider factors like servers, support, and payment options, such as PrivateVPN's Bitcoin option, when choosing a VPN.", "citations": {"2d12ece9-e12d-4faa-ba31-47fa17c5b80c_786304033": 1.0}}, {"text": "NordVPN offers the most servers and best support, while Surfshark provides quality features, including a Kill Switch, at a lower cost.", "citations": {"2d12ece9-e12d-4faa-ba31-47fa17c5b80c_786304033": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads should use strong, unique passwords and enable Two-Factor Authentication.", "citations": {"81ba302b-84e8-4d83-a3a3-4a344f7cbc87_801082282": 1.0}}, {"text": "Regular updates and unique passwords can help fix security vulnerabilities and prevent hackers from accessing all accounts.", "citations": {"81ba302b-84e8-4d83-a3a3-4a344f7cbc87_801082282": 1.0}}, {"text": "Reputable VPNs use AES256-bit encryption and have strict privacy policies.", "citations": {"a21fdae9-9d94-4023-8e85-c0d6ab6224a4_637726365": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads should choose a reputable VPN provider to avoid spyware and malware risks.", "citations": {"a21fdae9-9d94-4023-8e85-c0d6ab6224a4_637726365": 1.0}}, {"text": "Password managers and two-factor authentication add layers of security.", "citations": {"bcb294d1-7e5e-4b7d-873d-31e0c4fe1d9c_475880104": 1.0}}, {"text": "Antivirus software and unique passwords can prevent malware and cyberattacks.", "citations": {"bcb294d1-7e5e-4b7d-873d-31e0c4fe1d9c_475880104": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads should be cautious of public Wi-Fi risks and take protective steps, like verifying network names before connecting.", "citations": {"c5d75a84-d3a1-42ee-8060-9f572c2be0e4_717708439": 1.0}}, {"text": "Using a VPN provides an additional layer of security on public Wi-Fi.", "citations": {"c5d75a84-d3a1-42ee-8060-9f572c2be0e4_717708439": 1.0}}, {"text": "Firewalls and disabling file sharing on public Wi-Fi can help prevent hacking.", "citations": {"c5d75a84-d3a1-42ee-8060-9f572c2be0e4_717708439": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads should keep devices and antivirus software up to date and use parental controls.", "citations": {"de4192c3-e37b-4a03-b5d2-9fe5b752ae6c_855154138": 1.0}}, {"text": "Using password managers and regularly updating operating systems can help ensure cybersecurity.", "citations": {"de4192c3-e37b-4a03-b5d2-9fe5b752ae6c_855154138": 1.0}}, {"text": "The digital nomad lifestyle offers benefits like remote work and cultural experiences, but also challenges such as visa applications and financial transactions.", "citations": {"4c776202-438e-4b1b-add0-4396b5ada53c_356645195": 1.0, "7f832a88-280e-43d5-a515-01b65d5e428d_744015473": 0.5, "c26c56ae-0c40-4365-b72f-de4c435ebb25_984797946": 0.25}}, {"text": "Russian IT specialists can move to visa-free countries like Mexico and those in South America, where they can easily extend their stay.", "citations": {"cf58e6c6-c3e8-485d-b30a-70689cba1777_149442504": 1.0}}, {"text": "The search results lack comprehensive information on the digital nomad lifestyle.", "citations": {"72836102-23df-4f82-b338-56a356464891_682732748": 1.0}}, {"text": "The digital nomad lifestyle presents challenges like managing finances, taxes, and health insurance abroad.", "citations": {"1d9ff01a-de89-46ae-9206-79abab310bb7_1042542274": 1.0}}, {"text": "Japan offers digital nomad visas requiring private health insurance and a minimum annual income of 10 million yen.", "citations": {"15e8540b-5ba4-4152-9f0a-a15471c6bcb8_847147219": 1.0}}, {"text": "Costa Rica only taxes domestic income, making it attractive to digital nomads.", "citations": {"1d9ff01a-de89-46ae-9206-79abab310bb7_1042542274": 1.0}}, {"text": "Portugal's Golden Visa no longer includes real estate, while Spain offers digital nomad and entrepreneur visas.", "citations": {"1d9ff01a-de89-46ae-9206-79abab310bb7_1042542274": 1.0}}, {"text": "US citizens can easily obtain Germany's freelancer visa, while the Netherlands offers a 30% tax ruling for highly skilled workers.", "citations": {"1d9ff01a-de89-46ae-9206-79abab310bb7_1042542274": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads can manage their finances using multi-currency debit cards and researching local prices.", "citations": {"a3c70681-f2b9-494d-bb98-7de9c98f52da_736721641": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tax requirements vary by country, and digital nomads may be eligible for relief or exemption with digital nomad visas.", "citations": {"a3c70681-f2b9-494d-bb98-7de9c98f52da_736721641": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads often need international health insurance, and countries like Malta and Taiwan offer well-established healthcare systems.", "citations": {"db019ab6-b296-4293-83c7-9abde9a9b8e0_856576344": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomad visa applicants may need proof of income and can extend their visas up to five years in some countries.", "citations": {"db019ab6-b296-4293-83c7-9abde9a9b8e0_856576344": 1.0}}, {"text": "US citizens abroad face complex tax systems, high fees, and limited Medicare benefits.", "citations": {"ee4105d4-87c6-4131-aed9-9bd7449da497_288520891": 1.0}}, {"text": "Over 40 countries offer digital nomad visas with tax exemptions to mitigate multi-jurisdictional taxation.", "citations": {"f2d39679-7714-4818-8520-3a94256d29a9_262065431": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Comprehensive Avoidance of Double Taxation Agreement helps avoid double taxation, but digital nomads on tourist visas may need visa runs.", "citations": {"f2d39679-7714-4818-8520-3a94256d29a9_262065431": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomad visa applications require income and consider days stayed for tax residency.", "citations": {"f2d39679-7714-4818-8520-3a94256d29a9_262065431": 1.0}}, {"text": "The OECD plans to complete a tax rule review for digital nomads by the end of 2023.", "citations": {}}], "references": ["c26c56ae-0c40-4365-b72f-de4c435ebb25_984797946", "72836102-23df-4f82-b338-56a356464891_682732748", "4c776202-438e-4b1b-add0-4396b5ada53c_356645195", "2ec94e79-be7d-4bbd-bbda-d553fb44e0b0_711412342", "f2d39679-7714-4818-8520-3a94256d29a9_262065431", "15e8540b-5ba4-4152-9f0a-a15471c6bcb8_847147219", "0b66dd45-6a86-465c-9419-f8f71d442682_941024495", "ee4105d4-87c6-4131-aed9-9bd7449da497_288520891", "7f832a88-280e-43d5-a515-01b65d5e428d_744015473", "a3c70681-f2b9-494d-bb98-7de9c98f52da_736721641", "2d12ece9-e12d-4faa-ba31-47fa17c5b80c_786304033", "847086b9-159b-44fe-ba81-bc2142ed1f52_37638786", "1d9ff01a-de89-46ae-9206-79abab310bb7_1042542274", "45171739-fa19-4c9c-b960-c8821a65e515_540909178", "8d4e0568-da7f-48a1-9538-f65d6b4a2bf8_679684297", "a21fdae9-9d94-4023-8e85-c0d6ab6224a4_637726365", "22007e11-e905-4961-a00b-afd858aa8348_945646981", "81ba302b-84e8-4d83-a3a3-4a344f7cbc87_801082282", "87e78f2b-1ff8-47de-bab1-77eb4ca73e80_332625905", "c5d75a84-d3a1-42ee-8060-9f572c2be0e4_717708439", "db019ab6-b296-4293-83c7-9abde9a9b8e0_856576344", "de4192c3-e37b-4a03-b5d2-9fe5b752ae6c_855154138", "bcb294d1-7e5e-4b7d-873d-31e0c4fe1d9c_475880104", "cf58e6c6-c3e8-485d-b30a-70689cba1777_149442504", "afc80be8-c7ce-4266-99f6-fcc74c860e3c_493958532", "10d650ff-df9d-4ba7-9210-c2feb74e46a9_760698826", "2a5fa946-d348-4a44-b8af-bae47890dd30_595670943", "1cb6441c-71a8-4fd8-b960-f32890823c19_881333352"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "attract", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1005", "run_id": "attract-biological"}, "responses": [{"text": "The digital nomad lifestyle, which involves traveling and working remotely, is a growing trend supported by visas in many countries.", "citations": {"088e0346-91bf-43fd-b68c-748ae1e1247f_998032520": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads have high income and freedom, working remotely and traveling worldwide, with 35 million people expected to join this lifestyle by 2022.", "citations": {"495a3813-6b54-48f9-a9d3-18b74a1a72df_561526741": 1.0}}, {"text": "They include professionals who break free from traditional offices, enjoying flexibility and multicultural experiences.", "citations": {"495a3813-6b54-48f9-a9d3-18b74a1a72df_561526741": 1.0}}, {"text": "50 countries offer special visas for digital nomads, allowing longer stays than tourists.", "citations": {"ea90bb4e-0607-4636-afd5-5e325bcbfef8_77576442": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads face challenges like sleep deprivation and stress, requiring emotional flexibility and preparedness.", "citations": {"66a58391-3a62-480f-be64-9b2280bbe834_951964714": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomadism requires flexibility to avoid burnout, and offers benefits like community support, self-awareness, and personal growth.", "citations": {"66a58391-3a62-480f-be64-9b2280bbe834_951964714": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads can work remotely from anywhere with internet, with 16.9 million in the US and access to a growing number of coworking spaces.", "citations": {"72836102-23df-4f82-b338-56a356464891_682732748": 1.0}}, {"text": "Unpredictable expenses can range from $600 to $3,000 per month, but having a base camp and a multi-currency debit card can provide stability and save on fees.", "citations": {"a3c70681-f2b9-494d-bb98-7de9c98f52da_736721641": 1.0}}, {"text": "Financial proficiency, including understanding tax requirements and utilizing digital nomad visas, is key to maintaining a digital nomad lifestyle.", "citations": {"a3c70681-f2b9-494d-bb98-7de9c98f52da_736721641": 1.0}}, {"text": "Remote desktop software and tools help digital nomads overcome connectivity issues and increase productivity by providing secure file access and reducing data loss risk.", "citations": {"b67cd69f-4c83-4193-99ab-2cc0767b6bfd_37536649": 1.0}}, {"text": "Estonia, Malta, Bahamas, Cyprus, and Thailand offer digital nomad visas with varying requirements.", "citations": {"088e0346-91bf-43fd-b68c-748ae1e1247f_998032520": 1.0}}, {"text": "Japan's digital nomad visa requires a $68,300 income and excludes Russians, allowing 6-month remote work stays.", "citations": {"0be60a3e-b6c5-4420-9ef2-c97b0bd0919f_600996491": 1.0}}, {"text": "South Korea offers digital nomad visas requiring a $66,000 income and private health insurance.", "citations": {"0be60a3e-b6c5-4420-9ef2-c97b0bd0919f_600996491": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomadism suits jobs like programming, design, writing, law, and translation.", "citations": {"72836102-23df-4f82-b338-56a356464891_682732748": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads often engage in freelancing, online teaching, design, e-commerce, and programming.", "citations": {"f2d39679-7714-4818-8520-3a94256d29a9_256892267": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads need tools like laptops, noise-canceling headphones, and mobile hotspots to work efficiently.", "citations": {"4acd88c5-7d2b-4157-a17b-8edb9d9769ad_4928390": 1.0}}, {"text": "Citizen Remote assists digital nomads with visa applications, rentals, and global health insurance.", "citations": {"23980c8b-8970-4b9b-96ce-6f690a62ec45_787468909": 1.0}}], "references": ["ea90bb4e-0607-4636-afd5-5e325bcbfef8_77576442", "0be60a3e-b6c5-4420-9ef2-c97b0bd0919f_600996491", "23980c8b-8970-4b9b-96ce-6f690a62ec45_787468909", "72836102-23df-4f82-b338-56a356464891_682732748", "a3c70681-f2b9-494d-bb98-7de9c98f52da_736721641", "f2d39679-7714-4818-8520-3a94256d29a9_256892267", "088e0346-91bf-43fd-b68c-748ae1e1247f_998032520", "66a58391-3a62-480f-be64-9b2280bbe834_951964714", "4acd88c5-7d2b-4157-a17b-8edb9d9769ad_4928390", "495a3813-6b54-48f9-a9d3-18b74a1a72df_561526741", "b67cd69f-4c83-4193-99ab-2cc0767b6bfd_37536649"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "attract", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1006", "run_id": "attract-biological"}, "responses": [{"text": "The digital nomad lifestyle is a trend where people travel while working from laptops, and many countries are now offering digital nomad visas to support this lifestyle.", "citations": {"088e0346-91bf-43fd-b68c-748ae1e1247f_998032520": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads are individuals who work remotely and travel worldwide, often as programmers, writers, or designers, with 22 million Americans and 35 million people worldwide identifying as digital nomads.", "citations": {"72836102-23df-4f82-b338-56a356464891_682732748": 1.0}}, {"text": "The digital nomad lifestyle involves traveling while working remotely, with approximately 35 million digital nomads existing worldwide, spending $787 billion annually.", "citations": {"09cbaa0c-5e42-4814-a1a1-3e28d939b1c4_202321090": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads typically stay in one place for 3-6 months, with around 66% of them following this pattern.", "citations": {"09cbaa0c-5e42-4814-a1a1-3e28d939b1c4_202321090": 1.0}}, {"text": "Japan has introduced a digital nomad visa program to attract remote workers and promote domestic consumption, targeting highly skilled workers with an annual income of over 10 million yen.", "citations": {"15e8540b-5ba4-4152-9f0a-a15471c6bcb8_847147219": 1.0}}, {"text": "The visa program allows digital nomads to stay in Japan for up to six months and travel around the country for sightseeing while working remotely.", "citations": {"15e8540b-5ba4-4152-9f0a-a15471c6bcb8_847147219": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads can bring new creativity to local economies and help economic growth, as seen in Japan's efforts to attract overseas workers.", "citations": {"15e8540b-5ba4-4152-9f0a-a15471c6bcb8_847147219": 1.0}}, {"text": "However, the influx of digital nomads can also lead to gentrification and housing crises, as experienced in Mexico City, where housing costs have risen due to remote workers displacing residents and upending neighborhoods.", "citations": {"1e4c4e41-d986-4b7c-b8df-e1411563cf34_117973992": 1.0}}, {"text": "The average monthly rents in Mexico City have jumped from $880 to $1,080 between January 2020 and November, making it unaffordable for locals.", "citations": {"1e4c4e41-d986-4b7c-b8df-e1411563cf34_117973992": 1.0}}, {"text": "Airbnb stays booked for longer than a month have increased by 30% between April and June, contributing to the rising housing rates.", "citations": {"1e4c4e41-d986-4b7c-b8df-e1411563cf34_117973992": 1.0}}, {"text": "Remote workers have contributed to the rising housing rates, according to a mayoral adviser, and housing activists have accused city leaders of spurring gentrification and pricing out Mexicans.", "citations": {"1e4c4e41-d986-4b7c-b8df-e1411563cf34_117973992": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads can also bring benefits to local economies, such as boosting tourism and encouraging infrastructure development, as seen in Croatia, where digital nomads bring \u20ac6,500 monthly income.", "citations": {"c529ac8d-80af-410a-a327-3546b54a14c8_242137462": 1.0}}, {"text": "Croatia has introduced a digital nomad visa, and other countries like South Korea, Brazil, and Indonesia have also implemented similar visa programs to attract digital nomads.", "citations": {"45215aed-649b-4e8b-8378-232300408e0a_554827344": 1.0, "d812d020-b4d6-4b3b-a420-9f195bdf4ac4_35559448": 0.5, "ea90bb4e-0607-4636-afd5-5e325bcbfef8_77576442": 0.25}}, {"text": "Digital nomads can increase housing costs for locals, but they can also boost local economies with foreign funds and encourage intellectual exchange, spurring local entrepreneurship.", "citations": {"c7b767c9-09fd-43c7-83f7-b07f61e38ae6_818229618": 1.0}}, {"text": "Volunteering and socializing can help digital nomads integrate with locals and reduce resentment from local communities.", "citations": {"c7b767c9-09fd-43c7-83f7-b07f61e38ae6_818229618": 1.0}}, {"text": "However, digital nomads can also strain local communities and displace local jobs indirectly, highlighting the need for careful management of digital nomadism.", "citations": {"c7b767c9-09fd-43c7-83f7-b07f61e38ae6_818229618": 1.0, "ea90bb4e-0607-4636-afd5-5e325bcbfef8_77576442": 0.5}}, {"text": "Special visas are offered to digital nomads worldwide, with countries like Malta, Croatia, Ecuador, and Belize issuing visas to attract them.", "citations": {"fd58cfb9-f01b-4078-86a9-871fc3f6410e_322621379": 1.0}}, {"text": "The digital nomad lifestyle is suited for various types of work, including software engineering, content creation, and trade, with many digital nomads earning between \u20ac3,000 and \u20ac5,000 monthly.", "citations": {"495a3813-6b54-48f9-a9d3-18b74a1a72df_561526741": 1.0, "d812d020-b4d6-4b3b-a420-9f195bdf4ac4_35559448": 0.5}}, {"text": "Digital nomads often rely on remote work tools and infrastructure, such as coworking and coliving spaces, with 26,000 coworking spaces predicted by 2025.", "citations": {"72836102-23df-4f82-b338-56a356464891_682732748": 1.0}}, {"text": "Popular locations for digital nomads include Chiang Mai, Bali, and Lisbon, due to favorable climates and low costs.", "citations": {"72836102-23df-4f82-b338-56a356464891_682732748": 1.0}}, {"text": "The philosophy of digital nomadism emphasizes individualism, freedom, and openness, with values like anti-materialism, and digital nomads can face challenges such as balancing personal freedom and civic responsibility.", "citations": {"72836102-23df-4f82-b338-56a356464891_682732748": 1.0}}, {"text": "Governments may struggle with digital nomadism, as it can impact domestic economies and social infrastructure, highlighting the need for careful consideration of digital nomad visa programs.", "citations": {"72836102-23df-4f82-b338-56a356464891_682732748": 1.0, "ea90bb4e-0607-4636-afd5-5e325bcbfef8_77576442": 0.5}}, {"text": "Overall, digital nomadism presents both opportunities and challenges for local communities and economies, and its impact will depend on how it is managed and regulated.", "citations": {"ea90bb4e-0607-4636-afd5-5e325bcbfef8_77576442": 1.0, "fd58cfb9-f01b-4078-86a9-871fc3f6410e_322621379": 0.5}}, {"text": "Digital nomads use various project management tools to facilitate team collaboration and communication, with ClickUp being a popular choice that replaces tasks, documents, and chats.", "citations": {"07cf246f-1952-45a1-8031-4d4ba74b540a_121181923": 1.0}}, {"text": "ClickUp is a project management tool that facilitates team collaboration and communication.", "citations": {"14b4fea7-1be0-4a7c-beba-00550afcd896_10977012": 1.0}}, {"text": "Trello is another popular project management tool used by digital nomads for team collaboration.", "citations": {"2d43eb04-5d8b-4a30-bed0-4156dde6a2bd_586353010": 1.0}}, {"text": "Asana is a popular project management tool used globally, and it has a feature called Goals that helps teams set and manage objectives.", "citations": {"341d6515-cf02-4680-ad1a-22038e25b86a_699594729": 1.0}}, {"text": "MeisterTask is a collaboration and task management tool used by digital nomads.", "citations": {"6e880013-b616-4fdf-b1a7-1402fbb4d69e_40305401": 1.0}}, {"text": "Miro is an online collaborative whiteboard platform for distributed teams, including digital nomads.", "citations": {"07cf246f-1952-45a1-8031-4d4ba74b540a_121181923": 1.0}}, {"text": "Google Meet is a video-conferencing app used by digital nomads for remote meetings.", "citations": {"2d43eb04-5d8b-4a30-bed0-4156dde6a2bd_586353010": 1.0}}, {"text": "Zoom is a video conferencing app used by digital nomads for team communication.", "citations": {"59724541-c800-4b93-8655-97a4c778640f_938844996": 1.0}}, {"text": "Slack is a communication and collaboration platform used by digital nomads.", "citations": {"59724541-c800-4b93-8655-97a4c778640f_938844996": 1.0}}, {"text": "Microsoft Teams facilitates file sharing and collaboration among digital nomads.", "citations": {"59724541-c800-4b93-8655-97a4c778640f_938844996": 1.0}}, {"text": "Notion is a project management and document management platform used by digital nomads.", "citations": {"c4f9ce00-bbf9-49d0-affd-ee93f10c14f0_357802443": 1.0}}, {"text": "Trello has a simple-to-use interface with kanban boards and timelines, making it a popular choice among digital nomads.", "citations": {"c4f9ce00-bbf9-49d0-affd-ee93f10c14f0_357802443": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads also use tools like Lucid, MURAL, and Gliffy for visual collaboration and charting.", "citations": {"07cf246f-1952-45a1-8031-4d4ba74b540a_121181923": 1.0}}, {"text": "Fibery is a flexible workspace that connects company processes without code, used by some digital nomads.", "citations": {"07cf246f-1952-45a1-8031-4d4ba74b540a_121181923": 1.0}}, {"text": "Padlet is a digital canvas used by digital nomads for creating and collaborating on projects.", "citations": {"07cf246f-1952-45a1-8031-4d4ba74b540a_121181923": 1.0}}, {"text": "Creately is a visual workspace software used by digital nomads for collaborative brainstorming and planning.", "citations": {"07cf246f-1952-45a1-8031-4d4ba74b540a_121181923": 1.0}}, {"text": "Webex is a scalable webinar platform used by digital nomads for creating engaging and interactive experiences.", "citations": {"07cf246f-1952-45a1-8031-4d4ba74b540a_121181923": 1.0}}, {"text": "TeamGantt is a Gantt chart maker used by digital nomads for creating online charts in minutes.", "citations": {"14b4fea7-1be0-4a7c-beba-00550afcd896_10977012": 1.0}}, {"text": "Wrike provides complete visibility and control over tasks and projects for digital nomads.", "citations": {"14b4fea7-1be0-4a7c-beba-00550afcd896_10977012": 1.0}}, {"text": "Teamwork offers project management software with help desk, chat, and document management for digital nomads.", "citations": {"14b4fea7-1be0-4a7c-beba-00550afcd896_10977012": 1.0}}, {"text": "GanttPRO is an online Gantt chart software used by digital nomads for planning and managing tasks.", "citations": {"14b4fea7-1be0-4a7c-beba-00550afcd896_10977012": 1.0}}, {"text": "Hive is a productivity platform used by digital nomads for managing projects and tracking tasks.", "citations": {"14b4fea7-1be0-4a7c-beba-00550afcd896_10977012": 1.0}}, {"text": "Lytho provides workflow management for marketing and design teams of digital nomads.", "citations": {"14b4fea7-1be0-4a7c-beba-00550afcd896_10977012": 1.0}}, {"text": "Planful is a cloud FP&A platform used by digital nomads for continuous planning.", "citations": {"14b4fea7-1be0-4a7c-beba-00550afcd896_10977012": 1.0}}, {"text": "SproutLoud offers channel marketing automation for distributed marketing needs of digital nomads.", "citations": {"14b4fea7-1be0-4a7c-beba-00550afcd896_10977012": 1.0}}, {"text": "Canva is a designing platform used by digital nomads for creating graphics and videos.", "citations": {"2d43eb04-5d8b-4a30-bed0-4156dde6a2bd_586353010": 1.0}}, {"text": "Dropbox is a cloud-based file-sharing system used by digital nomads for team coordination.", "citations": {"2d43eb04-5d8b-4a30-bed0-4156dde6a2bd_586353010": 1.0}}, {"text": "Salesforce is a customer relationship management app used by some digital nomads.", "citations": {"2d43eb04-5d8b-4a30-bed0-4156dde6a2bd_586353010": 1.0}}, {"text": "JIRA is a robust management tool used by digital nomads in agile development environments.", "citations": {"2d43eb04-5d8b-4a30-bed0-4156dde6a2bd_586353010": 1.0}}, {"text": "Zendesk is a tool used by digital nomads for optimizing customer support team collaboration.", "citations": {"2d43eb04-5d8b-4a30-bed0-4156dde6a2bd_586353010": 1.0}}, {"text": "Datapine is a data organization tool used by enterprises of digital nomads.", "citations": {"2d43eb04-5d8b-4a30-bed0-4156dde6a2bd_586353010": 1.0}}, {"text": "Excalidraw is a virtual whiteboard collaboration tool used by digital nomads.", "citations": {"b4568a97-2125-422d-b744-7ceb6ce8de83_308632223": 1.0}}, {"text": "Diagrams.net is an open source charting software used by digital nomads.", "citations": {"b4568a97-2125-422d-b744-7ceb6ce8de83_308632223": 1.0}}, {"text": "Cacoo is an online chart software with over 2.5 million users, including digital nomads.", "citations": {"b4568a97-2125-422d-b744-7ceb6ce8de83_308632223": 1.0}}, {"text": "Samepage is a real-time collaboration platform used by digital nomads.", "citations": {"b4568a97-2125-422d-b744-7ceb6ce8de83_308632223": 1.0}}, {"text": "Overflow is a user-flow charting tool used by product development teams of digital nomads.", "citations": {"b4568a97-2125-422d-b744-7ceb6ce8de83_308632223": 1.0}}, {"text": "Snagit is a team management tool used by digital nomads for screen videos and recordings.", "citations": {"b6583863-0f88-476a-9f78-57b143ae24bd_50003737": 1.0}}, {"text": "Google Agenda is a shared calendar used by digital nomads for team management.", "citations": {"b6583863-0f88-476a-9f78-57b143ae24bd_50003737": 1.0}}, {"text": "ClickUp integrates with other tools like Google Drive and Slack, making it a popular choice among digital nomads.", "citations": {"b6583863-0f88-476a-9f78-57b143ae24bd_50003737": 1.0}}, {"text": "Notion integrates with Slack, Jira, GitHub, and Asana, making it a versatile tool for digital nomads.", "citations": {"c4f9ce00-bbf9-49d0-affd-ee93f10c14f0_357802443": 1.0}}, {"text": "Trello has numerous third-party integrations, making it a popular choice among digital nomads.", "citations": {"c4f9ce00-bbf9-49d0-affd-ee93f10c14f0_357802443": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads use various time tracking and productivity software to manage their work and stay focused while traveling, including Todoist Time Tracking by Everhour, which offers free options for tracking time and integrates with the Everhour browser extension.", "citations": {"0bcc3cd5-42e6-4327-9e7f-cc72b91d6d43_187602728": 1.0}}, {"text": "Todoist Time Tracking also extends Todoist with valuable features for productivity and allows manual time logging and timer tracking.", "citations": {"0bcc3cd5-42e6-4327-9e7f-cc72b91d6d43_187602728": 1.0}}, {"text": "Toggl is another popular tool that tracks work time and generates performance reports, and it assigns colored categories to tasks for organization.", "citations": {"1139a92e-09f2-4972-8ff3-8d731ad94c05_183574970": 1.0}}, {"text": "Simple Habit is also used by digital nomads, offering daily meditations to ease tension and sharpen attention, as well as specialized sessions for enhancing concentration.", "citations": {"1139a92e-09f2-4972-8ff3-8d731ad94c05_183574970": 1.0}}, {"text": "Focus@Will provides customized music to avoid distractions and includes a timer and productivity tracker, helping digital nomads stay focused.", "citations": {"1139a92e-09f2-4972-8ff3-8d731ad94c05_183574970": 1.0}}, {"text": "Momentum Dash personalizes browser pages for productivity, and Offtime blocks distracting apps and notifications on phones, helping digital nomads manage their time effectively.", "citations": {"1139a92e-09f2-4972-8ff3-8d731ad94c05_183574970": 1.0}}, {"text": "Mindly organizes thoughts and ideas in a visual way, and Freedom blocks distracting websites and apps across devices, providing a comprehensive productivity solution.", "citations": {"1139a92e-09f2-4972-8ff3-8d731ad94c05_183574970": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital Well-being is a free tool from Google that helps track device usage time and limits app use, offering daily reports on app usage and notifications.", "citations": {"3613edc3-8524-43f2-a74f-3e5768d21a7a_597732867": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital Well-being also has a focus mode to disable distracting apps, a night mode to reduce screen brightness, and daily timers to limit app usage time.", "citations": {"3613edc3-8524-43f2-a74f-3e5768d21a7a_597732867": 1.0}}, {"text": "Time Cop is a private time tracking app for digital nomads that has an offline-only and mobile-centric design, running on Linux, iOS, and Android.", "citations": {"37584b59-40e1-4952-a8e9-fdb2b706656b_30134373": 1.0}}, {"text": "Time Cop has multiple parallel timers, exports data as a .csv file, and is fully private with no tracking or ads.", "citations": {"37584b59-40e1-4952-a8e9-fdb2b706656b_30134373": 1.0}}, {"text": "ClickUp is used for time tracking and project management, providing a global timer for tracking time from anywhere and manual time tracking for adding time retroactively.", "citations": {"4da88c2e-7272-4f4e-9fb0-62813b55fce7_850324156": 1.0}}, {"text": "ClickUp helps with task allocation and resource management, enables budget tracking and cost estimation, and identifies time wasters to improve productivity.", "citations": {"4da88c2e-7272-4f4e-9fb0-62813b55fce7_850324156": 1.0}}, {"text": "FocalFilter blocks time-wasting sites to increase productivity, and Focus Booster manages tasks with timers for better time management", "citations": {}}], "references": ["0bcc3cd5-42e6-4327-9e7f-cc72b91d6d43_187602728", "3613edc3-8524-43f2-a74f-3e5768d21a7a_597732867", "c7b767c9-09fd-43c7-83f7-b07f61e38ae6_818229618", "45215aed-649b-4e8b-8378-232300408e0a_554827344", "b4568a97-2125-422d-b744-7ceb6ce8de83_308632223", "495a3813-6b54-48f9-a9d3-18b74a1a72df_561526741", "6e880013-b616-4fdf-b1a7-1402fbb4d69e_40305401", "09cbaa0c-5e42-4814-a1a1-3e28d939b1c4_202321090", "ea90bb4e-0607-4636-afd5-5e325bcbfef8_77576442", "088e0346-91bf-43fd-b68c-748ae1e1247f_998032520", "59724541-c800-4b93-8655-97a4c778640f_938844996", "72836102-23df-4f82-b338-56a356464891_682732748", "4da88c2e-7272-4f4e-9fb0-62813b55fce7_850324156", "1139a92e-09f2-4972-8ff3-8d731ad94c05_183574970", "c4f9ce00-bbf9-49d0-affd-ee93f10c14f0_357802443", "2d43eb04-5d8b-4a30-bed0-4156dde6a2bd_586353010", "d812d020-b4d6-4b3b-a420-9f195bdf4ac4_35559448", "37584b59-40e1-4952-a8e9-fdb2b706656b_30134373", "fd58cfb9-f01b-4078-86a9-871fc3f6410e_322621379", "c529ac8d-80af-410a-a327-3546b54a14c8_242137462", "b6583863-0f88-476a-9f78-57b143ae24bd_50003737", "07cf246f-1952-45a1-8031-4d4ba74b540a_121181923", "15e8540b-5ba4-4152-9f0a-a15471c6bcb8_8