{"metadata": {"team_id": "attract", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1007", "run_id": "attract-biological"}, "responses": [{"text": "Pakistan is the first country to purchase the J-10C, China's most advanced exported fighter, ordering 60 aircraft.", "citations": {"3ec181a2-af55-4af9-aeb3-8720edd1498e_711423819": 1.0}}, {"text": "The deal between China and Pakistan is worth about $1.5 billion, with each J-10C costing around $50 million.", "citations": {"558e844a-b52a-4f3a-8553-1ab6b696cb94_230889465": 1.0}}, {"text": "Pakistan plans to counter India's Rafale fighters with the J-10C, equipped with PL-15 missiles and active phased array radar.", "citations": {"558e844a-b52a-4f3a-8553-1ab6b696cb94_230889465": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10C is a 4.5-generation fighter jet with a bigger AESA radar and capability to carry fourth-generation air-to-air missiles.", "citations": {"cd6f7c06-5e22-4103-9de2-9817a9a60efa_121885815": 1.0}}, {"text": "Iran, Sudan, and Turkey are considering purchasing the J-10C to replace old aircraft or counter Indian fighters.", "citations": {"55be5184-98d3-47c4-8cdb-a96dfd09f592_1054504209": 1.0, "9e893a13-a5bb-4822-8f87-187cba831d3d_453477269": 0.5}}, {"text": "Pakistan's air force has praised the J-10C's combat capabilities, stating it improves the country's military capability.", "citations": {"cd6f7c06-5e22-4103-9de2-9817a9a60efa_121885815": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10C has low operating costs and requires less maintenance than other fighter jets, making it an attractive option for countries upgrading their air forces.", "citations": {"7662ae65-98c5-4a3f-9b24-83a5f9fb7a72_115461755": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10C has a 2,500km range, 1.9-ton payload capacity, and can carry missiles like the PL-15 and PL-10.", "citations": {"3e945ab6-3a90-49b4-a584-faa7b598737a_769586939": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10C is a formidable opponent due to its excellent maneuverability and quasi-stealth capabilities.", "citations": {"4b6adb7c-7a19-43aa-a46b-c07f9c22bb81_62818012": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10C has limitations, including reliability concerns with its WS-10B engine and potentially high maintenance costs.", "citations": {"3e945ab6-3a90-49b4-a584-faa7b598737a_769586939": 1.0}}, {"text": "Pakistan has received 25 J-10C fighter jets from China for its air force.", "citations": {"cd6f7c06-5e22-4103-9de2-9817a9a60efa_121885815": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10C is a highly advanced fighter jet with network-centric warfare and electronic warfare capabilities.", "citations": {"ff09c670-9bf8-4f5d-b6c2-1b4699af2744_618195561": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10C has a reduced radar cross section and a low-visibility coating, making it more stealthy.", "citations": {"ff09c670-9bf8-4f5d-b6c2-1b4699af2744_618195561": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10C is expected to become the Pakistan Air Force's elite fighter due to its strong performance and capabilities.", "citations": {"ff09c670-9bf8-4f5d-b6c2-1b4699af2744_618195561": 1.0}}, {"text": "Countries that have purchased the J-10C may need to invest in advanced maintenance and technical support for its effective operation.", "citations": {"7662ae65-98c5-4a3f-9b24-83a5f9fb7a72_115461755": 1.0}}, {"text": "Its low operating costs, maneuverability, and advanced avionics make it a formidable air opponent and valuable asset for network-centric and electronic warfare.", "citations": {"ff09c670-9bf8-4f5d-b6c2-1b4699af2744_618195561": 1.0}}, {"text": "Countries considering the J-10C must weigh its limitations, including reliability concerns and maintenance costs.", "citations": {"3e945ab6-3a90-49b4-a584-faa7b598737a_769586939": 1.0}}], "references": ["ff09c670-9bf8-4f5d-b6c2-1b4699af2744_618195561", "55be5184-98d3-47c4-8cdb-a96dfd09f592_1054504209", "7662ae65-98c5-4a3f-9b24-83a5f9fb7a72_115461755", "3e945ab6-3a90-49b4-a584-faa7b598737a_769586939", "9e893a13-a5bb-4822-8f87-187cba831d3d_453477269", "4b6adb7c-7a19-43aa-a46b-c07f9c22bb81_62818012", "3ec181a2-af55-4af9-aeb3-8720edd1498e_711423819", "558e844a-b52a-4f3a-8553-1ab6b696cb94_230889465", "cd6f7c06-5e22-4103-9de2-9817a9a60efa_121885815"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "attract", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1008", "run_id": "attract-biological"}, "responses": [{"text": "The J-10 fighter jet has been exported to several countries, including Pakistan, which has purchased 25 J-10CE fighters from China, with the country's J-10C fleet reaching 12 aircraft.", "citations": {"3ec181a2-af55-4af9-aeb3-8720edd1498e_711423819": 1.0}}, {"text": "Pakistan initially ordered 36 J-10C fighters, and the J-10C is China's first export order.", "citations": {"3ec181a2-af55-4af9-aeb3-8720edd1498e_711423819": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10C performance equals third-generation fighters, and Pakistan adheres to the one-China policy, receiving strong Chinese military assistance.", "citations": {"3ec181a2-af55-4af9-aeb3-8720edd1498e_711423819": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10C is China's most advanced exported fighter jet, and Pakistan is buying J-10C fighters from China.", "citations": {"558e844a-b52a-4f3a-8553-1ab6b696cb94_230889465": 1.0}}, {"text": "The country plans to purchase 35 to 40 J-10Cs for $1.5 billion, with each J-10C costing around $390 million.", "citations": {"558e844a-b52a-4f3a-8553-1ab6b696cb94_230889465": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10C will be the Pakistan Air Force's strongest fighter, and the first 25 J-10Cs will be delivered to Pakistan for the National Day parade.", "citations": {"558e844a-b52a-4f3a-8553-1ab6b696cb94_230889465": 1.0}}, {"text": "Iran is likely to import China's J-10C fighter jets due to sanctions, and the J-10C is a likely option for Iran's next-generation fighter.", "citations": {"55be5184-98d3-47c4-8cdb-a96dfd09f592_1054504209": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10C is equipped with AESA radar and PL-15 long-range air-to-air missile, making it an attractive option for countries under sanctions.", "citations": {"55be5184-98d3-47c4-8cdb-a96dfd09f592_1054504209": 1.0}}, {"text": "Egypt is in talks with China to purchase the J-10C fighter jet, and the Egyptian Air Force has sent a delegation to meet with Chengdu Aircraft Industries.", "citations": {"613a83ef-3b15-4765-854b-5d60ed7cc56c_379388153": 1.0}}, {"text": "Turkey considers replacing its F-16 with the J-10 fighter jet, and China has produced about 350 J-10 aircraft since 2005.", "citations": {"7662ae65-98c5-4a3f-9b24-83a5f9fb7a72_1044319203": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10 has a range of 1800 kilometers, can carry air-to-air missiles and bombs, and has a speed of 2,336 km/h.", "citations": {"7662ae65-98c5-4a3f-9b24-83a5f9fb7a72_1044319203": 1.0}}, {"text": "Turkey considers importing Chinese J-10C fighter jets, and Pakistan has imported Chinese J-10C fighter jets since 2022.", "citations": {"7662ae65-98c5-4a3f-9b24-83a5f9fb7a72_115461755": 1.0}}, {"text": "China exports J-10C to foreign countries like Pakistan, and the J-10C has low operating cost and improved avionics.", "citations": {"7662ae65-98c5-4a3f-9b24-83a5f9fb7a72_115461755": 1.0}}, {"text": "Sudan is buying China's J-10C fighter jets, and the country will be the second customer after Pakistan.", "citations": {"9e893a13-a5bb-4822-8f87-187cba831d3d_453477269": 1.0}}, {"text": "Sudan's purchase price may be higher than Pakistan's, and the J-10C will counter India's French Tornado and F-16.", "citations": {"9e893a13-a5bb-4822-8f87-187cba831d3d_453477269": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10C has been praised for its performance, with some reports suggesting that it excels in close-range combat against other fighter jets such as the J-16 and Su-35.", "citations": {"4b6adb7c-7a19-43aa-a46b-c07f9c22bb81_62818012": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10C has undergone several upgrades and modifications, including the installation of active phased array radar and missile warning devices.", "citations": {"4b6adb7c-7a19-43aa-a46b-c07f9c22bb81_62818012": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10C has a range of 2,500 kilometers and can carry a payload of 1.9 tons, making it a capable multirole fighter.", "citations": {"3e945ab6-3a90-49b4-a584-faa7b598737a_769586939": 1.0}}, {"text": "However, some reports have highlighted the J-10's limitations, including its vulnerability to destruction and lack of protection.", "citations": {"855ab901-32d2-49c8-b179-311d41c4a12f_597420948": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10C has been delivered to Pakistan, with 25 fighter jets handed over to the Pakistan Air Force.", "citations": {"cd6f7c06-5e22-4103-9de2-9817a9a60efa_121885815": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10C is expected to improve Pakistan's combat capabilities, and is considered a 4.5-generation medium-sized fighter jet.", "citations": {"cd6f7c06-5e22-4103-9de2-9817a9a60efa_121885815": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10CE is an export version of the J-10C, which has improved avionics and network-centric warfare capabilities, as well as electronic warfare countermeasures.", "citations": {"ff09c670-9bf8-4f5d-b6c2-1b4699af2744_618195561": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10CE has been purchased by Pakistan for potential combat use, and is expected to be the Pakistan Air Force's elite fighter.", "citations": {"ff09c670-9bf8-4f5d-b6c2-1b4699af2744_618195561": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10 fighter has received mixed reviews, with some praising its maneuverability and weapon package, while others have highlighted its reliability issues and limited export performance.", "citations": {"a834da70-5664-4631-bba7-dba8ef82cd52_942464069": 1.0}}, {"text": "Overall, the J-10 fighter jet has been a significant export success for China, with several countries showing interest in purchasing the jet.", "citations": {"7662ae65-98c5-4a3f-9b24-83a5f9fb7a72_1044319203": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10 has excellent high altitude and high speed performance, but it has poor reliability and export performance due to engine issues.", "citations": {"a834da70-5664-4631-bba7-dba8ef82cd52_942464069": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10's price is half that of the F-16, which makes it a competitive option in the export market.", "citations": {"a834da70-5664-4631-bba7-dba8ef82cd52_942464069": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10C has a larger AESA radar than the JF-17 Block 3, and can carry fourth-generation air-to-air missiles.", "citations": {"cd6f7c06-5e22-4103-9de2-9817a9a60efa_121885815": 1.0}}, {"text": "China will deliver 25 J-10C fighter jets to Pakistan, and the J-10C is a 4.5-generation medium-sized fighter jet, more powerful than the JF-17 fighter jet.", "citations": {"cd6f7c06-5e22-4103-9de2-9817a9a60efa_121885815": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10C improves Pakistan Air Force's combat capabilities, and it is also known as \"vigorous dragon\".", "citations": {"cd6f7c06-5e22-4103-9de2-9817a9a60efa_121885815": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10CE has low-visibility coating on cockpit cover, and it has new avionics and network-centric warfare capabilities.", "citations": {"ff09c670-9bf8-4f5d-b6c2-1b4699af2744_618195561": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10CE has helmet sights and electronic warfare countermeasures, and it has AESA radars with air-to-air missiles.", "citations": {"ff09c670-9bf8-4f5d-b6c2-1b4699af2744_618195561": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10CE's radar cross section has been significantly reduced, and Pakistan's J-10CE purchase raises concerns about performance.", "citations": {"ff09c670-9bf8-4f5d-b6c2-1b4699af2744_618195561": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10CE is expected to become Pakistan Air Force's elite fighter, and it has similar cockpit cover to US F-22 fighter.", "citations": {"ff09c670-9bf8-4f5d-b6c2-1b4699af2744_618195561": 1.0}}, {"text": "Pakistan is the first country in the region to benefit from J-10CE technology, and the J-10C has a larger AESA radar than JF-17 Block 3.", "citations": {"cd6f7c06-5e22-4103-9de2-9817a9a60efa_121885815": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10 has 11 mounting points for weapons and can carry laser-guided missiles and GPS-guided bombs, with a range of 2,500 kilometers and 1.9 tons payload.", "citations": {"3e945ab6-3a90-49b4-a584-faa7b598737a_769586939": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10 uses phased array radar to track 10 targets and can attack 2 targets with semi-active radar, and 4 targets with active radar.", "citations": {"3e945ab6-3a90-49b4-a584-faa7b598737a_769586939": 1.0}}, {"text": "In comparison, the F-15 radar can track 14 targets and attack 6, while the J-10 has been upgraded with domestic engine WS-10B.", "citations": {"3e945ab6-3a90-49b4-a584-faa7b598737a_769586939": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10C has active phased array radar with increased detection distance, and carries Perke-15 long-range radar guided missile and Perke-10 infrared fighting missile.", "citations": {"4b6adb7c-7a19-43aa-a46b-c07f9c22bb81_62818012": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10C's maneuverability is key to victory in close combat, and it outperforms J-16 and Su-35 in close-range combat, although its radar is inferior to J-16's airborne phased array radar.", "citations": {"4b6adb7c-7a19-43aa-a46b-c07f9c22bb81_62818012": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Su-35S has superior maneuverability of the 4++ generation, and is equipped with N035 Irbis radar system, carrying weapons on 12 points, and using R-73, R-77, and R-37M missiles.", "citations": {"6d5e3712-9d59-43a2-af35-82cf7c21e5d7_575154043": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10 has six under-wing external suspension points for weapons, a top speed of 2,336 km/h, a range of 1800 kilometers, and an altitude limit of 20,000 meters.", "citations": {"7662ae65-98c5-4a3f-9b24-83a5f9fb7a72_1044319203": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10C has an electronic radar and infrared guidance system, and can carry air-to-air missiles and laser-guided bombs, with a 23 mm internal machine gun.", "citations": {"7662ae65-98c5-4a3f-9b24-83a5f9fb7a72_1044319203": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10 is considered an alternative to the US F-16 fighter jet, and has been produced around 350 units since 2005.", "citations": {"7662ae65-98c5-4a3f-9b24-83a5f9fb7a72_1044319203": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10 has modern electronic warfare equipment and various missiles, while the Su-35 has modern radars and target detection station.", "citations": {"82c7d54c-fbec-441a-91f2-7aca1b82742c_1008363996": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10 is less expensive than J-16 to produce and maintain, and the Su-35 can launch R-37 and Ka-77 missiles.", "citations": {"82c7d54c-fbec-441a-91f2-7aca1b82742c_1008363996": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10's AESA radar is limited by Russian engine power, but it carries more missiles than some counterparts, and has better performance against Sukhois and Mirages.", "citations": {"855ab901-32d2-49c8-b179-311d41c4a12f_597420948": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10 has 11 hanging points but can only carry four missiles, with a limited internal oil load of 2.9 tons, while the F-16 has 9 hanging points and can carry 8 tons of weapons.", "citations": {"9749babb-dacd-4c90-9e4b-7b0e777899bc_432035562": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10C has single engine and dual delta wing configuration for high performance, and uses active phased array radar for enhanced capabilities.", "citations": {"a834da70-5664-4631-bba7-dba8ef82cd52_942464069": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10C made its public debut in 2017 at PLA anniversary parade, and Pakistan Air Force ordered 36 J-10CE fighters for foreign procurement.", "citations": {"a834da70-5664-4631-bba7-dba8ef82cd52_942464069": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10C has advanced avionics systems, multi-type advanced airborne weapons, and medium-close air control capabilities, with accurate strike capabilities against ground and sea targets.", "citations": {"be33afe4-1234-428c-b4fb-1131c471d30e_1055680907": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10C is a third-generation supersonic multipurpose fighter, carrying auxiliary fuel tanks and weapons systems, and participated in Zhuhai Air Show for the first time.", "citations": {"be33afe4-1234-428c-b4fb-1131c471d30e_1055680907": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10C has a larger AESA radar than JF-17 Block 3, and can carry fourth-generation air-to-air missiles, including PL-10 and PL-15 missiles.", "citations": {"cd6f7c06-5e22-4103-9de2-9817a9a60efa_121885815": 1.0}}, {"text": "China will deliver 25 J-10C fighter jets to Pakistan, and the J-10C is a 4.5-generation medium-sized fighter jet, more powerful than the JF-17 fighter jet.", "citations": {"cd6f7c06-5e22-4103-9de2-9817a9a60efa_121885815": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10C uses local WS-10B engines instead of Russian AL-31F, and has a multirole fourth-generation fighter capability, with L-150 \"Pastel\" radar warning system.", "citations": {"e4b92110-9fbd-434c-b539-87860d18695f_699124503": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10C has new avionics and network-centric warfare capabilities, with helmet sights and electronic warfare countermeasures, and AESA radars with Peri-15 and Peri-10 air-to-air missiles.", "citations": {"ff09c670-9bf8-4f5d-b6c2-1b4699af2744_618195561": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10CE has a low-visibility golden cockpit cover, reducing radar cross-sectional area, and is expected to be Pakistan Air Force's elite fighter, with similar cockpit cover to US F-22 and J-20.", "citations": {"ff09c670-9bf8-4f5d-b6c2-1b4699af2744_618195561": 1.0}}, {"text": "Pakistan is the first country to benefit from J-10CE technology, and the country is buying 35 to 40 J-10C fighters from", "citations": {}}], "references": ["558e844a-b52a-4f3a-8553-1ab6b696cb94_230889465", "9749babb-dacd-4c90-9e4b-7b0e777899bc_432035562", "613a83ef-3b15-4765-854b-5d60ed7cc56c_379388153", "9e893a13-a5bb-4822-8f87-187cba831d3d_453477269", "3e945ab6-3a90-49b4-a584-faa7b598737a_769586939", "855ab901-32d2-49c8-b179-311d41c4a12f_597420948", "cd6f7c06-5e22-4103-9de2-9817a9a60efa_121885815", "6d5e3712-9d59-43a2-af35-82cf7c21e5d7_575154043", "82c7d54c-fbec-441a-91f2-7aca1b82742c_1008363996", "be33afe4-1234-428c-b4fb-1131c471d30e_1055680907", "e4b92110-9fbd-434c-b539-87860d18695f_699124503", "7662ae65-98c5-4a3f-9b24-83a5f9fb7a72_115461755", "4b6adb7c-7a19-43aa-a46b-c07f9c22bb81_62818012", "55be5184-98d3-47c4-8cdb-a96dfd09f592_1054504209", "a834da70-5664-4631-bba7-dba8ef82cd52_942464069", "3ec181a2-af55-4af9-aeb3-8720edd1498e_711423819", "7662ae65-98c5-4a3f-9b24-83a5f9fb7a72_1044319203", "ff09c670-9bf8-4f5d-b6c2-1b4699af2744_618195561"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "attract", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1009", "run_id": "attract-biological"}, "responses": [{"text": "As a San Antonio city planner, understanding the impacts of Saharan dust storms on air quality, infrastructure, and public health is essential.", "citations": {}}, {"text": "Saharan dust storms bring hot, dry weather to San Antonio, causing hazy sunrises and sunsets and reducing rain chances.", "citations": {"121e372a-9dcd-4b4a-8dd2-1dea85b3c174_804983030": 1.0}}, {"text": "Saharan dust storms peak from late June to mid-August, causing hazy skies and breathing issues in South Texas.", "citations": {"5dc9163b-9ad8-4a82-8d61-269b3aa8f216_79048364": 1.0}}, {"text": "Saharan dust storms traveling from North Africa can worsen respiratory illnesses.", "citations": {"5dc9163b-9ad8-4a82-8d61-269b3aa8f216_79048364": 1.0}}, {"text": "Saharan dust can cause minor allergy-like symptoms in Texas and give the skies a milky hue.", "citations": {"847379b8-aea2-4369-b4fb-37b79f3e9753_449770659": 1.0}}, {"text": "To prepare for Saharan dust storms, monitor air quality and take precautions, especially if you have a respiratory illness.", "citations": {"5dc9163b-9ad8-4a82-8d61-269b3aa8f216_79048364": 1.0}}, {"text": "The city's power grid can be affected by Saharan dust storms, requiring upgrades and emergency plans to mitigate disruptions.", "citations": {"2af1935e-a992-4e19-a952-4a617dfa1cfc_29833790": 1.0}}, {"text": "Roads can be closed during heavy dust storms due to low visibility, and meteorology departments issue warnings.", "citations": {"02702bcd-fb43-4669-b330-e50e4295c1f6_1016355279": 1.0}}, {"text": "People with respiratory illnesses should avoid going out during dust storms to minimize health impacts.", "citations": {"434e8b02-8260-462d-ac95-40c19671b792_527192492": 1.0}}, {"text": "Wearing a muzzle or mask can help prevent dust entry and reduce respiratory risks.", "citations": {"434e8b02-8260-462d-ac95-40c19671b792_527192492": 1.0, "674ea45b-8522-4c29-9c9c-549d08278d84_176840780": 0.5, "9797cf01-4068-4d81-990b-78e90ab8b714_131682061": 0.25, "a4836f98-6671-47ec-85e3-6beee34928f3_390734008": 0.125, "a703bdc3-ae3c-438b-be87-dae3ae28a171_568898432": 0.0625, "b3ecdaa4-029d-49e3-ac30-fca64d81c798_536114052": 0.03125, "d2ad2c2b-4cb3-461a-a94c-298b31f47ee0_337092502": 0.015625, "d4777c31-c669-4d14-9ce3-8f80c0a8d706_15902920": 0.0078125, "dbd709ac-5600-48fe-9600-66218cdc28bf_106587816": 0.00390625, "e63fc314-91ea-428b-a9f9-60f852bd4052_76532119": 0.001953125, "edf4d263-1da5-4b51-a0e3-a2a63941433b_1044867268": 0.0009765625, "f19b92cf-edf9-4d3b-8843-741a12dcf7c6_513223553": 0.00048828125}}, {"text": "Staying in well-ventilated places can help avoid suffocation and respiratory problems.", "citations": {"434e8b02-8260-462d-ac95-40c19671b792_527192492": 1.0, "9797cf01-4068-4d81-990b-78e90ab8b714_131682061": 0.5, "d4777c31-c669-4d14-9ce3-8f80c0a8d706_15902920": 0.25}}, {"text": "The city can establish community outreach programs to educate residents and visitors about Saharan dust storm health risks.", "citations": {"7e002029-a365-40b8-baba-8c404b218e2b_996038172": 1.0}}, {"text": "These programs advise residents to stay indoors, close doors and windows, and use air purifiers during dust storms.", "citations": {"7e002029-a365-40b8-baba-8c404b218e2b_996038172": 1.0}}, {"text": "Implementing plans to mitigate Saharan dust storms will be costly, and further research is needed to determine potential costs and benefits.", "citations": {"1243b2ef-0235-4ad4-acfa-23ee80169a94_215835065": 1.0}}, {"text": "San Antonio has a weather monitoring system to support emergency preparedness and community outreach.", "citations": {"13ea93b3-b90a-433c-83f5-d01dbdf2cf08_499069273": 1.0}}, {"text": "The city should prioritize funding and utilize its existing infrastructure to support plans to mitigate Saharan dust storms.", "citations": {"13ea93b3-b90a-433c-83f5-d01dbdf2cf08_499069273": 1.0, "1243b2ef-0235-4ad4-acfa-23ee80169a94_215835065": 0.5}}, {"text": "San Antonio can reduce the negative impacts of Saharan dust storms by taking proactive measures.", "citations": {"5dc9163b-9ad8-4a82-8d61-269b3aa8f216_79048364": 1.0}}, {"text": "The city's efforts to mitigate Saharan dust storms should be guided by the latest research and prioritize vulnerable populations, like those with respiratory illnesses.", "citations": {"5dc9163b-9ad8-4a82-8d61-269b3aa8f216_79048364": 1.0, "434e8b02-8260-462d-ac95-40c19671b792_527192492": 0.5}}, {"text": "Continued monitoring and research of Saharan dust storms is essential to develop effective mitigation strategies.", "citations": {"dd2b8c3b-fd24-4dc2-b2ec-faefaccc0418_755265099": 1.0}}], "references": ["674ea45b-8522-4c29-9c9c-549d08278d84_176840780", "7e002029-a365-40b8-baba-8c404b218e2b_996038172", "edf4d263-1da5-4b51-a0e3-a2a63941433b_1044867268", "2af1935e-a992-4e19-a952-4a617dfa1cfc_29833790", "b3ecdaa4-029d-49e3-ac30-fca64d81c798_536114052", "e63fc314-91ea-428b-a9f9-60f852bd4052_76532119", "dbd709ac-5600-48fe-9600-66218cdc28bf_106587816", "13ea93b3-b90a-433c-83f5-d01dbdf2cf08_499069273", "5dc9163b-9ad8-4a82-8d61-269b3aa8f216_79048364", "a703bdc3-ae3c-438b-be87-dae3ae28a171_568898432", "d4777c31-c669-4d14-9ce3-8f80c0a8d706_15902920", "847379b8-aea2-4369-b4fb-37b79f3e9753_449770659", "121e372a-9dcd-4b4a-8dd2-1dea85b3c174_804983030", "02702bcd-fb43-4669-b330-e50e4295c1f6_1016355279", "1243b2ef-0235-4ad4-acfa-23ee80169a94_215835065", "f19b92cf-edf9-4d3b-8843-741a12dcf7c6_513223553", "dd2b8c3b-fd24-4dc2-b2ec-faefaccc0418_755265099", "a4836f98-6671-47ec-85e3-6beee34928f3_390734008", "9797cf01-4068-4d81-990b-78e90ab8b714_131682061", "434e8b02-8260-462d-ac95-40c19671b792_527192492", "d2ad2c2b-4cb3-461a-a94c-298b31f47ee0_337092502"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "attract", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1010", "run_id": "attract-biological"}, "responses": [{"text": "As a city planner in San Antonio, TX, it is essential to understand the potential impacts of Saharan dust storms on the city's air quality, respiratory health, and other aspects of citizen well-being.", "citations": {}}, {"text": "Saharan dust storms can cause respiratory diseases and allergies, and exacerbate cardiovascular diseases and eye diseases, particularly in San Antonio, TX.", "citations": {"a703bdc3-ae3c-438b-be87-dae3ae28a171_568898432": 1.0}}, {"text": "The dust peaks in late June through mid-August, and citizens with respiratory illnesses, such as asthma and COPD, should stay indoors during dust storms to minimize exposure to poor air quality.", "citations": {"5dc9163b-9ad8-4a82-8d61-269b3aa8f216_79048364": 1.0}}, {"text": "Wearing a mask helps avoid dust entry to airways, and drinking 2 liters of water improves lung blood flow.", "citations": {"434e8b02-8260-462d-ac95-40c19671b792_527192492": 1.0}}, {"text": "Closing windows and doors helps keep particles outside and prevents dust entry into houses.", "citations": {"434e8b02-8260-462d-ac95-40c19671b792_527192492": 1.0, "436f6dca-3571-4e87-b474-e70ec06c96ce_47645537": 0.5, "7e002029-a365-40b8-baba-8c404b218e2b_996038172": 0.25, "a4836f98-6671-47ec-85e3-6beee34928f3_390734008": 0.125, "a703bdc3-ae3c-438b-be87-dae3ae28a171_568898432": 0.0625, "c900d048-6402-4c50-a80d-ce34a6198233_143573691": 0.03125, "d4777c31-c669-4d14-9ce3-8f80c0a8d706_15902920": 0.015625, "e63fc314-91ea-428b-a9f9-60f852bd4052_76532119": 0.0078125}}, {"text": "N95 respirator masks reduce exposure to airborne particulate pollution and filter out small particles when worn correctly.", "citations": {"436f6dca-3571-4e87-b474-e70ec06c96ce_47645537": 1.0, "d4777c31-c669-4d14-9ce3-8f80c0a8d706_15902920": 0.5}}, {"text": "Staying indoors with good air quality is recommended, especially for people with respiratory illnesses, as it helps minimize exposure to dust storms.", "citations": {"436f6dca-3571-4e87-b474-e70ec06c96ce_47645537": 1.0, "5dc9163b-9ad8-4a82-8d61-269b3aa8f216_79048364": 0.5, "7e002029-a365-40b8-baba-8c404b218e2b_996038172": 0.25, "a4836f98-6671-47ec-85e3-6beee34928f3_390734008": 0.125, "a703bdc3-ae3c-438b-be87-dae3ae28a171_568898432": 0.0625, "c900d048-6402-4c50-a80d-ce34a6198233_143573691": 0.03125, "d4777c31-c669-4d14-9ce3-8f80c0a8d706_15902920": 0.015625, "e63fc314-91ea-428b-a9f9-60f852bd4052_76532119": 0.0078125, "edf4d263-1da5-4b51-a0e3-a2a63941433b_1044867268": 0.00390625}}, {"text": "The temperature in San Antonio, TX during a Saharan dust storm is expected to reach the low to mid-90s.", "citations": {"64fa5383-5a9a-4623-a472-e9660b1fc324_186813227": 1.0}}, {"text": "Winds in San Antonio during a Saharan dust storm come from the southeast and west at 5-10 knots.", "citations": {"64fa5383-5a9a-4623-a472-e9660b1fc324_186813227": 1.0}}, {"text": "Afternoon scattered storms can occur during a Saharan dust storm in San Antonio, helping to keep temperatures below the Heat Advisory level.", "citations": {"64fa5383-5a9a-4623-a472-e9660b1fc324_186813227": 1.0}}, {"text": "However, winds in San Antonio can also reach 20 to 30 mph during a storm, with gusts up to 45 mph expected in the area.", "citations": {"69a90ede-c00b-4144-9bfb-f82a76ba99db_487102147": 1.0}}, {"text": "These strong winds can impact the city's infrastructure, causing blown unsecured objects and tree limbs, and potentially resulting in power outages.", "citations": {"69a90ede-c00b-4144-9bfb-f82a76ba99db_487102147": 1.0}}, {"text": "The strong winds can also affect daily life, with drivers advised to use extra caution during the storm, especially those driving high profile vehicles.", "citations": {"69a90ede-c00b-4144-9bfb-f82a76ba99db_487102147": 1.0}}, {"text": "Outdoor objects should be secured during the storm to prevent damage and injury.", "citations": {"69a90ede-c00b-4144-9bfb-f82a76ba99db_487102147": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Saharan dust storm can also affect air quality, especially for those with asthma or COPD, causing hazy skies and breathing issues.", "citations": {"5dc9163b-9ad8-4a82-8d61-269b3aa8f216_79048364": 1.0}}, {"text": "The dust can combine sand and dust from North Africa, peaking in late June through mid-August, and affecting air quality throughout the week.", "citations": {"5dc9163b-9ad8-4a82-8d61-269b3aa8f216_79048364": 1.0}}, {"text": "Relief from the miserable weather is expected late in the next couple of days, with rogue showers possible in western Hill Country.", "citations": {"10d51b7a-38ba-4932-b057-41cbcb286084_1019182606": 1.0}}, {"text": "The city may experience milky white skies during afternoons and vibrant sunrises and sunsets due to the increased dust.", "citations": {"5dc9163b-9ad8-4a82-8d61-269b3aa8f216_79048364": 1.0}}, {"text": "Boating conditions are not severely affected by the wind during a Saharan dust storm.", "citations": {"64fa5383-5a9a-4623-a472-e9660b1fc324_186813227": 1.0}}, {"text": "Temperatures can persist in the high range on Sunday during the storm, with highs reaching 94\u00baF and 95\u00baF.", "citations": {"fca8890e-e803-45e4-bcfc-bb931582373a_201640595": 1.0}}, {"text": "The temperature lows can reach 79\u00baF at night, with moderate wind speeds expected on weekends.", "citations": {"fca8890e-e803-45e4-bcfc-bb931582373a_201640595": 1.0}}, {"text": "Breezy conditions can occur throughout the weekend, with gusts reaching up to 20 mph at night.", "citations": {"fca8890e-e803-45e4-bcfc-bb931582373a_201640595": 1.0}}, {"text": "Saharan dust storms can reduce thunderstorm activity by 50% due to low moisture.", "citations": {"976e5a88-b9d0-4613-be71-b666fa22d6f3_776351012": 1.0}}, {"text": "Saharan dust impacts hurricane season with reduced cyclone formation, which can have a significant effect on precipitation patterns in San Antonio, TX.", "citations": {"976e5a88-b9d0-4613-be71-b666fa22d6f3_776351012": 1.0}}, {"text": "The dry air and dust brought by Saharan dust storms are wild cards in tropical weather forecasts, making it challenging to predict the exact impact on San Antonio's weather.", "citations": {"976e5a88-b9d0-4613-be71-b666fa22d6f3_776351012": 1.0}}, {"text": "Years with significant Saharan dust experience reduced cyclone activity, which can lead to changes in precipitation patterns.", "citations": {"976e5a88-b9d0-4613-be71-b666fa22d6f3_776351012": 1.0}}, {"text": "Saharan dust can be detrimental to cloud formation and thunderstorms, affecting the city's water supply.", "citations": {"976e5a88-b9d0-4613-be71-b666fa22d6f3_776351012": 1.0}}, {"text": "Over 180 million tons of dust leave Africa annually, affecting the weather in the Americas, including San Antonio, TX.", "citations": {"976e5a88-b9d0-4613-be71-b666fa22d6f3_776351012": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Saharan Air Layer, which occurs from June to November, can bring haze and an orange horizon to Texas skies, including San Antonio.", "citations": {"847379b8-aea2-4369-b4fb-37b79f3e9753_449770659": 1.0}}, {"text": "Saharan dust storms can prevent storms from growing and strengthening, which can impact precipitation patterns in San Antonio.", "citations": {"847379b8-aea2-4369-b4fb-37b79f3e9753_449770659": 1.0}}, {"text": "Flooding is expected in south central Texas, including San Antonio, due to excessive rainfall, which can be exacerbated by the city's flood control systems.", "citations": {"5091cdd5-8a84-4c99-a5d9-76f407e8b065_606070600": 1.0}}, {"text": "Up to 2 inches of rain have fallen in the San Antonio area, with additional rainfall amounts up to 1 inch expected, leading to minor flooding in low-lying and poor drainage areas.", "citations": {"5091cdd5-8a84-4c99-a5d9-76f407e8b065_606070600": 1.0}}, {"text": "Flash flooding caused by thunderstorms is ongoing or expected in San Antonio, with flash flooding warnings issued for surrounding counties.", "citations": {"5091cdd5-8a84-4c99-a5d9-76f407e8b065_717321304": 1.0}}, {"text": "The National Weather Service has issued a Flash Flood Warning for southeastern Texas, including San Antonio, due to the potential for deadly flooding.", "citations": {"5091cdd5-8a84-4c99-a5d9-76f407e8b065_717321304": 1.0}}, {"text": "San Antonio faces water restrictions due to drought, with the Edwards Aquifer level around 631 feet, and stage four water restrictions triggered if the aquifer drops.", "citations": {"f3228440-9126-4eae-8a30-0b7f922258cd_712507094": 1.0}}, {"text": "The city's water supply is also affected by the low water levels in Medina Lake, which is only 9% full, and some area rivers having zero flow rates.", "citations": {"f3228440-9126-4eae-8a30-0b7f922258cd_712507094": 1.0}}, {"text": "The rainfall deficit in San Antonio is around 14 inches, making the city's water supply vulnerable to changes in precipitation patterns caused by Saharan dust storms.", "citations": {"f3228440-9126-4eae-8a30-0b7f922258cd_712507094": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tropical disturbances can bring some relief to the city's water supply, but the impact of Saharan dust storms on these systems is still a concern.", "citations": {"f3228440-9126-4eae-8a30-0b7f922258cd_712507094": 1.0}}, {"text": "Appropriate preparations to mitigate contemporary Saharan dust storms in San Antonio include monitoring local weather forecasts and warnings, and taking precautions to prevent flooding and water damage.", "citations": {"e4597b86-aa49-4dbd-a125-0d3d1e2cde34_962343730": 1.0}}, {"text": "Residents of San Antonio should be aware of the potential for flash flooding and take necessary precautions, such as turning around and not drowning when encountering flooded roads.", "citations": {"e4597b86-aa49-4dbd-a125-0d3d1e2cde34_962343730": 1.0}}, {"text": "The city's flood control systems should be prepared to handle excessive rainfall and flash flooding, which can be exacerbated by Saharan dust storms.", "citations": {"cb9196d4-5eb0-484d-b874-0203d40fe35a_456648827": 1.0}}, {"text": "Strong thunderstorms can impact the San Antonio area, bringing torrential rainfall and gusty winds, which can lead to localized flooding and minor damage to outdoor objects.", "citations": {"e4597b86-aa49-4dbd-a125-0d3d1e2cde34_962343730": 1.0}}, {"text": "Dust storms can damage fruit crops like mango and citrus, as the strong winds cause fruits to fall before maturity.", "citations": {"0a2d1ec2-1ee6-4f95-9d00-3b75d29dc6d0_517927188": 1.0}}, {"text": "Dust storms can also reduce visibility and cause low horizontal visibility, with wind speeds exceeding 45 km per hour.", "citations": {"0a2d1ec2-1ee6-4f95-9d00-3b75d29dc6d0_517927188": 1.0}}, {"text": "The air masses from Western Sahara can lead to high temperatures, and the unstable atmosphere continues throughout the day during dust storms.", "citations": {"0a2d1ec2-1ee6-4f95-9d00-3b75d29dc6d0_517927188": 1.0}}, {"text": "In San Antonio, TX, Saharan dust arrives in late June to mid-August, affecting people with respiratory illnesses like asthma and COPD.", "citations": {"5dc9163b-9ad8-4a82-8d61-269b3aa8f216_79048364": 1.0}}, {"text": "The dust can cause hazy skies and breathing trouble for sensitive individuals, and high pressure brings southeasterly flow pumping dust to South Texas.", "citations": {"5dc9163b-9ad8-4a82-8d61-269b3aa8f216_79048364": 1.0}}, {"text": "To mitigate the effects of Saharan dust storms, individuals with respiratory issues should avoid vigorous exercise and keep windows and doors closed during high dust levels.", "citations": {"5dc9163b-9ad8-4a82-8d61-269b3aa8f216_79048364": 1.0}}, {"text": "Millions of tons of Saharan dust cross the Atlantic annually, suppressing hurricane development and strength, and bringing nutrients to oceans and land, like iron and phosphorus.", "citations": {"847379b8-aea2-4369-b4fb-37b79f3e9753_449770659": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Saharan dust can affect Texas skies with haze and orange sunsets, and cause minor allergy-like symptoms for some in Texas.", "citations": {"847379b8-aea2-4369-b4fb-37b79f3e9753_449770659": 1.0}}, {"text": "However, the search results do not provide direct information on the economic impacts of Saharan dust storms on local businesses, tourism, and agriculture in San Antonio, TX.", "citations": {"0a2d1ec2-1ee6-4f95-9d00-3b75d29dc6d0_517927188": 1.0, "5dc9163b-9ad8-4a82-8d61-269b3aa8f216_79048364": 0.5, "847379b8-aea2-4369-b4fb-37b79f3e9753_449770659": 0.25}}, {"text": "The search results also do not provide specific strategies that can be employed to mitigate the economic effects of Saharan dust storms in San Antonio, TX.", "citations": {"0a2d1ec2-1ee6-4f95-9d00-3b75d29dc6d0_517927188": 1.0, "5dc9163b-9ad8-4a82-8d61-269b3aa8f216_79048364": 0.5, "847379b8-aea2-4369-b4fb-37b79f3e9753_449770659": 0.25}}, {"text": "Dust storms can lead to catastrophic damage to agricultural crops, which can have significant economic impacts on the agricultural industry.", "citations": {"0a2d1ec2-1ee6-4f95-9d00-3b75d29dc6d0_517927188": 1.0}}, {"text": "Insects like thrips and aphids can rapidly rehabilitate after dust storms, which can help to spread fruit trees, but this may not be relevant to the economic impacts in San Antonio, TX.", "citations": {"0a2d1ec2-1ee6-4f95-9d00-3b75d29dc6d0_517927188": 1.0}}, {"text": "Saharan dust affects Texas skies with a haze and milky hue.", "citations": {"847379b8-aea2-4369-b4fb-37b79f3e9753_449770659": 1.0}}, {"text": "Dust causes minor allergy-like symptoms for some in Texas.", "citations": {"847379b8-aea2-4369-b4fb-37b79f3e9753_449770659": 1.0}}, {"text": "Saharan dust suppresses hurricane development and strength.", "citations": {"847379b8-aea2-4369-b4fb-37b79f3e9753_449770659": 1.0}}, {"text": "Dust is rich in nutrients like iron and phosphorus.", "citations": {"847379b8-aea2-4369-b4fb-37b79f3e9753_449770659": 1.0}}, {"text": "180 million tons of dust are transported across the Atlantic yearly.", "citations": {"847379b8-aea2-4369-b4fb-37b79f3e9753_449770659": 1.0}}, {"text": "Saharan dust fertilizes algae and plankton in the ocean.", "citations": {"847379b8-aea2-4369-b4fb-37b79f3e9753_449770659": 1.0}}, {"text": "Dust benefits areas like the Amazon rainforest with extra nutrients.", "citations": {"847379b8-aea2-4369-b4fb-37b79f3e9753_449770659": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Saharan Air Layer limits hurricane formation and growth.", "citations": {"847379b8-aea2-4369-b4fb-37b79f3e9753_449770659": 1.0}}, {"text": "There is no direct mention of economic impact on local businesses.", "citations": {"847379b8-aea2-4369-b4fb-37b79f3e9753_449770659": 1.0}}, {"text": "There is no available information on specific economic impacts on tourism and agriculture in San Antonio, TX.", "citations": {"847379b8-aea2-4369-b4fb-37b79f3e9753_449770659": 1.0}}, {"text": "The available data does not provide quantifiable effects of Saharan dust storms on local businesses, tourism, and agriculture in San Antonio, TX.", "citations": {"847379b8-aea2-4369-b4fb-37b79f3e9753_449770659": 1.0}}, {"text": "Dust storms increase in spring and autumn seasons, which can have significant implications for regions like San Antonio, TX.", "citations": {"1fd604e6-30ba-4b91-b53c-ecb5241f2624_55169144": 1.0}}, {"text": "Desertification causes dust storms due to drought and human activities, highlighting the need for sustainable land use practices to mitigate their effects.", "citations": {"1fd604e6-30ba-4b91-b53c-ecb5241f2624_55169144": 1.0}}, {"text": "Dust storms transport dust and plankton, reducing visibility and potentially impacting local businesses and tourism in San Antonio, TX.", "citations": {"1fd604e6-30ba-4b91-b53c-ecb5241f2624_55169144": 1.0}}, {"text": "Dust storms contribute to allergic reactions and breathing problems, which can have negative impacts on public health and the local economy.", "citations": {"1fd604e6-30ba-4b91-b53c-ecb5241f2624_55169144": 1.0}}, {"text": "Saharan dust suppresses hurricane development, which can have positive impacts on regions like San Antonio, TX that are prone to hurricane activity.", "citations": {"847379b8-aea2-4369-b4fb-37b79f3e9753_449770659": 1.0}}, {"text": "Saharan dust is rich in nutrients like iron and phosphorus, and fertilizes algae and plankton, which can have beneficial effects on local ecosystems.", "citations": {"847379b8-aea2-4369-b4fb-37b79f3e9753_449770659": 1.0}}, {"text": "However, Saharan dust can also cause minor allergy-like symptoms in Texas, which can negatively impact local residents and tourists.", "citations": {"847379b8-aea2-4369-b4fb-37b79f3e9753_449770659": 1.0}}, {"text": "The economic impacts of dust storms on local businesses, tourism, and agriculture in San Antonio, TX can be significant, with the city losing $21 million in conference cancellations due to COVID-19, a related but distinct economic disruption.", "citations": {"84e45b67-3423-4fc3-9626-bbc03074a8ec_1067813509": 1.0}}, {"text": "Texas loses $80 billion in direct travel spending and double in economic", "citations": {}}], "references": ["cb9196d4-5eb0-484d-b874-0203d40fe35a_456648827", "d4777c31-c669-4d14-9ce3-8f80c0a8d706_15902920", "edf4d263-1da5-4b51-a0e3-a2a63941433b_1044867268", "a703bdc3-ae3c-438b-be87-dae3ae28a171_568898432", "64fa5383-5a9a-4623-a472-e9660b1fc324_186813227", "10d51b7a-38ba-4932-b057-41cbcb286084_1019182606", "e4597b86-aa49-4dbd-a125-0d3d1e2cde34_962343730", "e63fc314-91ea-428b-a9f9-60f852bd4052_76532119", "847379b8-aea2-4369-b4fb-37b79f3e9753_449770659", "7e002029-a365-40b8-baba-8c404b218e2b_996038172", "5091cdd5-8a84-4c99-a5d9-76f407e8b065_717321304", "0a2d1ec2-1ee6-4f95-9d00-3b75d29dc6d0_517927188", "434e8b02-8260-462d-ac95-40c19671b792_527192492", "84e45b67-3423-4fc3-9626-bbc03074a8ec_1067813509", "436f6dca-3571-4e87-b474-e70ec06c96ce_47645537", "f3228440-9126-4eae-8a30-0b7f922258cd_712507094", "976e5a88-b9d0-4613-be71-b666fa22d6f3_776351012", "c900d048-6402-4c50-a80d-ce34a6198233_143573691", "fca8890e-e803-45e4-bcfc-bb931582373a_201640595", "69a90ede-c00b-4144-9bfb-f82a76ba99db_487102147", "a4836f98-6671-47ec-85e3-6beee34928f3_390734008", "1fd604e6-30ba-4b91-b53c-ecb5241f2624_55169144", "5dc9163b-9ad8-4a82-8d61-269b3aa8f216_79048364", "5091cdd5-8a84-4c99-a5d9-76f407e8b065_606070600"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "attract", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1011", "run_id": "attract-biological"}, "responses": [{"text": "Mohammed bin Salman has introduced reforms as part of his 2030 vision to diversify Saudi Arabia's economy and reduce its dependence on oil.", "citations": {"2b3920b8-8643-4db0-8193-eb85f79b7368_479346508": 1.0}}, {"text": "The reforms include restricting the religious police's powers and improving women's rights, such as driving and attending concerts.", "citations": {"2b3920b8-8643-4db0-8193-eb85f79b7368_479346508": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Vision 2030 plan, launched in 2016, aims to transform the economy by increasing productivity and reducing spending.", "citations": {"776d6523-b2ce-4640-8969-33bc9666c8d7_71692390": 1.0}}, {"text": "The plan has seen significant progress, with 8.2 percent non-oil sector growth and an eight-rank advance in the World Competitiveness Yearbook 2022.", "citations": {"3575335e-eed6-4f6d-be45-e0b382b2a227_139594759": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women now make up 34.5 percent of the labor market and hold over 30 percent of middle and senior management positions.", "citations": {"b32bb298-210c-43d8-8b00-fde663665b52_715750258": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Kingdom achieved significant economic growth in 2023, with non-oil GDP exceeding 50 percent of GDP.", "citations": {"bd18bfb8-3df1-40fe-80d2-e6f7164cb150_463168187": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Vision 2030 plan has 243 indicators, with 176 exceeding 2023 expectations and 105 exceeding both 2023 and 2024 targets.", "citations": {"d1468c3c-66bf-45f2-aedd-88c6519e1dc3_909172667": 1.0}}, {"text": "The plan aims to raise the private sector's GDP contribution to 65 percent by 2030, with foreign direct investment already reaching $33 billion.", "citations": {"d1468c3c-66bf-45f2-aedd-88c6519e1dc3_909172667": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Saudi government has limited the powers of the Commission for the Promotion of Virtue and Prevention of Vice to reduce Wahhabi influence.", "citations": {"0f1b1e80-0ad8-47a9-958c-d307747ea092_404328681": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Commission now focuses on awareness campaigns and promoting ethics, without intervening in inappropriate behaviors.", "citations": {"2e03709c-a0f2-49c3-a204-0c5ebe79580e_315280229": 1.0}}, {"text": "The international community, including the IMF, has welcomed Saudi Arabia's economic reforms.", "citations": {"1c840334-99eb-4d0f-8bc2-f0129e0b4bf0_766333428": 1.0}}, {"text": "The IMF commended Saudi Arabia's efforts to promote private sector growth.", "citations": {"1c840334-99eb-4d0f-8bc2-f0129e0b4bf0_766333428": 1.0}}, {"text": "The reforms have faced criticism for not adequately addressing the country's human rights record.", "citations": {"eac6eeef-f0fb-427b-b9b3-a05209fb6f82_892176758": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Saudi government has been criticized for arresting women's rights activists.", "citations": {"eac6eeef-f0fb-427b-b9b3-a05209fb6f82_892176758": 1.0}}, {"text": "The government remains committed to Vision 2030, implementing reforms to promote development and reduce poverty.", "citations": {"f88cc687-b5a3-4a62-9459-8f6a00de7e89_312357274": 1.0}}], "references": ["b32bb298-210c-43d8-8b00-fde663665b52_715750258", "2b3920b8-8643-4db0-8193-eb85f79b7368_479346508", "3575335e-eed6-4f6d-be45-e0b382b2a227_139594759", "1c840334-99eb-4d0f-8bc2-f0129e0b4bf0_766333428", "0f1b1e80-0ad8-47a9-958c-d307747ea092_404328681", "eac6eeef-f0fb-427b-b9b3-a05209fb6f82_892176758", "bd18bfb8-3df1-40fe-80d2-e6f7164cb150_463168187", "776d6523-b2ce-4640-8969-33bc9666c8d7_71692390", "d1468c3c-66bf-45f2-aedd-88c6519e1dc3_909172667", "f88cc687-b5a3-4a62-9459-8f6a00de7e89_312357274", "2e03709c-a0f2-49c3-a204-0c5ebe79580e_315280229"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "attract", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1012", "run_id": "attract-biological"}, "responses": [{"text": "Mohammed bin Salman Al Saud, also known as MBS, has introduced a series of social and economic reforms in Saudi Arabia since his appointment as crown prince in 2017, aiming to diversify the economy and reduce oil dependence.", "citations": {"776d6523-b2ce-4640-8969-33bc9666c8d7_71692390": 1.0}}, {"text": "The reforms, part of his 2030 vision, have included empowering Saudi women and youth, and have received great support from the young population.", "citations": {"776d6523-b2ce-4640-8969-33bc9666c8d7_71692390": 1.0}}, {"text": "MBS has pushed through reforms that have shaken conservative Saudi Arabia, including the reopening of cinemas and the holding of film festivals and operas.", "citations": {"61f0a264-c8d0-472b-8599-43892bc248e2_211721979": 1.0}}, {"text": "The religious police have lost power, and MBS has arrested dissidents and forced religious organizations to obey.", "citations": {"61f0a264-c8d0-472b-8599-43892bc248e2_211721979": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women's rights have been improved, with the lifting of the decades-old ban on women driving and the allowance of women to attend concerts and sporting events.", "citations": {"61f0a264-c8d0-472b-8599-43892bc248e2_211721979": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Vision 2030 plan, launched by MBS in 2016, aims to diversify the economy beyond oil and attract young talent and companies.", "citations": {"776d6523-b2ce-4640-8969-33bc9666c8d7_71692390": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tourism is a new source of income for the Kingdom, and the economy has grown 8.7 percent in 2022.", "citations": {"776d6523-b2ce-4640-8969-33bc9666c8d7_71692390": 1.0, "a7edd07c-2d1d-41a1-b70d-fb67a5716290_360343144": 0.5}}, {"text": "Saudi Arabia has invested heavily in future technology, including a $6.4 billion investment and the launch of a $1 billion startup fund by Aramco.", "citations": {"77efa69a-9deb-4197-a702-ff3ae577fa6e_384696518": 1.0}}, {"text": "The country has also opened up to entertainment and tourism, with the creation of a gaming development group and the investment of $1 billion in cloud services hub by STC.", "citations": {"77efa69a-9deb-4197-a702-ff3ae577fa6e_384696518": 1.0}}, {"text": "However, the repression of political dissidents and human rights activists has been a major concern, with arrests and torture reported since 2017.", "citations": {"98212169-eb6b-4484-9329-2896742036b3_583754114": 1.0}}, {"text": "The assassination of Jamal Khashoggi in 2018 has also been a major controversy, and the country has a poor record on freedom of expression.", "citations": {"98212169-eb6b-4484-9329-2896742036b3_583754114": 1.0}}, {"text": "Despite these challenges, MBS has vowed to lead a moderate and free kingdom, and the social reforms have been widely supported by Saudi youth.", "citations": {"953f9f72-db6e-42cd-9ebe-68dd95925d36_92212195": 1.0}}, {"text": "The reforms have included changes to women's dress code and freedom, with women allowed to walk without a head covering and attend mixed concerts.", "citations": {"8df408b2-a4b8-4ddf-a1da-96da547a30eb_982545951": 1.0, "b07a8d73-e542-437e-8984-decb47d00cb5_125623190": 0.5}}, {"text": "The Saudization policy has replaced foreigners with Saudi citizens, and women make up 49.8 percent of Saudi nationals, with the ability to drive cars and enter the labor market.", "citations": {"a7edd07c-2d1d-41a1-b70d-fb67a5716290_360343144": 1.0}}, {"text": "Overall, the social reforms under MBS since 2017 have been significant, but the country still faces challenges in terms of human rights and freedom of expression.", "citations": {"09767899-ea0d-4c2a-a52c-1914cc6e079c_804292179": 1.0, "98212169-eb6b-4484-9329-2896742036b3_583754114": 0.5}}, {"text": "The implementation of Vision 2030 in Saudi Arabia has enhanced women's roles and promoted their participation in various fields, with unlimited support from the leadership.", "citations": {"4d1faeda-b88d-41c9-a433-d495c0696931_1020377662": 1.0}}, {"text": "Vision 2030 has granted Saudi women full rights, allowing them to work in all fields, and their presence in the labor market has become normal.", "citations": {"5f1834f3-fc63-4390-aa65-55fa5ea07503_901908835": 1.0}}, {"text": "The plan has addressed the issue of female and male salary differences, and women's rights have improved significantly since its launch.", "citations": {"5f1834f3-fc63-4390-aa65-55fa5ea07503_901908835": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women's labor force participation has risen to 36% in Saudi Arabia, with over 1.47 million women employed in 2022, and their participation in the labor market has more than doubled.", "citations": {"7bad6264-fc46-435a-a015-08b4f16ceb06_210604472": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Kingdom has achieved advancements in education, health, and livelihood through the implementation of Vision 2030, which prioritizes the interests of the Saudi people.", "citations": {"7bad6264-fc46-435a-a015-08b4f16ceb06_326471779": 1.0}}, {"text": "Saudi Arabia is committed to achieving gender equality through Vision 2030 and has launched initiatives to accelerate women's role in national development.", "citations": {"8056a1e2-9194-4950-a72e-281a37526317_336251424": 1.0}}, {"text": "The government promotes women's empowerment and balanced equality, and women occupy high positions inside and outside the Kingdom.", "citations": {"4d1faeda-b88d-41c9-a433-d495c0696931_1020377662": 1.0}}, {"text": "Vision 2030 includes women's participation at all levels, and their labor market participation has increased to 33.8%, with a decrease in the unemployment rate for Saudis to 11.7% in 2021.", "citations": {"80c8da15-5fa3-4f38-8fa6-3c8ddc7d04f2_637833400": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women have made significant breakthroughs in taking their rights, and they have the right to education, which has opened doors to ambition.", "citations": {"a5598577-4c5f-436e-883f-a8c9f76c66ec_519525995": 1.0}}, {"text": "Saudi women have proven themselves in science and research, and they participate in drafting legislation and amending laws.", "citations": {"a5598577-4c5f-436e-883f-a8c9f76c66ec_519525995": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Kingdom guarantees equal pay for equal work without discrimination, and retirement age is equal for men and women, with education being free and accessible without discrimination.", "citations": {"b32bb298-210c-43d8-8b00-fde663665b52_715750258": 1.0}}, {"text": "Vision 2030 ensures equal opportunities and reduces inequality based on sex, with over 150 legislative reforms achieved since its adoption.", "citations": {"dfd14e7b-3406-4e16-a115-03740ce3a786_237343048": 1.0}}, {"text": "However, despite these advancements, challenges remain in achieving full equality for women in Saudi Arabia, including the male guardianship system, which still restricts women's decisions.", "citations": {"eac6eeef-f0fb-427b-b9b3-a05209fb6f82_892176758": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women's rights activists are arbitrarily arrested and detained, and female labor force participation remains low in Saudi Arabia.", "citations": {"eac6eeef-f0fb-427b-b9b3-a05209fb6f82_892176758": 1.0}}, {"text": "Some jobs in Saudi Arabia are still reserved for men, and restrictions on women working with men in certain shops remain.", "citations": {"f31c59b2-4dbf-4577-b5e5-171d743cf570_1000033909": 1.0}}, {"text": "Nevertheless, the implementation of Vision 2030 has changed women's status dramatically since 2016, and Crown Prince Mohammed bin Salman champions women's progress.", "citations": {"e3a72078-1055-4a67-be09-6dda7e9aca0b_126689011": 1.0}}, {"text": "Investing in Saudi women's training could yield $400 billion by 2030, and Vision 2030 enables women to obtain the highest levels of education.", "citations": {"e3a72078-1055-4a67-be09-6dda7e9aca0b_126689011": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Makkah Document affirms women's right to equal pay and promotes women's legitimate empowerment in Saudi Arabia.", "citations": {"46ce48cc-0ae1-4703-af4b-7e9f422ea00c_311242318": 1.0}}, {"text": "The document rejects marginalizing women's role and ensures fair equality in wages, with over 1200 muftis and scholars signing it.", "citations": {"46ce48cc-0ae1-4703-af4b-7e9f422ea00c_311242318": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Makkah Document strengthens women's rights in Saudi Arabia and promotes women's opportunities in various affairs.", "citations": {"46ce48cc-0ae1-4703-af4b-7e9f422ea00c_311242318": 1.0}}, {"text": "It also rejects insulting women's dignity and was signed by scholars from all Islamic sects.", "citations": {"46ce48cc-0ae1-4703-af4b-7e9f422ea00c_311242318": 1.0}}, {"text": "The document has been praised by international religious leaders and has been adopted by Islamic countries in Niamey, Niger.", "citations": {"71496ee3-2418-4aba-a591-9602bdddeff4_407562307": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Makkah Document celebrates religious and cultural diversity and is considered a turning point in Islamic history.", "citations": {"71496ee3-2418-4aba-a591-9602bdddeff4_407562307": 1.0}}, {"text": "However, some sources do not mention the Makkah Document specifically, but instead highlight other initiatives and reforms aimed at promoting women's empowerment in Saudi Arabia.", "citations": {"315a347c-6464-445b-99b1-39a02effae37_1048873339": 1.0, "7bad6264-fc46-435a-a015-08b4f16ceb06_210604472": 0.5, "f3f6c566-9c4f-4d07-a262-9f6ef4ef8f69_103249073": 0.25}}, {"text": "Saudi Arabia has made significant progress in promoting women's rights, with women's labor force participation increasing to 36% and employment rates reaching 30.4% in 2022.", "citations": {"7bad6264-fc46-435a-a015-08b4f16ceb06_210604472": 1.0}}, {"text": "The country has also launched programs to support working women and has promoted women's leadership, with Saudi women occupying senior positions in government institutions.", "citations": {"03a65bda-15ab-45ee-8824-f2c9b4fcc7aa_430978275": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Crown Prince of Saudi Arabia has stressed the importance of family stability and has initiated efforts to promote women's empowerment since 2016.", "citations": {"82c6566c-3a78-497c-8c35-ecd4eb506d81_576823188": 1.0}}, {"text": "Despite these efforts, some human rights groups have criticized Saudi Arabia's women's rights record, citing the need for further reforms.", "citations": {"fa56b545-7fd4-4147-9905-8c732476766f_208152208": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Makkah Document has played a significant role in promoting women's rights and empowerment in Saudi Arabia, but its impact and reception vary across different segments of Saudi society.", "citations": {"46ce48cc-0ae1-4703-af4b-7e9f422ea00c_311242318": 1.0, "71496ee3-2418-4aba-a591-9602bdddeff4_407562307": 0.5}}, {"text": "The key performance indicators used to measure the success of MBS's 2030 vision include real growth rate of economy, private sector growth rate, unemployment rate, national workers in private sector, Emiratization rate, women's participation rate in labor market, fiscal surplus, public expenditures, and GDP growth.", "citations": {"9da67260-bbac-4452-ab2d-d2267138a77c_812745220": 1.0}}, {"text": "The unemployment rate target is 7% by 2030, and the current unemployment rate is 9.7%, with a decrease of 0.4 percentage points.", "citations": {"0de0133f-5479-4c3c-be6c-9b7630e8e37a_246652226": 1.0}}, {"text": "The participation rate has increased by 1.5% to 67.5%, and the employed to population rate has increased by 1.6% to 64.3%.", "citations": {"0de0133f-5479-4c3c-be6c-9b7630e8e37a_246652226": 1.0}}, {"text": "Vision 2030 aims to develop human capabilities, with a focus on education and skill development, to enable citizens to compete globally.", "citations": {"0de0133f-5479-4c3c-be6c-9b7630e8e37a_246652226": 1.0}}, {"text": "The KPIs also include reducing the unemployment rate to 7%, achieving fiscal balance, improving government performance and capacity, and increasing employment in the private sector.", "citations": {"2a71159d-8419-47be-a5f6-27e2d320f5da_749180540": 1.0}}, {"text": "The vision has achieved most of its targets before the set dates, and the banking sector has been ranked fourth globally by Fitch.", "citations": {"2a71159d-8419-47be-a5f6-27e2d320f5da_749180540": 1.0}}, {"text": "The KPIs are tracked and evaluated through various means, including the publication of key facts and figures, such as the non-oil activities contributing 50% to GDP, and the non-oil government revenues reaching 457 billion riyals.", "citations": {"3070d6a1-fc25-41bc-8539-08c048cf7606_862949452": 1.0}}, {"text": "The real GDP has increased by 0.9%, and the inflation levels have fallen to 1.6% by 2023.", "citations": {"3070d6a1-fc25-41bc-8539-08c048cf7606_862949452": 1.0}}, {"text": "The kingdom ranks 17th globally in competitiveness and third among G20 countries in competitiveness.", "citations": {"3070d6a1-fc25-41bc-8539-08c048cf7606_862949452": 1.0}}, {"text": "The KPIs are also tracked through the National Center for Measuring Performance, which evaluates public sectors and tracks ministries' achievements.", "citations": {"a4356fd1-9158-4ed3-8641-d8dec70526d1_102378466": 1.0}}, {"text": "The performance is measured across three pillars: vital society, prosperous economy, and ambitious homeland.", "citations": {"624c59a5-41a2-42d1-85c4-ce9fc2ce26d9_111381016": 1.0}}, {"text": "The vision has achieved 75% of its targets, with the highest achievement since measurement started.", "citations": {"624c59a5-41a2-42d1-85c4-ce9fc2ce26d9_111381016": 1.0}}, {"text": "The KPIs targets are defined for the first and second level objectives of Vision 2030, and the non-oil private sector PMI has risen in November 2023.", "citations": {"624c59a5-41a2-42d1-85c4-ce9fc2ce26d9_111381016": 1.0}}, {"text": "The inflation has continued to decline in October 2023, and the percentage of completed initiatives has increased from Q2 2023.", "citations": {"624c59a5-41a2-42d1-85c4-ce9fc2ce26d9_111381016": 1.0}}, {"text": "The performance contracts measure efficiency and effectiveness, and user satisfaction is evaluated through performance indicators.", "citations": {"7f77426c-16a1-436e-a03e-3e5c8741ab8b_81662565": 1.0}}, {"text": "The governance programs are strengthened in the sector, and transparency and spending efficiency are achieved.", "citations": {"7f77426c-16a1-436e-a03e-3e5c8741ab8b_81662565": 1.0}}, {"text": "The latest technologies are used for project implementation, and the National Strategy for Transport and Logistics is followed.", "citations": {"7f77426c-16a1-436e-a03e-3e5c8741ab8b_81662565": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Vision 2030 objectives are achieved through performance contracts, and asset management methodology is used to measure performance.", "citations": {"7f77426c-16a1-436e-a03e-3e5c8741ab8b_81662565": 1.0}}, {"text": "The key performance indicators (KPIs) mentioned include satisfaction index of beneficiaries, sector participation in GDP, empowerment of beneficiaries able to work, and number of volunteers.", "citations": {"ba458257-2602-48bf-a8f4-1995348ba470_782835034": 1.0}}, {"text": "Saudi Arabia tracks 243 indicators for Vision 2030, with 176 indicators exceeding 2023 expectations, and 105 indicators exceeding 2023 and 2024 targets.", "citations": {"d1468c3c-66bf-45f2-aedd-88c6519e1dc3_909172667": 1.0}}, {"text": "The private sector contributes 45% to GDP, with a target of 65% private sector contribution to GDP by 2030.", "citations": {"d1468c3c-66bf-45f2-aedd-88c6519e1dc3_909172667": 1.0}}, {"text": "The women's labor market participation is 34%, and the unemployment among Saudis is 7.7%.", "citations": {"d1468c3c-66bf-45f2-aedd-88c6519e1dc3_909172667": 1.0}}, {"text": "The KPI", "citations": {}}], "references": ["7f77426c-16a1-436e-a03e-3e5c8741ab8b_81662565", "80c8da15-5fa3-4f38-8fa6-3c8ddc7d04f2_637833400", "624c59a5-41a2-42d1-85c4-ce9fc2ce26d9_111381016", "953f9f72-db6e-42cd-9ebe-68dd95925d36_92212195", "f3f6c566-9c4f-4d07-a262-9f6ef4ef8f69_103249073", "7bad6264-fc46-435a-a015-08b4f16ceb06_326471779", "776d6523-b2ce-4640-8969-33bc9666c8d7_71692390", "d1468c3c-66bf-45f2-aedd-88c6519e1dc3_909172667", "4d1faeda-b88d-41c9-a433-d495c0696931_1020377662", "77efa69a-9deb-4197-a702-ff3ae577fa6e_384696518", "3070d6a1-fc25-41bc-8539-08c048cf7606_862949452", "2a71159d-8419-47be-a5f6-27e2d320f5da_749180540", "a4356fd1-9158-4ed3-8641-d8dec70526d1_102378466", "0de0133f-5479-4c3c-be6c-9b7630e8e37a_246652226", "a7edd07c-2d1d-41a1-b70d-fb67a5716290_360343144", "61f0a264-c8d0-472b-8599-43892bc248e2_211721979", "03a65bda-15ab-45ee-8824-f2c9b4fcc7aa_430978275", "9da67260-bbac-4452-ab2d-d2267138a77c_812745220", "eac6eeef-f0fb-427b-b9b3-a05209fb6f82_892176758", "e3a72078-1055-4a67-be09-6dda7e9aca0b_126689011", "46ce48cc-0ae1-4703-af4b-7e9f422ea00c_311242318", "315a347c-6464-445b-99b1-39a02effae37_1048873339", "82c6566c-3a78-497c-8c35-ecd4eb506d81_576823188", "09767899-ea0d-4c2a-a52c-1914cc6e079c_804292179", "dfd14e7b-3406-4e16-a115-03740ce3a786_237343048", "b07a8d73-e542-437e-8984-decb47d00cb5_125623190", "98212169-eb6b-4484-9329-2896742036b3_583754114", "71496ee3-2418-4aba-a591-9602bdddeff4_407562307", "8056a1e2-9194-4950-a72e-281a37526317_336251424", "7bad6264-fc46-435a-a015-08b4f16ceb06_210604472", "5f1834f3-fc63-4390-aa65-55fa5ea07503_901908835", "fa56b545-7fd4-4147-9905-8c732476766f_208152208", "b32bb298-210c-43d8-8b00-fde663665b52_715750258", "8df408b2-a4b8-4ddf-a1da-96da547a30eb_982545951", "f31c59b2-4dbf-4577-b5e5-171d743cf570_1000033909", "ba458257-2602-48bf-a8f4-1995348ba470_782835034", "a5598577-4c5f-436e-883f-a8c9f76c66ec_519525995"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "attract", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1013", "run_id": "attract-biological"}, "responses": [{"text": "The slow food movement originated in Italy over 30 years ago, with a focus on promoting local ingredients, traditional food practices, and environmental protection.", "citations": {"3fc1cd45-38d0-4612-8e8e-21d9a4fd7376_751985363": 1.0}}, {"text": "The movement was started in the late 1980s by Carlo Petrini, who aimed to promote traditional food methods and local ingredients.", "citations": {"3fc1cd45-38d0-4612-8e8e-21d9a4fd7376_751985363": 1.0}}, {"text": "The slow food movement has been popular worldwide for over 30 years, with a presence in over 150 countries.", "citations": {"3fc1cd45-38d0-4612-8e8e-21d9a4fd7376_751985363": 1.0, "96da40f6-f654-43da-a3f7-d19d9c31ede9_78339237": 0.5}}, {"text": "The movement is guided by the principles of \"Good quality, clean and fair\", which emphasize the importance of sustainable and environmentally-friendly food production.", "citations": {"347aa98a-ba79-4341-963b-fe558f633c81_611052333": 1.0, "7c2a1fe5-6d77-43d3-b615-45dfa7772754_981252650": 0.5}}, {"text": "The slow food movement promotes traditional food culture in contemporary society, with a focus on seasonality, locality, and tradition in food production.", "citations": {"3fc1cd45-38d0-4612-8e8e-21d9a4fd7376_751985363": 1.0}}, {"text": "The movement has been promoted in Taitung, Taiwan, for over 10 years, where it has become a key part of the local food culture.", "citations": {"347aa98a-ba79-4341-963b-fe558f633c81_611052333": 1.0, "573bbdbd-ccb5-417f-82b3-117a2073ed1c_97571398": 0.5, "7c2a1fe5-6d77-43d3-b615-45dfa7772754_981252650": 0.25}}, {"text": "Some current proponents of the slow food movement worldwide include Carlo Petrini, Aruna Tirkey, Andrea Amato, and Ramon Uy Jr, who have been involved in various slow food initiatives and events globally.", "citations": {"3fc1cd45-38d0-4612-8e8e-21d9a4fd7376_751985363": 1.0, "a6e139e5-2201-4127-b6c0-b6b459a4db5e_18544158": 0.5, "b702106c-5025-4436-a5d8-8cb8153a683a_482923612": 0.25}}, {"text": "To sample the best slow food cuisine, one can visit Taitung, Taiwan, which hosts the Taitung Slow Food Festival, featuring local ingredients and food culture.", "citations": {"573bbdbd-ccb5-417f-82b3-117a2073ed1c_97571398": 1.0}}, {"text": "The festival has won Japan's Good Design Award and has been recognized for its efforts in promoting community engagement and cultural sensitivity.", "citations": {"89e87dc2-272d-4055-8419-f253560719f7_771613945": 1.0}}, {"text": "Other destinations for slow food enthusiasts include Yunlin County and Hualien County in Taiwan, which promote high-quality agricultural products, sustainable agriculture, and traditional food culture.", "citations": {"47c318de-0df6-40ed-976e-0abcd31d8ccb_585421035": 1.0, "ba5e7a01-a860-4e26-a47c-0e52b3c682e6_174285831": 0.5}}, {"text": "The slow food movement has contributed to preserving traditional food cultures and promoting sustainable agriculture, with various initiatives and events worldwide.", "citations": {"21597006-6a4b-4e4d-bdb3-16063020492e_526063534": 1.0, "347aa98a-ba79-4341-963b-fe558f633c81_611052333": 0.5, "47c318de-0df6-40ed-976e-0abcd31d8ccb_585421035": 0.25, "573bbdbd-ccb5-417f-82b3-117a2073ed1c_97571398": 0.125, "7c2a1fe5-6d77-43d3-b615-45dfa7772754_981252650": 0.0625, "89e87dc2-272d-4055-8419-f253560719f7_771613945": 0.03125, "a6e139e5-2201-4127-b6c0-b6b459a4db5e_18544158": 0.015625, "b702106c-5025-4436-a5d8-8cb8153a683a_482923612": 0.0078125, "ba5e7a01-a860-4e26-a47c-0e52b3c682e6_174285831": 0.00390625, "bef51873-d3bd-4cc6-b635-f7eb2515325e_755701371": 0.001953125, "dd7ff73b-98ef-45e7-9f14-d2a70c70b3c0_467564914": 0.0009765625, "e67a5795-5982-45ea-b316-ae40e65f5aa4_478826959": 0.00048828125}}, {"text": "Overall, the slow food movement is a global phenomenon that promotes a slower, more sustainable approach to food and living, and has a wide range of supporters and proponents around the world.", "citations": {"3fc1cd45-38d0-4612-8e8e-21d9a4fd7376_751985363": 1.0}}], "references": ["347aa98a-ba79-4341-963b-fe558f633c81_611052333", "3fc1cd45-38d0-4612-8e8e-21d9a4fd7376_751985363", "96da40f6-f654-43da-a3f7-d19d9c31ede9_78339237", "21597006-6a4b-4e4d-bdb3-16063020492e_526063534", "dd7ff73b-98ef-45e7-9f14-d2a70c70b3c0_467564914", "573bbdbd-ccb5-417f-82b3-117a2073ed1c_97571398", "b702106c-5025-4436-a5d8-8cb8153a683a_482923612", "a6e139e5-2201-4127-b6c0-b6b459a4db5e_18544158", "89e87dc2-272d-4055-8419-f253560719f7_771613945", "47c318de-0df6-40ed-976e-0abcd31d8ccb_585421035", "bef51873-d3bd-4cc6-b635-f7eb2515325e_755701371", "ba5e7a01-a860-4e26-a47c-0e52b3c682e6_174285831", "e67a5795-5982-45ea-b316-ae40e65f5aa4_478826959", "7c2a1fe5-6d77-43d3-b615-45dfa7772754_981252650"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "attract", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1014", "run_id": "attract-biological"}, "responses": [{"text": "The slow food movement originated in Italy over 30 years ago, with the goal of promoting good quality, clean, and fair food.", "citations": {"347aa98a-ba79-4341-963b-fe558f633c81_611052333": 1.0}}, {"text": "The movement was founded by Carlo Petrini in the 1980s as a reaction to the opening of McDonald's in Rome's heart, with the aim of defending regional food traditions.", "citations": {"3fc1cd45-38d0-4612-8e8e-21d9a4fd7376_751985363": 1.0, "96da40f6-f654-43da-a3f7-d19d9c31ede9_78339237": 0.5, "e5453a54-a53d-46c1-88ec-cb93130fa116_485767238": 0.25}}, {"text": "The slow food movement has since spread globally, with supporters in over 150 countries, and has been adapted and modified in non-Western contexts, such as in Asia.", "citations": {"347aa98a-ba79-4341-963b-fe558f633c81_611052333": 1.0, "573bbdbd-ccb5-417f-82b3-117a2073ed1c_97571398": 0.5, "96da40f6-f654-43da-a3f7-d19d9c31ede9_78339237": 0.25}}, {"text": "The movement promotes traditional food culture in contemporary society, focusing on seasonality, locality, and tradition, and aims to raise awareness of the industrial food system's impact and to build a sustainable and eco-friendly food system.", "citations": {"3fc1cd45-38d0-4612-8e8e-21d9a4fd7376_751985363": 1.0, "ba5e7a01-a860-4e26-a47c-0e52b3c682e6_174285831": 0.5, "b702106c-5025-4436-a5d8-8cb8153a683a_482923612": 0.25}}, {"text": "The slow food movement has been promoted in various locations, including Taitung, Taiwan, which has been promoting slow food for over 10 years, and hosts the International Slow Food Forum and the Taitung Slow Food Festival.", "citations": {"347aa98a-ba79-4341-963b-fe558f633c81_611052333": 1.0, "573bbdbd-ccb5-417f-82b3-117a2073ed1c_97571398": 0.5, "21597006-6a4b-4e4d-bdb3-16063020492e_526063534": 0.25}}, {"text": "The Taitung Slow Food Festival features local ingredients and unique diet, and has won Japan's Good Design Award, and is held annually in Taipei's Huashan 1914 Cultural Park.", "citations": {"bef51873-d3bd-4cc6-b635-f7eb2515325e_755701371": 1.0, "21597006-6a4b-4e4d-bdb3-16063020492e_526063534": 0.5}}, {"text": "To sample the best slow food cuisine, one can attend the Taitung Slow Food Festival, which features 30 restaurants and a variety of local ingredients and food culture.", "citations": {"573bbdbd-ccb5-417f-82b3-117a2073ed1c_97571398": 1.0, "bef51873-d3bd-4cc6-b635-f7eb2515325e_755701371": 0.5, "89e87dc2-272d-4055-8419-f253560719f7_771613945": 0.25}}, {"text": "The slow food movement has also been promoted in other parts of the world, including Italy, where the International Slow Food Headquarters is located, and India, Malaysia, and the Philippines, which have their own unique slow food traditions.", "citations": {"347aa98a-ba79-4341-963b-fe558f633c81_611052333": 1.0, "ba5e7a01-a860-4e26-a47c-0e52b3c682e6_174285831": 0.5, "b702106c-5025-4436-a5d8-8cb8153a683a_482923612": 0.25}}, {"text": "Current proponents of the slow food movement worldwide include over 30,000 activists, who participate in global Slow Food Conferences, and notable figures such as Aruna Tirkey from India, Nazlina Spice Station from Malaysia, and Ramon Uy Jr from Southeast Asia.", "citations": {"ba5e7a01-a860-4e26-a47c-0e52b3c682e6_174285831": 1.0, "b702106c-5025-4436-a5d8-8cb8153a683a_482923612": 0.5}}, {"text": "The slow food movement has led to the emergence of slow tourism and sustainable travel, with a focus on local folk food and environmental preservation, and has been recognized globally for its efforts to promote sustainable food systems and preserve traditional food cultures.", "citations": {"e5453a54-a53d-46c1-88ec-cb93130fa116_485767238": 1.0, "47c318de-0df6-40ed-976e-0abcd31d8ccb_585421035": 0.5}}, {"text": "Overall, the slow food movement offers a unique approach to food production and consumption, one that emphasizes quality, sustainability, and community involvement, and has the potential to promote positive change in diverse cultural settings around the world.", "citations": {"347aa98a-ba79-4341-963b-fe558f633c81_611052333": 1.0, "7c2a1fe5-6d77-43d3-b615-45dfa7772754_981252650": 0.5}}], "references": ["573bbdbd-ccb5-417f-82b3-117a2073ed1c_97571398", "ba5e7a01-a860-4e26-a47c-0e52b3c682e6_174285831", "e5453a54-a53d-46c1-88ec-cb93130fa116_485767238", "b702106c-5025-4436-a5d8-8cb8153a683a_482923612", "89e87dc2-272d-4055-8419-f253560719f7_771613945", "3fc1cd45-38d0-4612-8e8e-21d9a4fd7376_751985363", "347aa98a-ba79-4341-963b-fe558f633c81_611052333", "47c318de-0df6-40ed-976e-0abcd31d8ccb_585421035", "7c2a1fe5-6d77-43d3-b615-45dfa7772754_981252650", "21597006-6a4b-4e4d-bdb3-16063020492e_526063534", "bef51873-d3bd-4cc6-b635-f7eb2515325e_755701371", "96da40f6-f654-43da-a3f7-d19d9c31ede9_78339237"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "attract", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1015", "run_id": "attract-biological"}, "responses": [{"text": "The contemporary flat Earth movement has gained significant attention in recent years, mainly through social media.", "citations": {"f61994b0-dc34-40d6-a1e2-a7f66b22774b_548175167": 1.0}}, {"text": "Flat Earth societies exist in countries including the UK, where they have been criticized by Richard Dawkins at universities like Cambridge for promoting pseudoscience.", "citations": {"4c0ee3ad-3947-4c32-9bdc-e1ea45fa3dd9_669431569": 1.0}}, {"text": "In countries like Egypt, Romania, and Tunisia, individuals and organizations promote flat Earth theory via social media and online platforms.", "citations": {"50c7426a-508b-480c-94f9-7abba543020d_362358128": 1.0, "6e47a5cf-47a7-42a3-812e-ef81ba1e7a5f_46222320": 0.5, "7614d155-5beb-49f4-b13a-4f2675a1d6c8_866557951": 0.25}}, {"text": "Public figures like Kyrie Irving, Sammy Watkins, and Yuri Loza have expressed support for flat Earth theory, contributing to its popularity.", "citations": {"234c0ac8-224a-4ae9-b9fc-df4652c033eb_450387180": 1.0, "2990af1b-c7a6-422c-b322-682c563674ad_197670865": 0.5}}, {"text": "Flat Earth proponents argue that the Earth looks flat in footage and cite a lack of visible curve, also disputing its spherical nature.", "citations": {"4a564c34-5ed1-4d7d-961c-125e44d9f0aa_999086473": 1.0}}, {"text": "Scientific evidence and the vast majority of experts confirm the Earth is an oblate spheroid.", "citations": {"1f2e1692-fc89-4d74-94ce-348046c2140b_715798368": 1.0}}, {"text": "The resurgence of flat Earth beliefs may be linked to factors like financial struggles, health issues, narcissism, low analytical thinking, and anxiety.", "citations": {"bf008ce8-700e-4b3b-88ed-bac465f6aa3b_540286097": 1.0}}, {"text": "Social media has significantly contributed to the spread of conspiracy theories, including flat Earth ideology, among younger generations.", "citations": {"23b3f452-0d7f-49b9-898d-fa51ce1e5529_717482675": 1.0}}, {"text": "Parents should maintain good communication with their children to counter flat Earth beliefs from friends' families.", "citations": {"0bccd2ff-59da-4f33-8440-d01ae62047f8_910576184": 1.0}}, {"text": "Parents should teach their children critical thinking and media literacy to evaluate information effectively.", "citations": {"0e11d42f-a5b1-4bbb-b585-84e3274a7239_534772390": 1.0}}, {"text": "Parents can help their children develop critical thinking and media literacy to navigate complex social situations and make informed decisions.", "citations": {"1898ccb2-a289-4b8c-b712-f9c1a8916fb4_123956340": 1.0}}, {"text": "Parents should provide a supportive environment where children can openly discuss their beliefs and emotions.", "citations": {"5b6c419c-56c6-4df3-9cca-e0097a73f5c0_194988493": 1.0}}, {"text": "Addressing flat Earth misinformation requires promoting critical thinking, media literacy, and open communication to help children evaluate information effectively.", "citations": {"f0932c14-bf26-4a29-a8e3-cbacb4a1a279_599324161": 1.0}}], "references": ["5b6c419c-56c6-4df3-9cca-e0097a73f5c0_194988493", "0e11d42f-a5b1-4bbb-b585-84e3274a7239_534772390", "f0932c14-bf26-4a29-a8e3-cbacb4a1a279_599324161", "bf008ce8-700e-4b3b-88ed-bac465f6aa3b_540286097", "23b3f452-0d7f-49b9-898d-fa51ce1e5529_717482675", "4c0ee3ad-3947-4c32-9bdc-e1ea45fa3dd9_669431569", "1f2e1692-fc89-4d74-94ce-348046c2140b_715798368", "7614d155-5beb-49f4-b13a-4f2675a1d6c8_866557951", "6e47a5cf-47a7-42a3-812e-ef81ba1e7a5f_46222320", "f61994b0-dc34-40d6-a1e2-a7f66b22774b_548175167", "0bccd2ff-59da-4f33-8440-d01ae62047f8_910576184", "1898ccb2-a289-4b8c-b712-f9c1a8916fb4_123956340", "50c7426a-508b-480c-94f9-7abba543020d_362358128", "4a564c34-5ed1-4d7d-961c-125e44d9f0aa_999086473", "2990af1b-c7a6-422c-b322-682c563674ad_197670865", "234c0ac8-224a-4ae9-b9fc-df4652c033eb_450387180"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "attract", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1016", "run_id": "attract-biological"}, "responses": [{"text": "Contemporary flat Earth believers reject overwhelming scientific evidence that the Earth is a sphere, instead believing it is flat.", "citations": {"f61994b0-dc34-40d6-a1e2-a7f66b22774b_548175167": 1.0}}, {"text": "They argue the Earth is not round, citing the horizon's appearance at eye level and lack of visible curvature.", "citations": {"4a564c34-5ed1-4d7d-961c-125e44d9f0aa_999086473": 1.0}}, {"text": "Public figures like Kyrie Irving and Tila Tequila have publicly endorsed flat Earth beliefs, amplifying the movement.", "citations": {"234c0ac8-224a-4ae9-b9fc-df4652c033eb_450387180": 1.0}}, {"text": "The flat Earth movement is linked to other conspiracy theories, including anti-vaccination and anti-government ideologies.", "citations": {"6e47a5cf-47a7-42a3-812e-ef81ba1e7a5f_46222320": 1.0}}, {"text": "Research shows that those skeptical of authority and institutions tend to subscribe to flat Earth beliefs.", "citations": {"6e47a5cf-47a7-42a3-812e-ef81ba1e7a5f_46222320": 1.0}}, {"text": "People who believe in a flat Earth tend to have lower education, more cognitive biases, and greater distrust of institutions.", "citations": {"6e47a5cf-47a7-42a3-812e-ef81ba1e7a5f_46222320": 1.0}}, {"text": "The resurgence of flat Earth beliefs can be attributed to internet misinformation and charismatic figures.", "citations": {"f61994b0-dc34-40d6-a1e2-a7f66b22774b_548175167": 1.0}}, {"text": "The internet has enabled the spread of flat Earth ideologies and connected like-minded individuals.", "citations": {"f61994b0-dc34-40d6-a1e2-a7f66b22774b_548175167": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Flat Earth Society, with chapters in countries like the US, Canada, and the UK, promotes the idea and provides a platform for believers.", "citations": {"f61994b0-dc34-40d6-a1e2-a7f66b22774b_548175167": 1.0}}, {"text": "NFL players such as Sammy Watkins, Darius Slay, and Patrick Queen support the flat Earth theory.", "citations": {"234c0ac8-224a-4ae9-b9fc-df4652c033eb_450387180": 1.0}}, {"text": "Flat Earth arguments are not supported by scientific evidence.", "citations": {"cb0c3f18-a020-4791-a2ac-9a74a11514b5_356931984": 1.0}}, {"text": "Some flat Earth believers claim the Earth is flat due to the horizon's appearance at eye level and lack of visible curvature.", "citations": {"4a564c34-5ed1-4d7d-961c-125e44d9f0aa_999086473": 1.0}}, {"text": "Others claim that governments and organizations are hiding the Earth's true nature, fabricating or manipulating space images and videos.", "citations": {"4a564c34-5ed1-4d7d-961c-125e44d9f0aa_999086473": 1.0}}, {"text": "Flat Earth beliefs are influenced by a desire for autonomy, a need to challenge authority, and conspiratorial thinking.", "citations": {"6e47a5cf-47a7-42a3-812e-ef81ba1e7a5f_46222320": 1.0}}, {"text": "Social factors, including social media and the desire for community, contribute to the spread of flat Earth ideologies.", "citations": {"6e47a5cf-47a7-42a3-812e-ef81ba1e7a5f_46222320": 1.0}}, {"text": "To address flat Earth beliefs, focus on education and teaching critical thinking skills to recognize unreliable information.", "citations": {"0e11d42f-a5b1-4bbb-b585-84e3274a7239_534772390": 1.0}}, {"text": "Critical thinking skills can help evaluate conspiracy theories by promoting media literacy and constructive conversations about scientific evidence.", "citations": {"0a23f98b-5107-4cce-91a8-481591d1a7a6_853260936": 1.0}}, {"text": "Teaching critical thinking and focusing on education can prevent conspiracy theories and combat misinformation.", "citations": {"0e11d42f-a5b1-4bbb-b585-84e3274a7239_534772390": 1.0}}, {"text": "Recognizing unreliable sources and using analytical thinking can prevent the spread of conspiracy theories and misinformation.", "citations": {"0e11d42f-a5b1-4bbb-b585-84e3274a7239_534772390": 1.0}}, {"text": "Education can reduce belief in conspiracy theories, but factual counterarguments often have little effect.", "citations": {"0e11d42f-a5b1-4bbb-b585-84e3274a7239_534772390": 1.0}}, {"text": "Video games can combat misinformation and promote critical thinking about conspiracy theories.", "citations": {"0a23f98b-5107-4cce-91a8-481591d1a7a6_853260936": 1.0}}, {"text": "The internet must be kept safe and reliable to prevent the spread of misinformation.", "citations": {"0a23f98b-5107-4cce-91a8-481591d1a7a6_853260936": 1.0}}, {"text": "Parents influence children's critical thinking from a young age by teaching them to evaluate information reliability.", "citations": {"1898ccb2-a289-4b8c-b712-f9c1a8916fb4_123956340": 1.0}}, {"text": "Discussing situations with children and modeling argument culture using facts fosters critical thinking.", "citations": {"1898ccb2-a289-4b8c-b712-f9c1a8916fb4_123956340": 1.0}}, {"text": "Half of 15-year-olds can't distinguish facts from opinions, underscoring UNESCO's concerns about education, technology, and disinformation.", "citations": {"5efbdc36-5d1f-41e3-8eb4-65a5c1891d84_484451435": 1.0}}, {"text": "Investing in critical thinking is crucial to mitigate disinformation risks.", "citations": {"5efbdc36-5d1f-41e3-8eb4-65a5c1891d84_484451435": 1.0}}, {"text": "Media literacy education is essential in combating misinformation and is being promoted in schools.", "citations": {"7b4bbaf5-e66c-4dcf-a295-a8c7b4c95565_144354483": 1.0}}, {"text": "Taiwan's \"3X2 principle\" counters online misinformation with a \"zero trust\" approach to online information.", "citations": {"e74577b4-c6c3-4f44-a4a1-5de7aec14182_714973940": 1.0}}, {"text": "Education and critical thinking are essential for combating deep fake technology and preserving democracy.", "citations": {"e74577b4-c6c3-4f44-a4a1-5de7aec14182_714973940": 1.0}}, {"text": "By age 14, children often believe unproven conspiracy theories and many confuse ads with news stories.", "citations": {"f0932c14-bf26-4a29-a8e3-cbacb4a1a279_599324161": 1.0}}, {"text": "Education and collective action are necessary to develop critical thinking and protect children from misinformation.", "citations": {"f0932c14-bf26-4a29-a8e3-cbacb4a1a279_599324161": 1.0}}, {"text": "Policymakers and tech companies should develop norms and policies to regulate misinformation based on children's rights.", "citations": {"f0932c14-bf26-4a29-a8e3-cbacb4a1a279_599324161": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Ministry of Education promotes media literacy among teenagers through scientific news and rumor-cracking lesson plans.", "citations": {"f25532ee-612b-4201-9398-777633fc3a59_1051356406": 1.0}}, {"text": "The media literacy curriculum and scientific communication projects receive Ministry support.", "citations": {"f25532ee-612b-4201-9398-777633fc3a59_1051356406": 1.0}}, {"text": "Online curriculum enhances self-learning and analytical skills in students.", "citations": {"f25532ee-612b-4201-9398-777633fc3a59_1051356406": 1.0}}, {"text": "Believing in a flat Earth can hinder a teenager's academic and social development.", "citations": {"7614d155-5beb-49f4-b13a-4f2675a1d6c8_866557951": 1.0}}, {"text": "Media influence can spread false beliefs and perpetuate ignorance, especially among young people.", "citations": {"7614d155-5beb-49f4-b13a-4f2675a1d6c8_866557951": 1.0}}, {"text": "Destructive ideas and misinformation can be spread to children and the public through media.", "citations": {"7614d155-5beb-49f4-b13a-4f2675a1d6c8_866557951": 1.0}}, {"text": "False beliefs and social media misinformation can hinder teenagers' ability to distinguish fact from fiction, impeding academic development.", "citations": {"7614d155-5beb-49f4-b13a-4f2675a1d6c8_866557951": 1.0}}, {"text": "Public figures can influence teenagers, emphasizing the need for critical thinking to counter misinformation.", "citations": {"7614d155-5beb-49f4-b13a-4f2675a1d6c8_866557951": 1.0}}, {"text": "Negative thoughts and rejection can worsen over time and erode self-confidence in children with unconventional beliefs.", "citations": {"caae83a2-6127-4218-92b9-5cdc25849462_904914359": 1.0}}, {"text": "Self-loathing and low confidence can develop in teenagers with flat Earth beliefs due to harsh peer reactions and ostracism.", "citations": {"caae83a2-6127-4218-92b9-5cdc25849462_904914359": 1.0}}, {"text": "Parental pressure can lead to giving up and fear of failure, emphasizing the importance of supportive parenting.", "citations": {"caae83a2-6127-4218-92b9-5cdc25849462_904914359": 1.0}}, {"text": "Parents should emphasize love and support, and acknowledge their children's varying talents to foster a positive self-image.", "citations": {"caae83a2-6127-4218-92b9-5cdc25849462_904914359": 1.0}}, {"text": "By 14, many children believe unproven conspiracy theories and mistake ads for news, underscoring the need for media literacy.", "citations": {"f0932c14-bf26-4a29-a8e3-cbacb4a1a279_599324161": 1.0}}, {"text": "YouTube algorithms can spread false information, including flat Earth beliefs, by recommending extreme videos.", "citations": {"f0932c14-bf26-4a29-a8e3-cbacb4a1a279_599324161": 1.0}}, {"text": "Children are vulnerable to false information, making education and critical thinking skills essential.", "citations": {"f0932c14-bf26-4a29-a8e3-cbacb4a1a279_599324161": 1.0}}, {"text": "UNICEF recommends policymakers develop regulations to protect children from misinformation.", "citations": {"f0932c14-bf26-4a29-a8e3-cbacb4a1a279_599324161": 1.0}}, {"text": "Excessive social media use has long-term consequences on adolescents, whose developing brains are vulnerable to negative effects and misinformation.", "citations": {"fb92792f-3080-493c-a89a-094846f8e782_863632919": 1.0}}, {"text": "Social media can negatively impact teenagers' development, emphasizing the need for guidance and support.", "citations": {"fb92792f-3080-493c-a89a-094846f8e782_863632919": 1.0}}, {"text": "Frances Hogan warns that Instagram can harm young people and have negative long-term effects on teens.", "citations": {"fb92792f-3080-493c-a89a-094846f8e782_863632919": 1.0}}, {"text": "Older teens tend to be more liberal and humanitarian, and higher moral needs are associated with more liberal thinking, mitigating misinformation's negative effects.", "citations": {"69b8fd94-1cb6-4670-b3d5-2fd1662a06a1_305047613": 1.0}}, {"text": "Moral connection links individual identity and social community, and develops rapidly in youth through religious thinking.", "citations": {"69b8fd94-1cb6-4670-b3d5-2fd1662a06a1_305047613": 1.0}}, {"text": "Identity development in adolescents is influenced by community and organizational aspects of religion, which aid in forming moral values to navigate complex social issues.", "citations": {"69b8fd94-1cb6-4670-b3d5-2fd1662a06a1_305047613": 1.0}}, {"text": "Liberalism and humanitarianism are linked to prosocial moral indicators, emphasizing empathy and compassion.", "citations": {"69b8fd94-1cb6-4670-b3d5-2fd1662a06a1_305047613": 1.0}}, {"text": "Parents should maintain good communication with their children to address flat Earth beliefs and social pressures.", "citations": {"0bccd2ff-59da-4f33-8440-d01ae62047f8_910576184": 1.0}}, {"text": "Inviting their children's friends home helps parents understand their beliefs and values.", "citations": {"0bccd2ff-59da-4f33-8440-d01ae62047f8_910576184": 1.0}}, {"text": "Encouraging critical thinking about unsafe behaviors, like believing in conspiracy theories, can be effective.", "citations": {"0bccd2ff-59da-4f33-8440-d01ae62047f8_910576184": 1.0}}, {"text": "Prevention and education can counter conspiracy theories like flat Earth beliefs.", "citations": {"0e11d42f-a5b1-4bbb-b585-84e3274a7239_534772390": 1.0}}, {"text": "Teaching critical thinking can reduce belief in conspiracy theories, with parents playing a significant role.", "citations": {"0e11d42f-a5b1-4bbb-b585-84e3274a7239_534772390": 1.0}}, {"text": "Parents should focus on promoting critical thinking and media literacy rather than just refuting conspiracy theories with facts.", "citations": {"0e11d42f-a5b1-4bbb-b585-84e3274a7239_534772390": 1.0}}, {"text": "Respecting a teenager's privacy can help parents build trust and have open conversations about sensitive topics, like flat Earth beliefs.", "citations": {"1994d6db-6d7c-4579-a865-4884a579fdc0_774080507": 1.0}}, {"text": "Parents should avoid forcing interaction with guests or criticizing their teenager's friends to prevent tension.", "citations": {"1994d6db-6d7c-4579-a865-4884a579fdc0_774080507": 1.0}}, {"text": "Showing interest in a teenager's hobbies can help parents build a stronger relationship and encourage open conversations.", "citations": {"5b6c419c-56c6-4df3-9cca-e0097a73f5c0_194988493": 1.0}}, {"text": "Spend quality time with your child to positively influence their beliefs and values.", "citations": {"5b6c419c-56c6-4df3-9cca-e0097a73f5c0_194988493": 1.0}}, {"text": "Effective communication is crucial for healthy relationships and encourages open dialogue about sensitive topics.", "citations": {}}], "references": ["4a564c34-5ed1-4d7d-961c-125e44d9f0aa_999086473", "1994d6db-6d7c-4579-a865-4884a579fdc0_774080507", "0bccd2ff-59da-4f33-8440-d01ae62047f8_910576184", "cb0c3f18-a020-4791-a2ac-9a74a11514b5_356931984", "5efbdc36-5d1f-41e3-8eb4-65a5c1891d84_484451435", "1898ccb2-a289-4b8c-b712-f9c1a8916fb4_123956340", "5b6c419c-56c6-4df3-9cca-e0097a73f5c0_194988493", "6e47a5cf-47a7-42a3-812e-ef81ba1e7a5f_46222320", "e74577b4-c6c3-4f44-a4a1-5de7aec14182_714973940", "234c0ac8-224a-4ae9-b9fc-df4652c033eb_450387180", "7614d155-5beb-49f4-b13a-4f2675a1d6c8_866557951", "fb92792f-3080-493c-a89a-094846f8e782_863632919", "0e11d42f-a5b1-4bbb-b585-84e3274a7239_534772390", "f61994b0-dc34-40d6-a1e2-a7f66b22774b_548175167", "f25532ee-612b-4201-9398-777633fc3a59_1051356406", "69b8fd94-1cb6-4670-b3d5-2fd1662a06a1_305047613", "7b4bbaf5-e66c-4dcf-a295-a8c7b4c95565_144354483", "0a23f98b-5107-4cce-91a8-481591d1a7a6_853260936", "caae83a2-6127-4218-92b9-5cdc25849462_904914359", "f0932c14-bf26-4a29-a8e3-cbacb4a1a279_599324161"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "attract", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1017", "run_id": "attract-biological"}, "responses": [{"text": "Disney has been producing live-action remakes of classic animated films, including Cinderella, The Jungle Book, and others, to adapt timeless stories for contemporary audiences.", "citations": {"2b7b6721-9b08-432c-b318-1f57bf8a8139_226946838": 1.0}}, {"text": "The company's decision to produce remakes is driven by nostalgia, financial success, and a desire to update classics for modern audiences.", "citations": {"4f066135-2b16-40d4-b7e2-53d7b2c13378_369931830": 1.0}}, {"text": "Nostalgia drives Disney's decisions, as they capitalize on fond memories of older audiences and introduce classics to new generations.", "citations": {"4f066135-2b16-40d4-b7e2-53d7b2c13378_369931830": 1.0}}, {"text": "The live-action remakes have introduced changes, including new characters, plot twists, and modern themes, to appeal to contemporary audiences.", "citations": {"7f460acf-43fa-4323-886b-7ace4ae531c6_350718074": 1.0}}, {"text": "Disney balances nostalgia with fresh storytelling by incorporating classic characters into new storylines.", "citations": {"4036b750-2ab7-4ad1-9c53-26b176baf9f8_268887610": 1.0}}, {"text": "The company uses hidden Easter Eggs to make remakes appealing to both old and new fans.", "citations": {"4036b750-2ab7-4ad1-9c53-26b176baf9f8_268887610": 1.0}}, {"text": "Disney updates characters, settings, and themes to appeal to modern audiences while keeping the original stories' core elements.", "citations": {"4f066135-2b16-40d4-b7e2-53d7b2c13378_369931830": 1.0}}, {"text": "Some critics argue that the remakes prioritize nostalgia over storytelling, with John Musk suggesting Disney should focus on entertainment over concepts.", "citations": {"9bf4d61e-80c6-417e-8c40-6d987236d4fb_1002818262": 1.0}}, {"text": "The public reaction to the adaptations has been mixed, with some appreciating the updates and others missing the originals' magic.", "citations": {"9bf4d61e-80c6-417e-8c40-6d987236d4fb_1002818262": 1.0}}, {"text": "The remakes have been criticized for lacking the original's charm and relying too heavily on special effects over storytelling.", "citations": {"a46ff8d5-65d2-4767-bbbd-744e15e266f1_655286817": 1.0}}, {"text": "Disney's live-action remakes aim to balance nostalgia for older audiences with introduction to new generations, achieving varying success.", "citations": {"4f066135-2b16-40d4-b7e2-53d7b2c13378_369931830": 1.0}}, {"text": "The company's use of nostalgia has successfully appealed to older audiences familiar with the original films.", "citations": {"d8e024e0-ebe0-4e2a-92a9-debca6d24c2e_1011401893": 1.0}}, {"text": "Disney plans to release live-action remakes of The Little Mermaid and Peter Pan in the coming years.", "citations": {"b6f37f43-db4b-4ec1-979e-79dc640021ee_932228249": 1.0}}, {"text": "The success of these remakes depends on Disney's ability to balance appeal to new audiences with faithfulness to the originals.", "citations": {"ea377c05-0dd4-4101-9f45-e8bc8a306035_752351010": 1.0}}, {"text": "Disney's live-action remakes will remain a key part of the company's strategy and a major force in the film industry for years to come.", "citations": {"f2ef50c0-4817-4aae-bd18-4208e7c369cb_452895435": 1.0}}], "references": ["4f066135-2b16-40d4-b7e2-53d7b2c13378_369931830", "4036b750-2ab7-4ad1-9c53-26b176baf9f8_268887610", "9bf4d61e-80c6-417e-8c40-6d987236d4fb_1002818262", "a46ff8d5-65d2-4767-bbbd-744e15e266f1_655286817", "b6f37f43-db4b-4ec1-979e-79dc640021ee_932228249", "7f460acf-43fa-4323-886b-7ace4ae531c6_350718074", "d8e024e0-ebe0-4e2a-92a9-debca6d24c2e_1011401893", "2b7b6721-9b08-432c-b318-1f57bf8a8139_226946838", "ea377c05-0dd4-4101-9f45-e8bc8a306035_752351010", "f2ef50c0-4817-4aae-bd18-4208e7c369cb_452895435"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "attract", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1018", "run_id": "attract-biological"}, "responses": [{"text": "Disney has been producing live-action remakes of their classic animated films in recent years, including Cinderella, The Jungle Book, Beauty and the Beast, Dumbo, Aladdin, The Lion King, Mulan, Pinocchio, and Little Mermaid, with the goal of introducing the stories and characters to a new generation of viewers while also appealing to nostalgic fans of the originals.", "citations": {"4f066135-2b16-40d4-b7e2-53d7b2c13378_369931830": 1.0}}, {"text": "The company's decision to produce these remakes is driven in part by a desire to capitalize on nostalgia for the original films, as well as to create new and innovative storytelling experiences for modern audiences.", "citations": {"7f460acf-43fa-4323-886b-7ace4ae531c6_350718074": 1.0}}, {"text": "The live-action remakes often feature realistic animation and live-action, with updates to the original stories and characters, such as the addition of LGBT characters, and have received mixed reactions from the public, with some praising the new interpretations and others criticizing the changes to the original stories and characters.", "citations": {"7f460acf-43fa-4323-886b-7ace4ae531c6_350718074": 1.0}}, {"text": "Disney's live-action remakes have been successful in adapting timeless stories for modern audiences, with changes made to the original stories and characters, such as adding more realistic characters, female characters, and tougher scenes, as seen in The Jungle Book 2016 remake.", "citations": {"7f460acf-43fa-4323-886b-7ace4ae531c6_350718074": 1.0}}, {"text": "The company's commitment to diversity and inclusion is also evident in its live-action remakes, with films like The Little Mermaid featuring a black actress, Halle Bailey, in the lead role, and Snow White featuring a Latina actress, Rachel Zegler, in the title role.", "citations": {"08bf5561-f112-47d8-ae82-2041a9b4fc15_814052845": 1.0}}, {"text": "The live-action remakes have been adapted to contemporary realia, with changes made to the original stories and characters to reflect modern values and sensibilities, such as the inclusion of new characters, plot twists, and social commentary.", "citations": {"7f460acf-43fa-4323-886b-7ace4ae531c6_350718074": 1.0}}, {"text": "The use of nostalgic elements in live-action remakes has been a key factor in their financial success, with films like Beauty and the Beast and Aladdin grossing over $1 billion worldwide.", "citations": {"affa62b6-3681-4651-bd81-70d2425e5fae_433916494": 1.0}}, {"text": "The company's strategy of incorporating nostalgic elements into their live-action remakes is driven by the desire to attract both old and new audiences, with the company reproducing classics to ensure financial success.", "citations": {"4f066135-2b16-40d4-b7e2-53d7b2c13378_369931830": 1.0}}, {"text": "The live-action remakes have received mixed reviews from critics, with some films receiving critical acclaim, such as The Jungle Book, which won an Oscar for Visual Effects, while others have received negative reviews, such as the live-action Pinocchio, which received 27% on Rotten Tomatoes.", "citations": {"7f460acf-43fa-4323-886b-7ace4ae531c6_350718074": 1.0, "a46ff8d5-65d2-4767-bbbd-744e15e266f1_655286817": 0.5}}, {"text": "Despite the mixed reactions, Disney continues to produce live-action remakes of their animated classics, with the company finalizing the script for the live-action Hercules remake and planning to release a live-action Mufasa film in 2024.", "citations": {"4f066135-2b16-40d4-b7e2-53d7b2c13378_369931830": 1.0, "c5f26e63-75b5-48b1-9501-c8ee23be61f2_694539873": 0.5}}, {"text": "The production costs of live-action remakes can be high, with big-budget adaptations like Beauty and the Beast requiring significant investments in visual effects and production design.", "citations": {"b0cdad92-634f-4d6e-b764-f694603e164e_943700962": 1.0}}, {"text": "The use of CGI and other technologies has also allowed Disney to create more realistic and detailed environments and characters, which has helped to enhance the overall viewing experience.", "citations": {"7f460acf-43fa-4323-886b-7ace4ae531c6_350718074": 1.0}}, {"text": "The company's commitment to creating inclusive and diverse stories has also been reflected in its casting decisions, such as the choice of Yara Shahidi to play Tinker Bell in the upcoming remake of Peter Pan.", "citations": {"e0351793-b3d1-488b-9cfb-84d9ec00c54f_579640465": 1.0}}, {"text": "The reaction of the public to these remakes has been mixed, with some viewers praising the company's efforts to increase diversity and representation, while others have criticized the changes made to the original stories and characters.", "citations": {"b78e3040-8d67-4e6a-a1c6-a71459ab2824_66087799": 1.0}}, {"text": "Overall, Disney's live-action remakes of their classic animated films represent a complex and multifaceted attempt to balance authenticity and relevance with diversity and inclusion, and the company's efforts in this area are likely to continue to be the subject of debate and discussion in the years to come.", "citations": {"bdddcb95-f6a7-4001-b07d-c74d32a56f6e_1012056560": 1.0}}, {"text": "The key performance indicators used by Disney to measure the success of their live-action remakes include box office performance, with The Little Mermaid expected to generate $104 million over the weekend.", "citations": {"c7e579e6-3738-495f-b411-43f31a0e8d23_584006662": 1.0}}, {"text": "The global debut of The Little Mermaid is expected to be over $200 million, with overseas markets being a significant contributor to global revenue.", "citations": {"c7e579e6-3738-495f-b411-43f31a0e8d23_584006662": 1.0}}, {"text": "The success of Disney's live-action remakes is also driven by their ability to evoke childhood memories and drive viewership, with The Little Mermaid being a favorite among older women and men.", "citations": {"4b7b2e66-ee70-426e-b6b1-ebfd29dca20b_59301776": 1.0}}, {"text": "Disney aims to create an artistic epic or film series with their live-action remakes, such as The Lion King, which explores universal themes like love and life.", "citations": {"4f066135-2b16-40d4-b7e2-53d7b2c13378_369931830": 1.0}}, {"text": "The company's live-action remakes have received positive reviews, with The Little Mermaid having a 67% rating on Rotten Tomatoes.", "citations": {"c7e579e6-3738-495f-b411-43f31a0e8d23_584006662": 1.0}}, {"text": "The role of nostalgia in driving financial profits for Disney's live-action remakes is significant, as it allows the company to tap into the nostalgia of older audiences while also attracting new fans.", "citations": {"4b7b2e66-ee70-426e-b6b1-ebfd29dca20b_59301776": 1.0}}, {"text": "The live-action remakes of Disney's classic animated films have been adapted to the contemporary realia, with changes made to the original stories and characters to appeal to modern audiences.", "citations": {"4f066135-2b16-40d4-b7e2-53d7b2c13378_369931830": 1.0}}, {"text": "The use of nostalgic elements in live-action remakes has been successful in driving the company's decisions, with the goal of creating a sense of familiarity and nostalgia among audiences.", "citations": {"b0cdad92-634f-4d6e-b764-f694603e164e_943700962": 1.0}}, {"text": "The company's commitment to turning their animated catalog into live-action films is expected to continue in the future, with new remakes and sequels in development.", "citations": {"b0cdad92-634f-4d6e-b764-f694603e164e_943700962": 1.0}}, {"text": "The live-action remakes have been successful in adapting timeless stories for modern audiences, with changes made to the original stories and characters to reflect modern values and sensibilities.", "citations": {"7f460acf-43fa-4323-886b-7ace4ae531c6_350718074": 1.0}}, {"text": "The production costs of live-action remakes can be significant, with some films costing over $250 million to produce, but the revenue generated from various streams makes them profitable for Disney.", "citations": {"c4db539d-2500-4014-851f-589cfa76e055_393116507": 1.0}}, {"text": "Disney considers multiple revenue streams for their live-action remakes, including box office gross, merchandising, home video sales, and streaming revenue, to determine their overall financial performance.", "citations": {"b78e3040-8d67-4e6a-a1c6-a71459ab2824_241773455": 1.0}}, {"text": "The company's decision to produce live-action remakes is driven by the desire to recreate classic stories and characters for new audiences, while also generating significant revenue from various streams.", "citations": {"4b7b2e66-ee70-426e-b6b1-ebfd29dca20b_59301776": 1.0}}, {"text": "Nostalgia plays a significant role in driving Disney's decisions to produce live-action remakes, as the company aims to tap into the nostalgic value of their classic animated films.", "citations": {"4b7b2e66-ee70-426e-b6b1-ebfd29dca20b_59301776": 1.0}}, {"text": "The public reaction to the live-action remakes has been generally positive, with many fans appreciating the nostalgic value and the introduction of classic stories to new audiences.", "citations": {"2fb45285-061a-49a7-b46b-202e68873010_493023833": 1.0}}, {"text": "However, some remakes have faced criticism, such as the \"Haunted Mansion\" remake, which lost money at the box office, but still contributed to the popularity of park projects.", "citations": {"b78e3040-8d67-4e6a-a1c6-a71459ab2824_241773455": 1.0}}, {"text": "Overall, Disney's live-action remakes have been a commercial success, generating significant revenue from various streams and appealing to both old and new audiences.", "citations": {"8a9df4e3-7853-4595-8d6a-57e31dace6a1_812527426": 1.0}}], "references": ["4f066135-2b16-40d4-b7e2-53d7b2c13378_369931830", "b78e3040-8d67-4e6a-a1c6-a71459ab2824_241773455", "2fb45285-061a-49a7-b46b-202e68873010_493023833", "b78e3040-8d67-4e6a-a1c6-a71459ab2824_66087799", "08bf5561-f112-47d8-ae82-2041a9b4fc15_814052845", "bdddcb95-f6a7-4001-b07d-c74d32a56f6e_1012056560", "affa62b6-3681-4651-bd81-70d2425e5fae_433916494", "8a9df4e3-7853-4595-8d6a-57e31dace6a1_812527426", "7f460acf-43fa-4323-886b-7ace4ae531c6_350718074", "c7e579e6-3738-495f-b411-43f31a0e8d23_584006662", "c5f26e63-75b5-48b1-9501-c8ee23be61f2_694539873", "b0cdad92-634f-4d6e-b764-f694603e164e_943700962", "4b7b2e66-ee70-426e-b6b1-ebfd29dca20b_59301776", "e0351793-b3d1-488b-9cfb-84d9ec00c54f_579640465", "a46ff8d5-65d2-4767-bbbd-744e15e266f1_655286817", "c4db539d-2500-4014-851f-589cfa76e055_393116507"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "attract", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1019", "run_id": "attract-biological"}, "responses": [{"text": "Tai Chi improves balance and reduces the risk of falls in older adults.", "citations": {"2e864b6f-2e85-4876-845a-6831478b1237_437053624": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi alleviates degenerative arthritis symptoms, improves lung function in COPD patients, and enhances balance and mobility in those with Parkinson's disease.", "citations": {"2e864b6f-2e85-4876-845a-6831478b1237_437053624": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi can improve cognitive function, help dementia patients, and benefit people of all ages, particularly older adults.", "citations": {"2e864b6f-2e85-4876-845a-6831478b1237_437053624": 1.0}}, {"text": "Older adults can learn Tai Chi through adapted classes at community centers or at home with online guidance or mobile apps.", "citations": {"07e86353-4df1-47dd-8ddd-a2c4d7b73d7d_327853608": 1.0}}, {"text": "Caregivers can support older adults practicing Tai Chi by finding qualified instructors, creating a safe environment, and providing encouragement.", "citations": {"cf237750-b384-48ad-85be-e9e241319e81_464746224": 1.0}}, {"text": "Regular Tai Chi practice, 2-3 times a week, can improve balance, reduce falls, and enhance overall health in older adults.", "citations": {"41541b00-f7b4-4a15-8ec7-2d7431c26695_263273629": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi can be modified to suit individual needs, making it accessible and effective for improving balance and reducing fall risk in older adults.", "citations": {"5c1162ae-4b10-4556-b59e-5a30440f6c83_159992918": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi enhances flexibility and calmness, reducing fall risk and improving wellbeing, and can be combined with exercises like walking or swimming for a comprehensive program.", "citations": {"b387b7e2-f045-452b-8758-c89e0f69c760_775838414": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi is a safe and effective way to improve balance and reduce falls in older adults.", "citations": {"2e864b6f-2e85-4876-845a-6831478b1237_437053624": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi is accessible to older adults with mobility issues and can be modified to suit different ages and abilities.", "citations": {"31918ed2-62bc-4739-8e23-6eefc0cb0d67_37632800": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi reduces waist circumference, improves metabolic health, and lowers the risk of type 2 diabetes and cardiovascular disease.", "citations": {"41541b00-f7b4-4a15-8ec7-2d7431c26695_263273629": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi is a low-impact exercise suitable for all ages that improves balance, reduces fall risk, and enhances overall health.", "citations": {"2e864b6f-2e85-4876-845a-6831478b1237_437053624": 1.0}}, {"text": "Regular Tai Chi practice can be incorporated into daily routine to sustain its benefits and improve overall health and wellbeing.", "citations": {"41541b00-f7b4-4a15-8ec7-2d7431c26695_263273629": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi can be practiced in a group or at home with online guidance, making it a convenient exercise option for older adults.", "citations": {"07e86353-4df1-47dd-8ddd-a2c4d7b73d7d_327853608": 1.0}}], "references": ["31918ed2-62bc-4739-8e23-6eefc0cb0d67_37632800", "5c1162ae-4b10-4556-b59e-5a30440f6c83_159992918", "41541b00-f7b4-4a15-8ec7-2d7431c26695_263273629", "2e864b6f-2e85-4876-845a-6831478b1237_437053624", "07e86353-4df1-47dd-8ddd-a2c4d7b73d7d_327853608", "cf237750-b384-48ad-85be-e9e241319e81_464746224", "b387b7e2-f045-452b-8758-c89e0f69c760_775838414"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "attract", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1020", "run_id": "attract-biological"}, "responses": [{"text": "Tai Chi is a traditional Chinese martial art that has been shown to improve balance and reduce the risk of falls in older adults, making it a valuable exercise for this demographic.", "citations": {"2e864b6f-2e85-4876-845a-6831478b1237_437053624": 1.0}}, {"text": "The practice of Tai Chi combines physical movement, breathing techniques, and meditation to promote relaxation, balance, and overall well-being, which can be beneficial for older adults with mobility issues.", "citations": {"2e864b6f-2e85-4876-845a-6831478b1237_437053624": 1.0}}, {"text": "Regular Tai Chi practice has been found to reduce the risk of falls in older adults by improving balance, strength, and flexibility, as well as enhancing cognitive function and reducing the risk of chronic diseases.", "citations": {"184485a7-25df-4efa-b2f3-f28ae72d25e3_199781782": 1.0, "2e864b6f-2e85-4876-845a-6831478b1237_437053624": 0.5}}, {"text": "Tai Chi has also been shown to improve cardiovascular health, reduce blood pressure, and enhance immune function, making it a comprehensive exercise program for older adults.", "citations": {"41541b00-f7b4-4a15-8ec7-2d7431c26695_263273629": 1.0, "b387b7e2-f045-452b-8758-c89e0f69c760_775838414": 0.5}}, {"text": "In addition to its physical benefits, Tai Chi has also been found to have a positive impact on mental health, reducing stress, anxiety, and depression, and improving overall quality of life.", "citations": {"2e864b6f-2e85-4876-845a-6831478b1237_437053624": 1.0, "b387b7e2-f045-452b-8758-c89e0f69c760_775838414": 0.5}}, {"text": "The cost-effectiveness of Tai Chi as a fall prevention strategy is not well-documented, but it is known that falls have a high economic cost, and reducing falls through exercise programs like Tai Chi could lead to potential cost savings.", "citations": {"b5deff92-79ef-4228-bd4b-4f3b4f16fac9_3509450": 1.0}}, {"text": "To promote and sustain Tai Chi programs in community settings, it is essential to develop effective marketing strategies, partnerships with local organizations, and collaborations with healthcare providers and insurance companies.", "citations": {"46aac298-47e3-40c4-b112-cf04be57240a_846751787": 1.0, "4c83d72d-b7dc-4abe-8e29-a7bcab3394b1_692759984": 0.5, "562e6db7-0c75-42e7-954d-def9d02d9fd3_190965873": 0.25}}, {"text": "Tai Chi programs can be tailored to meet the specific needs and abilities of older adults with varying levels of mobility and health status, and can be modified to accommodate different health conditions, such as arthritis, Parkinson's disease, and chronic obstructive pulmonary disease.", "citations": {"5c1162ae-4b10-4556-b59e-5a30440f6c83_159992918": 1.0, "6bb86295-c49b-4797-ab4b-5652344f2d4a_686292122": 0.5, "31918ed2-62bc-4739-8e23-6eefc0cb0d67_37632800": 0.25}}, {"text": "The ideal class size for a Tai Chi program is around 20 participants, and instructor qualifications, such as being a certified Tai Chi instructor or having a martial arts black belt, are crucial for leading an effective program.", "citations": {"21b2b9d7-7acb-4f63-8d6c-9e8c7ffc0238_985396261": 1.0, "147a9a55-ed1d-4db8-8c3d-da71f65b9d64_869443431": 0.5, "8138d416-ceaa-43d3-a92d-7ad903317f2b_135477836": 0.25}}, {"text": "Participant engagement strategies, such as step-by-step instructions, practice, and socializing, are vital for maintaining interest and ensuring participants benefit from the program.", "citations": {"147a9a55-ed1d-4db8-8c3d-da71f65b9d64_869443431": 1.0, "46aac298-47e3-40c4-b112-cf04be57240a_846751787": 0.5, "a57e582a-7ccb-4b99-8b52-28541cee9200_951382897": 0.25}}, {"text": "The duration and frequency of Tai Chi sessions can vary, but typical sessions are 1 hour long, held 3 times a week, with a course lasting 12 weeks.", "citations": {"41541b00-f7b4-4a15-8ec7-2d7431c26695_263273629": 1.0, "8138d416-ceaa-43d3-a92d-7ad903317f2b_135477836": 0.5}}, {"text": "Tai Chi can be practiced in various settings, including community centers, parks, and at home, making it a convenient and accessible exercise program for older adults.", "citations": {"562e6db7-0c75-42e7-954d-def9d02d9fd3_190965873": 1.0, "1a1b9bfd-2e52-474d-b03d-4eaecf6c5453_427589468": 0.5, "5c1162ae-4b10-4556-b59e-5a30440f6c83_159992918": 0.25}}, {"text": "Overall, Tai Chi is a low-impact, cost-effective exercise program that can be beneficial for older adults, improving balance, strength, flexibility, and overall well-being, while also reducing the risk of falls and chronic diseases.", "citations": {"2e864b6f-2e85-4876-845a-6831478b1237_437053624": 1.0, "b387b7e2-f045-452b-8758-c89e0f69c760_775838414": 0.5, "f3f6c566-9c4f-4d07-a262-9f6ef4ef8f69_83051545": 0.25}}], "references": ["2e864b6f-2e85-4876-845a-6831478b1237_437053624", "a57e582a-7ccb-4b99-8b52-28541cee9200_951382897", "b387b7e2-f045-452b-8758-c89e0f69c760_775838414", "562e6db7-0c75-42e7-954d-def9d02d9fd3_190965873", "21b2b9d7-7acb-4f63-8d6c-9e8c7ffc0238_985396261", "b5deff92-79ef-4228-bd4b-4f3b4f16fac9_3509450", "5c1162ae-4b10-4556-b59e-5a30440f6c83_159992918", "147a9a55-ed1d-4db8-8c3d-da71f65b9d64_869443431", "8138d416-ceaa-43d3-a92d-7ad903317f2b_135477836", "f3f6c566-9c4f-4d07-a262-9f6ef4ef8f69_83051545", "31918ed2-62bc-4739-8e23-6eefc0cb0d67_37632800", "4c83d72d-b7dc-4abe-8e29-a7bcab3394b1_692759984", "41541b00-f7b4-4a15-8ec7-2d7431c26695_263273629", "6bb86295-c49b-4797-ab4b-5652344f2d4a_686292122", "1a1b9bfd-2e52-474d-b03d-4eaecf6c5453_427589468", "46aac298-47e3-40c4-b112-cf04be57240a_846751787", "184485a7-25df-4efa-b2f3-f28ae72d25e3_199781782"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "attract", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1021", "run_id": "attract-biological"}, "responses": [{"text": "Tai Chi improves mobility and prevents falls in older adults by enhancing balance, strength, and flexibility.", "citations": {"0f5cd105-7572-4a55-9c42-607d1c65be3d_663764653": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi gently stimulates muscles, tendons, joints, and bones, relieving intervertebral disc pressure and positively affecting the nervous system.", "citations": {"2e864b6f-2e85-4876-845a-6831478b1237_437053624": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi is suitable for older adults with various health conditions, including diabetes, heart disease, and arthritis.", "citations": {"0f5cd105-7572-4a55-9c42-607d1c65be3d_663764653": 1.0}}, {"text": "Practicing Tai Chi at least three times a week for 12 weeks can improve balance, mobility, and overall health, reducing the risk of falls and related injuries.", "citations": {"41541b00-f7b4-4a15-8ec7-2d7431c26695_263273629": 1.0}}, {"text": "The World Health Organization recommends 150-300 minutes of moderate-intensity aerobic exercise, such as Tai Chi, per week for adults over 65.", "citations": {"4502ea6b-f423-4f08-b3e9-2c45e7a80185_337609787": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi improves balance, reduces fall risk, and offers various health benefits in older adults.", "citations": {"2e864b6f-2e85-4876-845a-6831478b1237_437053624": 1.0}}, {"text": "Individuals with conditions like osteoporosis, diabetes, or COPD should consult their doctor before starting Tai Chi to avoid injury.", "citations": {"13b98add-9f70-4376-9cea-bc8dd786e2c9_337644403": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi can cause strain or injury, especially for those with poor stability, and should be practiced with caution under a qualified instructor's guidance.", "citations": {"13b98add-9f70-4376-9cea-bc8dd786e2c9_337644403": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi has physical and mental health benefits, reducing stress and anxiety while improving overall well-being.", "citations": {"2e864b6f-2e85-4876-845a-6831478b1237_437053624": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi can be adapted to accommodate individuals with mobility issues or limitations.", "citations": {"14b74b2e-eb4c-4316-a13f-2b94ab1cae1a_760925045": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi practice improves strength, balance, and coordination, reducing the risk of falls and injuries, making it valuable for older adults.", "citations": {"8138d416-ceaa-43d3-a92d-7ad903317f2b_135477836": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi instructors can provide guidance on proper technique and modifications, helping participants improve balance and prevent falls.", "citations": {"147a9a55-ed1d-4db8-8c3d-da71f65b9d64_869443431": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi reduces fall risk and alleviates arthritis symptoms in older adults, while also improving lung function, balance, and cognitive brain function.", "citations": {"2e864b6f-2e85-4876-845a-6831478b1237_437053624": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi is a low-impact exercise suitable for older adults with various health conditions or mobility levels.", "citations": {"0f5cd105-7572-4a55-9c42-607d1c65be3d_663764653": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi is a safe and effective exercise option for older adults that can be adapted to meet individual needs.", "citations": {"41541b00-f7b4-4a15-8ec7-2d7431c26695_263273629": 1.0}}], "references": ["0f5cd105-7572-4a55-9c42-607d1c65be3d_663764653", "4502ea6b-f423-4f08-b3e9-2c45e7a80185_337609787", "14b74b2e-eb4c-4316-a13f-2b94ab1cae1a_760925045", "2e864b6f-2e85-4876-845a-6831478b1237_437053624", "13b98add-9f70-4376-9cea-bc8dd786e2c9_337644403", "147a9a55-ed1d-4db8-8c3d-da71f65b9d64_869443431", "41541b00-f7b4-4a15-8ec7-2d7431c26695_263273629", "8138d416-ceaa-43d3-a92d-7ad903317f2b_135477836"]}
