{"metadata": {"team_id": "attract", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1023", "run_id": "attract-biological"}, "responses": [{"text": "The global aerospace market is expected to grow significantly over the next two decades, driven by demand for fuel-efficient aircraft and sustainable aviation solutions.", "citations": {"bf2732d0-bb7b-4e55-9d35-f1d548672746_296106203": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Asia Pacific region is expected to drive global aircraft demand, with China's passenger share expected to grow to 20% by 2040.", "citations": {"bf2732d0-bb7b-4e55-9d35-f1d548672746_296106203": 1.0}}, {"text": "Global demand for new aircraft is expected to reach 43,610 by 2040, led by North America at 9,160.", "citations": {"bf2732d0-bb7b-4e55-9d35-f1d548672746_296106203": 1.0}}, {"text": "75% of new aircraft deliveries are expected to be single-aisle aircraft, driven by size and flexibility.", "citations": {"bf2732d0-bb7b-4e55-9d35-f1d548672746_296106203": 1.0}}, {"text": "The global civil aviation fleet is expected to exceed 49,000 by 2040, with 21% based in the Asia Pacific region.", "citations": {"bf2732d0-bb7b-4e55-9d35-f1d548672746_296106203": 1.0}}, {"text": "The aerospace industry is shifting towards efficiency and sustainability through investments in sustainable fuels and electric propulsion.", "citations": {"58cb9ae7-c967-4d94-9059-9765953b9d81_31367334": 1.0}}, {"text": "Sustainable aviation fuels can cut carbon emissions by up to 80%, but are currently more expensive than traditional fuels.", "citations": {"1576b471-6582-4657-8b4f-795ce9cbaf69_166577778": 1.0}}, {"text": "Electric and hybrid-electric propulsion systems are expected to reduce emissions and costs, with companies like Zunum Aero and Boeing investing in them.", "citations": {"00ac3a93-3310-4f70-9268-f04353c61fc3_623414700": 1.0}}, {"text": "The global Hybrid Electric Jet market is expected to reach US$ millions by 2028, with its batteries segment also reaching $ million by then.", "citations": {"00ac3a93-