{"metadata": {"team_id": "attract", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1024", "run_id": "attract-biological"}, "responses": [{"text": "The global aerospace market is expected to grow significantly, driven by increasing air travel demand and the need for more efficient aircraft.", "citations": {}}, {"text": "Boeing and Airbus dominate the market and are expected to continue doing so over the next decade.", "citations": {"81bd4ecf-6dcf-4408-a784-42cc345a06ed_699091290": 1.0}}, {"text": "COMAC and others are expected to challenge their market share, especially in Asia.", "citations": {"c5d75a84-d3a1-42ee-8060-9f572c2be0e4_722279503": 1.0}}, {"text": "The demand for fuel-efficient aircraft is driving innovation, with companies like Boeing and Airbus investing in electric and hybrid-electric propulsion systems.", "citations": {"00ac3a93-3310-4f70-9268-f04353c61fc3_623414700": 1.0}}, {"text": "Airbus and Boeing aim to achieve net-zero emissions by 2050 through sustainable aviation fuel.", "citations": {"a7b3981c-68e9-4d1d-9996-256dff4462eb_936719364": 1.0}}, {"text": "Regional market dynamics, driven by countries like China and the UAE, will shape the aerospace market's future.", "citations": {"24b5190a-056e-412e-8f76-cf3223f6d336_725979455": 1.0, "a7336eac-d6ec-4395-bf8a-45c5613cec04_692382941": 0.5}}, {"text": "The Asia-Pacific region and China are expected to account for 42% of new fleet deliveries.", "citations": {"5867527f-48e2-4543-921b-79edad641fbf_807412611": 1.0}}, {"text": "The aerospace market will be driven by trends like sustainable aviation fuel, zero-emission aircraft, and eco-friendly technologies.", "citations": {"29b7e07e-b2eb-4301-9415-f8454de03031_418809617": 1.0}}, {"text": "The aviation industry is shifting towards greater efficiency and sustainability.", "citations": {"b13e4fc9-7c80-4b39-bd16-cad6374c2e50_1047343470": 1.0}}, {"text": "Aircraft manufacturers are incorporating electric and hybrid-electric propulsion to reduce emissions and improve efficiency.", "citations": {"00580580-2d22-4655-a113-539c80fc105d_1072121227": 1.0}}, {"text": "Investing in these technologies is likely to give aircraft manufacturers a competitive advantage.", "citations": {"00580580-2d22-4655-a113-539c80fc105d_1072121227": 1.0}}, {"text": "The EU's 2050 carbon neutral target is driving the aviation industry to develop more fuel-efficient aircraft.", "citations": {"7fd4f4a0-d06e-4faa-abeb-fc116cab0fe5_679484596": 1.0}}, {"text": "Airbus and Boeing's strategic moves will impact their competitiveness in the next decade, with sustainability and innovation being key.", "citations": {"29b7e07e-b2eb-4301-9415-f8454de03031_418809617": 1.0, "daf4c75c-3870-4467-9566-86868603f4ff_388897130": 0.5}}, {"text": "The aerospace market is expected to experience significant growth, driven by demand for sustainable aircraft and changing regulatory requirements.", "citations": {"29b7e07e-b2eb-4301-9415-f8454de03031_418809617": 1.0}}, {"text": "New wing designs, like the Transonic Truss-Braced Wing, aim to improve fuel efficiency and reduce emissions in commercial aircraft.", "citations": {"0bc02225-e196-4709-9403-0a56d936838a_421120779": 1.0}}, {"text": "NASA plans to develop a transonic trussed-braced wing to cut emissions by 30%.", "citations": {"15aabe9c-37fd-46a4-b12c-2e8e0a1ab3c5_1046511097": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Transonic Truss-Braced Wing design reduces fuel consumption and emissions by up to 30%.", "citations": {"1b16c8de-abe9-4d6a-be29-aef8920c0e7e_870572865": 1.0}}, {"text": "Using eco-fuel and sustainable aviation fuel will reduce emissions and costs, but requires significant investment and government support.", "citations": {"1c10a75f-dd16-423a-bd82-eb5f51e92f88_311269111": 1.0}}, {"text": "Sustainable fuel is currently more expensive, but its cost is expected to equalize with traditional fuel by 2035.", "citations": {"24fc3cb2-c7d9-495f-bdbe-db8bcfdf618d_421443222": 1.0}}, {"text": "The EU is investing 2 billion euros to support the adoption of fuel-efficient aircraft, which will reduce carbon emissions and operating costs.", "citations": {"1c10a75f-dd16-423a-bd82-eb5f51e92f88_311269111": 1.0}}, {"text": "The return on investment and payback periods for fuel-efficient aircraft depend on factors like fuel prices, operating costs, and aircraft cost.", "citations": {"24fc3cb2-c7d9-495f-bdbe-db8bcfdf618d_421443222": 1.0}}, {"text": "A cost-benefit analysis of fuel-efficient aircraft will determine the strategic moves of major manufacturers and the aerospace market's future.", "citations": {"65a6d821-4ded-4ba5-874a-2aa5ee48ba5e_72581204": 1.0}}, {"text": "The global aerospace market is expected to see significant growth, with 45,000 fuel-efficient aircraft worth $2.9 trillion to be delivered by 2040.", "citations": {"65a6d821-4ded-4ba5-874a-2aa5ee48ba5e_72581204": 1.0}}, {"text": "China is expected to lead aircraft demand with a 20% share of deliveries.", "citations": {"65a6d821-4ded-4ba5-874a-2aa5ee48ba5e_72581204": 1.0}}, {"text": "The industry expects 3.7% annual growth in air passenger traffic, requiring 22,000 new aircraft.", "citations": {"65a6d821-4ded-4ba5-874a-2aa5ee48ba5e_72581204": 1.0}}, {"text": "The strategic moves of major manufacturers like Boeing and Airbus will be critical in determining their market position.", "citations": {"50685a27-77f5-434a-b697-8a74ca52028a_20945242": 1.0}}, {"text": "Sustainable aviation fuel and fuel-efficient aircraft will drive aerospace market growth.", "citations": {"3f642ac3-60a8-4868-b7c8-714ed5d0a6c2_258894888": 1.0}}, {"text": "The aviation industry accounted for 2% of carbon exhaust in 2022, underscoring the need for sustainable fuels.", "citations": {"1576b471-6582-4657-8b4f-795ce9cbaf69_166577778": 1.0}}, {"text": "Decarbonization, necessary for carbon pricing, will be costly for industries like aviation.", "citations": {"0dff0ffb-7386-4cb8-be45-4701cd809c1d_640583255": 1.0}}, {"text": "Sustainable aviation fuel reduces emissions by up to 80% and is made from renewable materials.", "citations": {"1576b471-6582-4657-8b4f-795ce9cbaf69_166577778": 1.0, "c360e8e0-56b6-43c1-88d1-404432dedf25_3813035": 0.5}}, {"text": "Sustainable aviation fuel costs 2-4 times more than conventional fuel, increasing flight costs by 300,000 yuan with just a 10% blend.", "citations": {"24fc3cb2-c7d9-495f-bdbe-db8bcfdf618d_421443222": 1.0}}, {"text": "Sustainable fuel costs eight times more than regular fuel, posing a significant challenge for airlines.", "citations": {"833892cf-f345-4674-a75c-52170bad7e90_405374091": 1.0}}, {"text": "The EU targets 2% eco-fuel at airports by 2025, 6% by 2030, and 70% by 2050.", "citations": {"1c10a75f-dd16-423a-bd82-eb5f51e92f88_311269111": 1.0}}, {"text": "The US aims for 3 billion gallons of SAF use by 2030 to help airlines reduce their carbon footprint.", "citations": {"40a41541-e16a-4ec2-8f33-000537942ae0_397584368": 1.0}}, {"text": "ICAO will charge a fee for CO2 emissions on international flights from 2027, capping them at 2019 levels.", "citations": {"2ae00aaf-f17c-4884-b9eb-0f63faaf9227_534775916": 1.0}}, {"text": "Airlines may face $1.5-6 billion in annual emissions offset costs by 2025.", "citations": {"2ae00aaf-f17c-4884-b9eb-0f63faaf9227_534775916": 1.0}}, {"text": "Airlines will bear less burden as sustainable fuel prices are expected to match traditional fuel prices by 2035.", "citations": {"24fc3cb2-c7d9-495f-bdbe-db8bcfdf618d_421443222": 1.0}}, {"text": "The EU's revised carbon pricing may increase airline fares by \u20ac10 per round trip.", "citations": {"4fd296af-9478-4af6-860b-a0ab7eaadf9f_554907147": 1.0}}, {"text": "Air fares will rise due to sustainable aviation fuels and increasing carbon costs.", "citations": {"65a1e139-c35e-4006-acd5-c56430b2d3f5_290289202": 1.0}}, {"text": "Companies like Shell aim to mass-produce low-carbon jet fuel by 2025.", "citations": {"833892cf-f345-4674-a75c-52170bad7e90_405374091": 1.0}}, {"text": "The US Inflation Reduction Act provides tax relief to make sustainable aviation fuel more competitive.", "citations": {"c360e8e0-56b6-43c1-88d1-404432dedf25_3813035": 1.0, "f136a9aa-a757-4639-949a-e14aa35f1462_426481605": 0.5}}, {"text": "The aviation industry aims for net-zero carbon emissions by 2050, with companies like United Airlines investing in sustainable flight funds.", "citations": {"c360e8e0-56b6-43c1-88d1-404432dedf25_3813035": 1.0, "f136a9aa-a757-4639-949a-e14aa35f1462_426481605": 0.5}}, {"text": "The adoption of electric and hybrid-electric propulsion in commercial aircraft is promising, but reliability and safety are major concerns.", "citations": {"00580580-2d22-4655-a113-539c80fc105d_1072121227": 1.0}}, {"text": "Hybrid power plants and electric aircraft will be key discussion topics.", "citations": {"00580580-2d22-4655-a113-539c80fc105d_1072121227": 1.0}}, {"text": "Hybrid-electric jets can save fuel and reduce noise and emissions, with the global market valued at millions and projected to grow by 2028.", "citations": {"00ac3a93-3310-4f70-9268-f04353c61fc3_623414700": 1.0}}, {"text": "The market is expected to grow, with the US market estimated at millions in 2021 and China forecast to reach millions by 2028.", "citations": {"00ac3a93-3310-4f70-9268-f04353c61fc3_623414700": 1.0}}, {"text": "The top five battery players are expected to hold a significant revenue share by 2028.", "citations": {"00ac3a93-3310-4f70-9268-f04353c61fc3_623414700": 1.0}}, {"text": "Zunum Aero and Boeing HorizonX are driving the global market forward.", "citations": {"00ac3a93-3310-4f70-9268-f04353c61fc3_623414700": 1.0}}, {"text": "China aims to mainstream new energy aircraft by 2035, with interim goals set for 2025.", "citations": {"24b5190a-056e-412e-8f76-cf3223f6d336_725979455": 1.0}}, {"text": "Electric aircraft, including eVTOL, are expected to enter commercial use by 2025.", "citations": {"24b5190a-056e-412e-8f76-cf3223f6d336_725979455": 1.0}}, {"text": "Hydrogen energy aircraft are a key technology to be verified by 2025 for green aviation.", "citations": {"24b5190a-056e-412e-8f76-cf3223f6d336_725979455": 1.0}}, {"text": "By 2025, small aircraft will use electric propulsion, while trunk lines will adopt new pneumatic layouts and sustainable fuel.", "citations": {"24b5190a-056e-412e-8f76-cf3223f6d336_725979455": 1.0}}, {"text": "Collins Aerospace has developed a scalable 1MW electric motor-generator that delivers four times the power and twice the voltage.", "citations": {"3719f558-6468-455c-88ee-cf264ce78462_415293122": 1.0}}, {"text": "The motor will undergo flight testing in 2024 on a Dash 8-100 aircraft.", "citations": {"3719f558-6468-455c-88ee-cf264ce78462_415293122": 1.0}}, {"text": "Collins Aerospace has produced a 500 kilowatt electric motor prototype to power the Airlander 10, a hybrid-electric aircraft expected to operate in 2026.", "citations": {"3e13f82a-3311-41a4-90ee-843be2bee6dc_859341427": 1.0}}, {"text": "The motor will be used for hybrid-electric propulsion, aiming for net-zero carbon emissions by 2050.", "citations": {"3e13f82a-3311-41a4-90ee-843be2bee6dc_859341427": 1.0}}, {"text": "Global aviation produces 915 million tonnes of CO2 annually, and electric planes could cut operating costs by 80%.", "citations": {"ab2cc3e9-01c4-4096-8d87-226fa4f2b437_1027095428": 1.0}}, {"text": "Aviation accounts for 2.1% of human-induced CO2 emissions, targeting net-zero by 2050.", "citations": {"ab2cc3e9-01c4-4096-8d87-226fa4f2b437_1027095428": 1.0}}, {"text": "Electric planes face technical challenges, with smaller models possibly available in the 2030s.", "citations": {"ab2cc3e9-01c4-4096-8d87-226fa4f2b437_1027095428": 1.0}}, {"text": "Hybrid models can save 50-70% on fuel and 25-50% on maintenance, with around 170 electric aeroplane projects in development.", "citations": {"ab2cc3e9-01c4-4096-8d87-226fa4f2b437_1027095428": 1.0}}, {"text": "Ecological concerns are driving governments to set net-zero targets for militaries and civil aviation.", "citations": {"b4bbaecf-fdee-47ff-a0c7-689b9b4d8492_633043543": 1.0}}, {"text": "Military departments are interested in electric aircraft for lower costs.", "citations": {}}], "references": ["15aabe9c-37fd-46a4-b12c-2e8e0a1ab3c5_1046511097", "24b5190a-056e-412e-8f76-cf3223f6d336_725979455", "b4bbaecf-fdee-47ff-a0c7-689b9b4d8492_633043543", "2ae00aaf-f17c-4884-b9eb-0f63faaf9227_534775916", "65a1e139-c35e-4006-acd5-c56430b2d3f5_290289202", "c5d75a84-d3a1-42ee-8060-9f572c2be0e4_722279503", "4fd296af-9478-4af6-860b-a0ab7eaadf9f_554907147", "a7b3981c-68e9-4d1d-9996-256dff4462eb_936719364", "3719f558-6468-455c-88ee-cf264ce78462_415293122", "a7336eac-d6ec-4395-bf8a-45c5613cec04_692382941", "833892cf-f345-4674-a75c-52170bad7e90_405374091", "3e13f82a-3311-41a4-90ee-843be2bee6dc_859341427", "1576b471-6582-4657-8b4f-795ce9cbaf69_166577778", "1c10a75f-dd16-423a-bd82-eb5f51e92f88_311269111", "daf4c75c-3870-4467-9566-86868603f4ff_388897130", "65a6d821-4ded-4ba5-874a-2aa5ee48ba5e_72581204", "3f642ac3-60a8-4868-b7c8-714ed5d0a6c2_258894888", "ab2cc3e9-01c4-4096-8d87-226fa4f2b437_1027095428", "f136a9aa-a757-4639-949a-e14aa35f1462_426481605", "24fc3cb2-c7d9-495f-bdbe-db8bcfdf618d_421443222", "50685a27-77f5-434a-b697-8a74ca52028a_20945242", "0dff0ffb-7386-4cb8-be45-4701cd809c1d_640583255", "b13e4fc9-7c80-4b39-bd16-cad6374c2e50_1047343470", "0bc02225-e196-4709-9403-0a56d936838a_421120779", "c360e8e0-56b6-43c1-88d1-404432dedf25_3813035", "7fd4f4a0-d06e-4faa-abeb-fc116cab0fe5_679484596", "00ac3a93-3310-4f70-9268-f04353c61fc3_623414700", "81bd4ecf-6dcf-4408-a784-42cc345a06ed_699091290", "00580580-2d22-4655-a113-539c80fc105d_1072121227", "40a41541-e16a-4ec2-8f33-000537942ae0_397584368", "1b16c8de-abe9-4d6a-be29-aef8920c0e7e_870572865", "29b7e07e-b2eb-4301-9415-f8454de03031_418809617", "5867527f-48e2-4543-921b-79edad641fbf_807412611"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "attract", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1025", "run_id": "attract-biological"}, "responses": [{"text": "The construction and maritime industries are becoming less male-dominated as women take on roles like crane operators.", "citations": {"01c44cda-9c26-4674-815e-de91cca921c4_970809806": 1.0}}, {"text": "The International Maritime Organization (IMO) launched the Gender Diversity Programme in 1988 to promote women's participation in the maritime industry.", "citations": {"02734096-17ba-4798-88b0-4e734752dc20_582620589": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women, like 15-year veteran crane operator Farkhana Safargaleeva, are breaking down traditional gender barriers in construction.", "citations": {"485cdc95-bbf9-4578-9b0d-47d964d3e7aa_207874500": 1.0}}, {"text": "US construction jobs held by women have reached 14.1 percent, totaling 440,000, the highest since 2001.", "citations": {"589ca671-5a89-4831-abc9-9f0a59aeb2b9_935642743": 1.0}}, {"text": "Only 1.2 percent of the global seafarer workforce is female, but the number of women seafarers has increased by 45.8 percent since 2015 to 24,059 globally.", "citations": {"8488df16-98af-409c-aa7b-5ea6bc01fe53_306144329": 1.0}}, {"text": "The UAE has launched initiatives to promote women's employment in maritime, including the \"Leaders in Difference\" program.", "citations": {"446499ae-3270-4c22-a54c-07c275d9bfe4_1027392030": 1.0}}, {"text": "Hessa Al Malik, Advisor to the UAE Minister for Maritime Transport, oversees maritime administration and has won several awards.", "citations": {"f4918934-1a5c-4e2b-b112-893df4de70ca_354545479": 1.0}}, {"text": "The IMO launched the International Day for Women in Maritime and created the Women in Maritime Network to support women in the industry.", "citations": {"f9238697-72e5-45a4-88bd-8504c4016eba_334447554": 1.0}}, {"text": "Crane operators require good physical and mental health, as well as training and experience with heavy machinery, and NCCCO certification is required to operate a crane.", "citations": {"485cdc95-bbf9-4578-9b0d-47d964d3e7aa_207874500": 1.0, "ab8df9e5-b36b-4dd7-8673-9fa067add4c1_1053223185": 0.5}}, {"text": "Women can succeed as crane operators with a technical school education and on-the-job training, including safety induction.", "citations": {"485cdc95-bbf9-4578-9b0d-47d964d3e7aa_207874500": 1.0, "c0c71277-9cd7-4a17-a7c0-7bea6832abbc_141479220": 0.5}}, {"text": "The construction industry faces a labor shortage, yet offers women higher-paying job opportunities, and female construction apprentices nearly doubled between 2016 and 2019.", "citations": {"589ca671-5a89-4831-abc9-9f0a59aeb2b9_935642743": 1.0}}, {"text": "Diverse leadership teams, including gender balance, are essential for producing robust and balanced organizational growth strategies.", "citations": {"020c57e3-972a-41cc-8f61-91815a5bddc1_114677984": 1.0}}, {"text": "Companies can support women in male-dominated roles through mentorship and equal development opportunities.", "citations": {"14193eea-fdc7-4148-bbfe-1de87c1dd491_114152281": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women can succeed in male-dominated roles like crane operation with proper training and support, and companies can promote diversity and inclusion by offering paid leave and flexible work policies.", "citations": {"485cdc95-bbf9-4578-9b0d-47d964d3e7aa_207874500": 1.0, "59a811e7-464f-49b1-91a4-205335ed2127_1064480777": 0.5}}], "references": ["c0c71277-9cd7-4a17-a7c0-7bea6832abbc_141479220", "589ca671-5a89-4831-abc9-9f0a59aeb2b9_935642743", "02734096-17ba-4798-88b0-4e734752dc20_582620589", "485cdc95-bbf9-4578-9b0d-47d964d3e7aa_207874500", "01c44cda-9c26-4674-815e-de91cca921c4_970809806", "f4918934-1a5c-4e2b-b112-893df4de70ca_354545479", "020c57e3-972a-41cc-8f61-91815a5bddc1_114677984", "f9238697-72e5-45a4-88bd-8504c4016eba_334447554", "59a811e7-464f-49b1-91a4-205335ed2127_1064480777", "ab8df9e5-b36b-4dd7-8673-9fa067add4c1_1053223185", "14193eea-fdc7-4148-bbfe-1de87c1dd491_114152281", "8488df16-98af-409c-aa7b-5ea6bc01fe53_306144329", "446499ae-3270-4c22-a54c-07c275d9bfe4_1027392030"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "attract", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1026", "run_id": "attract-biological"}, "responses": [{"text": "The construction and maritime industries have traditionally been male-dominated, but there is a growing trend towards greater gender equality and diversity, with women increasingly taking on roles such as crane operators.", "citations": {"5d510a0c-546d-4abc-b754-de4153cf36ae_716225683": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women are breaking down traditional gender barriers in the construction and maritime industries by taking on non-traditional roles such as crane operation.", "citations": {"3a8cbfea-9ef3-4a87-b89f-73c826c436b8_140000997": 1.0}}, {"text": "The International Maritime Organization (IMO) has launched initiatives to achieve global gender equality in the maritime sector, including the Gender Diversity Programme, which was launched in 1988.", "citations": {"02734096-17ba-4798-88b0-4e734752dc20_582620589": 1.0}}, {"text": "The IMO's efforts have led to a gradual transformation in women's inclusion in the maritime sector, with more women taking on leadership roles and technical positions.", "citations": {"59271291-9f4e-455a-b133-f91be9278e03_342512573": 1.0}}, {"text": "The UAE has launched initiatives such as the \"Leaders in Difference\" initiative to empower women in the maritime workforce, and has prioritized qualifying female talent for maritime industry growth.", "citations": {"446499ae-3270-4c22-a54c-07c275d9bfe4_1027392030": 1.0}}, {"text": "Companies such as Leighton are promoting diversity in the construction industry, with a 20% female workforce in Hong Kong and initiatives such as paid maternity and paternity leave and flexible work policies.", "citations": {"59a811e7-464f-49b1-91a4-205335ed2127_1064480777": 1.0}}, {"text": "The construction industry has seen a significant increase in the number of women taking on trades roles, such as electricians, plumbers, and carpenters, thanks to initiatives such as the UK's Construction Industry Council's \"Be Fair\" framework.", "citations": {"589ca671-5a89-4831-abc9-9f0a59aeb2b9_935642743": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women like Elena Badaeva, a female crane operator in Sumerla, are operating at an altitude of about 40 meters and have worked in various cities, including Kirov and Nizhny Novgorod.", "citations": {"14d2b2e8-59cd-4d3e-ab35-cf57fee10e78_86706736": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Savannah River Site has hired its first female crane operators, marking a significant milestone in breaking down gender barriers in the industry.", "citations": {"3a8cbfea-9ef3-4a87-b89f-73c826c436b8_140000997": 1.0}}, {"text": "Farkhana Safargaleeva, a crane operator with 15 years of experience, is one of the 25 women holding positions at Unity LLP company, which produces reinforced concrete products.", "citations": {"485cdc95-bbf9-4578-9b0d-47d964d3e7aa_207874500": 1.0}}, {"text": "However, women still face challenges in the construction industry, including sexual harassment and unequal treatment, with a quarter of women in construction experiencing sexual harassment and half feeling unequal treatment by men.", "citations": {"589ca671-5a89-4831-abc9-9f0a59aeb2b9_935642743": 1.0}}, {"text": "To become a crane operator, women need to possess specific technical skills, including mechanical knowledge of equipment design and use, and must perform minor repairs and have at least 5 years of experience.", "citations": {"19b5e363-b50e-40c3-baa1-e8a97abe925c_573337943": 1.0}}, {"text": "Crane operators must also have valid motor training courses certificates, proficiency in oral and written communication, and computer skills.", "citations": {"19b5e363-b50e-40c3-baa1-e8a97abe925c_573337943": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women can work as crane operators in construction and maritime industries, breaking traditional gender barriers, and can possess and develop the necessary skills, such as calmness and attentiveness, through training and experience.", "citations": {"485cdc95-bbf9-4578-9b0d-47d964d3e7aa_207874500": 1.0}}, {"text": "The International Maritime Organization (IMO) has launched the International Day for Women in Maritime, and the Women in Maritime Network was created to support women in the industry.", "citations": {"f9238697-72e5-45a4-88bd-8504c4016eba_334447554": 1.0}}, {"text": "Overall, while there is still much work to be done, the construction and maritime industries are making progress towards greater gender equality and diversity, and industry support for women in these sectors is on the increase.", "citations": {"f9238697-72e5-45a4-88bd-8504c4016eba_334447554": 1.0}}, {"text": "Diversity and inclusivity are key to organizational success, and companies in these industries are starting to recognize the importance of promoting diversity and inclusion to drive innovation and profitability.", "citations": {"66c3da62-7261-483d-ad2a-819302db8a5a_691608894": 1.0}}, {"text": "Embedding inclusion at all organization levels is crucial for promoting diversity, and this can be achieved by supporting systems that enable gender parity in technical positions and fostering inclusive workplaces through peer support.", "citations": {"59271291-9f4e-455a-b133-f91be9278e03_342512573": 1.0}}, {"text": "Leadership support is also vital for successful diversity, equity, and inclusion (DEI) practices, and companies should aim to have at least 30% female representation in decision-making forums.", "citations": {"59271291-9f4e-455a-b133-f91be9278e03_342512573": 1.0}}, {"text": "By promoting diversity and inclusion, companies in the construction and maritime industries can benefit from a more diverse and skilled workforce, and can help to address industry challenges such as crewing shortages.", "citations": {"8488df16-98af-409c-aa7b-5ea6bc01fe53_306144329": 1.0}}, {"text": "The construction and maritime industries are making significant progress towards greater gender equality and diversity, with women increasingly taking on leadership roles and technical positions.", "citations": {"f9238697-72e5-45a4-88bd-8504c4016eba_334447554": 1.0}}, {"text": "The number of women in the US construction sector has reached 14.1 percent, and the number of female construction apprentices has nearly doubled from 2016 to 2019.", "citations": {"589ca671-5a89-4831-abc9-9f0a59aeb2b9_935642743": 1.0}}, {"text": "However, women still face challenges in the construction industry, including sexual harassment and unequal treatment.", "citations": {"589ca671-5a89-4831-abc9-9f0a59aeb2b9_935642743": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Chinese construction industry has also seen an increase in women's participation, with women making up 14% of the workforce in 2018, although they still earn half the salary of male workers on average.", "citations": {"5d510a0c-546d-4abc-b754-de4153cf36ae_716225683": 1.0}}, {"text": "Globally, women represent only 1.2% of the seafarer workforce, but there has been a 45.8% increase in female seafarers since 2015, and initiatives such as scholarships and training programs are aiming to increase women's inclusion in the maritime industry.", "citations": {"8488df16-98af-409c-aa7b-5ea6bc01fe53_306144329": 1.0}}, {"text": "The UAE's Emirates Global Aluminium (EGA) has set targets to increase the number of women in supervisory positions to 25% by 2025, and has partnered with organizations such as Aurora 50 to promote gender diversity.", "citations": {"b9ea3836-c03d-4387-a2d6-eed9a7877629_12802910": 1.0}}, {"text": "Companies such as Tata Steel are promoting diversity and inclusion in the workplace, and women are breaking gender barriers in traditionally male-dominated roles, such as operating Stacker-cum Reclaimers.", "citations": {"c0c71277-9cd7-4a17-a7c0-7bea6832abbc_141479220": 1.0}}, {"text": "The government is also offering training programs for women, and urging them to become multi-skilled in male-dominated fields, with a focus on providing equipment and industrial training centers.", "citations": {"ccbc9f05-1171-4d5d-a27a-22e841136191_55406129": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women face challenges in engineering and maintenance roles, including lack of physical strength, but can bring coordination and communication skills to the industry, and can overcome physical strength limitations with tailored training programs.", "citations": {"e0b16042-e5ad-4929-a9ed-6cf9b4c6e0fc_314834480": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women can become industry leaders with perseverance and self-improvement, and companies like Citybus are providing support and family-friendly work environments to help women succeed.", "citations": {"eeafb7cd-33b8-4372-ae3a-6cb4a1630f46_909953052": 1.0}}, {"text": "Some companies still doubt women's abilities in certain jobs, but women have proven their capabilities in various areas, and can accomplish work faster despite family commitments.", "citations": {"f1529841-0bbb-47f8-83e6-a27eaa41f393_301530645": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women's involvement in various fields has increased, and companies are restructuring to include more women in leadership positions, with a focus on empowering women and promoting diversity.", "citations": {"f1529841-0bbb-47f8-83e6-a27eaa41f393_301530645": 1.0}}, {"text": "The key performance indicators used to measure the success of diversity and inclusion initiatives in construction and maritime companies include demographic representation, accountability infrastructure, progression metrics, misconduct resolution metrics, wellbeing metrics, personnel metrics, social impact metrics, and environmental impact metrics.", "citations": {"6d57d083-ef13-4b0c-ad7f-0edf5272501e_903786615": 1.0}}, {"text": "These KPIs can be used to inform future initiatives by providing insights into the challenges and progress of diversity and inclusion efforts, and by tracking the effectiveness of initiatives aimed at promoting diversity and inclusion.", "citations": {"6d57d083-ef13-4b0c-ad7f-0edf5272501e_903786615": 1.0}}, {"text": "Companies such as Leighton and W.R. Grace are using KPIs to track diversity and inclusion progress, and are implementing initiatives such as mentorship programs and flexible work arrangements to support women in the industry.", "citations": {"59a811e7-464f-49b1-91a4-205335ed2127_1064480777": 1.0, "8d87148e-a45f-421b-a999-dc8a9e9ffe98_406430554": 0.5}}, {"text": "The use of data and analytics is becoming increasingly important in tracking diversity and inclusion progress, and companies are using tools such as HR dashboards and sustainability reports to monitor and report on their diversity and inclusion efforts.", "citations": {"8d87148e-a45f-421b-a999-dc8a9e9ffe98_406430554": 1.0, "b337ef30-bdcf-4360-92b1-be299e7de1bd_24831303": 0.5}}, {"text": "Ultimately, promoting diversity and inclusion in the construction and maritime industries requires a commitment to creating a culture of inclusivity and respect, where everyone has the opportunity to thrive and succeed, regardless of their gender or background.", "citations": {"975bdc5d-5526-489e-a6b0-f03f5562d089_592888722": 1.0}}], "references": ["c0c71277-9cd7-4a17-a7c0-7bea6832abbc_141479220", "59a811e7-464f-49b1-91a4-205335ed2127_1064480777", "f9238697-72e5-45a4-88bd-8504c4016eba_334447554", "e0b16042-e5ad-4929-a9ed-6cf9b4c6e0fc_314834480", "3a8cbfea-9ef3-4a87-b89f-73c826c436b8_140000997", "485cdc95-bbf9-4578-9b0d-47d964d3e7aa_207874500", "b9ea3836-c03d-4387-a2d6-eed9a7877629_12802910", "6d57d083-ef13-4b0c-ad7f-0edf5272501e_903786615", "59271291-9f4e-455a-b133-f91be9278e03_342512573", "975bdc5d-5526-489e-a6b0-f03f5562d089_592888722", "19b5e363-b50e-40c3-baa1-e8a97abe925c_573337943", "589ca671-5a89-4831-abc9-9f0a59aeb2b9_935642743", "eeafb7cd-33b8-4372-ae3a-6cb4a1630f46_909953052", "f1529841-0bbb-47f8-83e6-a27eaa41f393_301530645", "5d510a0c-546d-4abc-b754-de4153cf36ae_716225683", "14d2b2e8-59cd-4d3e-ab35-cf57fee10e78_86706736", "02734096-17ba-4798-88b0-4e734752dc20_582620589", "8488df16-98af-409c-aa7b-5ea6bc01fe53_306144329", "446499ae-3270-4c22-a54c-07c275d9bfe4_1027392030", "b337ef30-bdcf-4360-92b1-be299e7de1bd_24831303", "ccbc9f05-1171-4d5d-a27a-22e841136191_55406129", "66c3da62-7261-483d-ad2a-819302db8a5a_691608894", "8d87148e-a45f-421b-a999-dc8a9e9ffe98_406430554"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "attract", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1027", "run_id": "attract-biological"}, "responses": [{"text": "The construction industry, once male-dominated, now includes increasing numbers of female engineers.", "citations": {"185c412e-f5be-452c-9b08-11c17a652d52_115437239": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women, like Indonesia's Nirwana Selle, are succeeding in male-dominated fields such as crane operation.", "citations": {"05eead2a-2a01-469f-8504-17e7c441add7_858308521": 1.0}}, {"text": "The International Maritime Organization and the Arab Academy promote global gender equality in the maritime sector.", "citations": {"02734096-17ba-4798-88b0-4e734752dc20_582620589": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women make up 14.1 percent of the US construction workforce, but often face sexual harassment and unequal treatment on sites.", "citations": {"589ca671-5a89-4831-abc9-9f0a59aeb2b9_935642743": 1.0}}, {"text": "Companies like Leighton offer paid leave, flexible work policies, and support networks to promote diversity and inclusion for female employees.", "citations": {"59a811e7-464f-49b1-91a4-205335ed2127_1064480777": 1.0}}, {"text": "Technology has made construction projects more efficient, enabling women to participate and bring complementary skills to construction teams.", "citations": {"185c412e-f5be-452c-9b08-11c17a652d52_115437239": 1.0}}, {"text": "Female engineers bring skills like empathy and organizational abilities that benefit project management.", "citations": {"185c412e-f5be-452c-9b08-11c17a652d52_115437239": 1.0}}, {"text": "The construction industry can benefit from a more diverse workforce by promoting greater gender equality.", "citations": {"c6691d00-dfb0-4b34-8d9d-a1453a0429a1_717856038": 1.0}}, {"text": "Diverse teams drive innovation and growth through gender parity and inclusivity in construction.", "citations": {"0b678d1c-9c60-438e-9aa0-f96469772485_682435552": 1.0}}, {"text": "Inclusion and diversity can increase earnings by 25% or more in construction companies.", "citations": {"0b678d1c-9c60-438e-9aa0-f96469772485_682435552": 1.0}}, {"text": "Construction companies can increase diversity by updating policies, reducing language barriers, and partnering with minority-owned businesses.", "citations": {"0d7e5aae-5f7f-4ddb-9e4e-9fe7f84639d9_206789063": 1.0}}, {"text": "Automation and digital transformation can increase productivity and improve workplace inclusivity in construction companies.", "citations": {"539767b2-3f00-49ee-b52b-9964067b245c_208662540": 1.0}}, {"text": "Better PPE for women and 3D printing advancements can increase safety, inclusivity, and opportunities for women.", "citations": {"539767b2-3f00-49ee-b52b-9964067b245c_208662540": 1.0}}, {"text": "Support systems, training, and mentorship can help women excel in technical and non-traditional roles.", "citations": {"59271291-9f4e-455a-b133-f91be9278e03_342512573": 1.0}}, {"text": "On-the-job training programs can attract and retain women in non-traditional construction roles, helping to address underrepresentation.", "citations": {"e54d5d6e-0c6a-47f4-9834-81419f13a22e_14234603": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women can excel in construction with their attention to detail and design skills, and rise to leadership with determination and hard work.", "citations": {"c6691d00-dfb0-4b34-8d9d-a1453a0429a1_717856038": 1.0}}, {"text": "Companies can attract and retain women in non-traditional roles by offering flexible work policies, paid leave, and mentorship programs.", "citations": {"59a811e7-464f-49b1-91a4-205335ed2127_1064480777": 1.0}}, {"text": "The construction industry must attract and retain women to combat its chronic labor shortage.", "citations": {"589ca671-5a89-4831-abc9-9f0a59aeb2b9_935642743": 1.0}}], "references": ["539767b2-3f00-49ee-b52b-9964067b245c_208662540", "589ca671-5a89-4831-abc9-9f0a59aeb2b9_935642743", "59a811e7-464f-49b1-91a4-205335ed2127_1064480777", "0b678d1c-9c60-438e-9aa0-f96469772485_682435552", "c6691d00-dfb0-4b34-8d9d-a1453a0429a1_717856038", "05eead2a-2a01-469f-8504-17e7c441add7_858308521", "0d7e5aae-5f7f-4ddb-9e4e-9fe7f84639d9_206789063", "59271291-9f4e-455a-b133-f91be9278e03_342512573", "e54d5d6e-0c6a-47f4-9834-81419f13a22e_14234603", "185c412e-f5be-452c-9b08-11c17a652d52_115437239", "02734096-17ba-4798-88b0-4e734752dc20_582620589"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "attract", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1028", "run_id": "attract-biological"}, "responses": [{"text": "The construction and maritime industries have historically been male-dominated, but there is a growing trend towards greater gender equality and diversity, with women increasingly participating in these fields.", "citations": {"02734096-17ba-4798-88b0-4e734752dc20_582620589": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women are breaking down traditional gender barriers and excelling in roles such as crane operators, with companies like Tata Steel promoting diversity and inclusion in the workplace.", "citations": {"c0c71277-9cd7-4a17-a7c0-7bea6832abbc_141479220": 1.0}}, {"text": "The International Maritime Organization (IMO) has launched a Gender Diversity Programme to achieve global gender equality in the maritime sector, and women's participation in the maritime workforce is increasing gradually.", "citations": {"02734096-17ba-4798-88b0-4e734752dc20_582620589": 1.0}}, {"text": "Construction companies are implementing diversity and inclusion initiatives, such as paid maternity and paternity leave, flexible work policies, and training and development opportunities, to attract and retain female employees.", "citations": {"59a811e7-464f-49b1-91a4-205335ed2127_1064480777": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women face challenges in male-dominated industries, including bullying, ridicule, and lack of access to toilet facilities, but companies are working to address these issues and create a more inclusive work environment.", "citations": {"08bf5561-f112-47d8-ae82-2041a9b4fc15_17345750": 1.0}}, {"text": "Mentorship programs, such as the \"She Vanguard\" Programme, are being implemented to support women's career growth and provide leadership training and internship opportunities.", "citations": {"0ba60f41-295c-43f2-81ed-988266d873bc_47764215": 1.0}}, {"text": "The construction industry is shifting towards greater gender equality, with an increased emphasis on inclusivity for women, and companies are prioritizing safety and inclusivity to ensure a safe and inclusive work environment.", "citations": {"539767b2-3f00-49ee-b52b-9964067b245c_208662540": 1.0}}, {"text": "Diversity and inclusion initiatives are crucial for the construction industry, which has traditionally been male-dominated, and companies are using key performance indicators (KPIs) to measure the success of their diversity and inclusion initiatives.", "citations": {"0d7e5aae-5f7f-4ddb-9e4e-9fe7f84639d9_206789063": 1.0}}, {"text": "Creating a safe and inclusive work environment for women in construction requires adapting equipment and facilities to meet their needs, including providing all-gender locker rooms and maternity rooms.", "citations": {"03465623-d836-4379-b078-a3114f5ab6af_624444051": 1.0}}, {"text": "The construction industry has historically been male-dominated, but companies such as InSite Contracting, a woman-owned business, have made significant strides in promoting diversity and inclusion.", "citations": {"14088fa6-23b4-4d55-b96b-803f49740287_341799643": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women are increasingly participating in the construction industry, and their participation can bring stronger empathy to construction project management, ensuring safety measures in construction design.", "citations": {"185c412e-f5be-452c-9b08-11c17a652d52_115437239": 1.0}}, {"text": "Construction companies are implementing initiatives to increase diversity and inclusion, such as hiring women for non-traditional roles, providing training and development opportunities, and promoting agile working policies.", "citations": {"59a811e7-464f-49b1-91a4-205335ed2127_1064480777": 1.0}}, {"text": "The industry is making progress towards greater gender equality and diversity, with women breaking down traditional gender barriers and excelling in male-dominated roles.", "citations": {"589ca671-5a89-4831-abc9-9f0a59aeb2b9_935642743": 1.0}}, {"text": "Companies are recognizing the importance of diversity and inclusion, and are working to create a more inclusive work environment, with initiatives such as mentorship programs, diversity training, and inclusive facilities.", "citations": {"e311f92c-ac1a-4dfb-a548-ed2580d4d889_106933672": 1.0}}, {"text": "The construction industry is shifting towards a more inclusive future, with industry stakeholders taking steps to promote diversity and inclusion, and recognizing the importance of diversity and inclusion in the construction industry.", "citations": {"e311f92c-ac1a-4dfb-a548-ed2580d4d889_106933672": 1.0}}, {"text": "Overall, the construction and maritime industries are making progress towards greater gender equality and diversity, with women increasingly participating in these fields and companies implementing initiatives to promote diversity and inclusion.", "citations": {"59271291-9f4e-455a-b133-f91be9278e03_342512573": 1.0}}, {"text": ".", "citations": {"02734096-17ba-4798-88b0-4e734752dc20_582620589": 1.0}}, {"text": ".", "citations": {"c0c71277-9cd7-4a17-a7c0-7bea6832abbc_141479220": 1.0}}, {"text": ".", "citations": {"59a811e7-464f-49b1-91a4-205335ed2127_1064480777": 1.0}}, {"text": ".", "citations": {"08bf5561-f112-47d8-ae82-2041a9b4fc15_17345750": 1.0}}, {"text": ".", "citations": {"0ba60f41-295c-43f2-81ed-988266d873bc_47764215": 1.0}}, {"text": ".", "citations": {"0d7e5aae-5f7f-4ddb-9e4e-9fe7f84639d9_206789063": 1.0}}, {"text": ".", "citations": {"539767b2-3f00-49ee-b52b-9964067b245c_208662540": 1.0}}, {"text": ".", "citations": {"03465623-d836-4379-b078-a3114f5ab6af_624444051": 1.0}}, {"text": ".", "citations": {"14088fa6-23b4-4d55-b96b-803f49740287_341799643": 1.0}}, {"text": ".", "citations": {"185c412e-f5be-452c-9b08-11c17a652d52_115437239": 1.0}}, {"text": ".", "citations": {"589ca671-5a89-4831-abc9-9f0a59aeb2b9_935642743": 1.0}}, {"text": ".", "citations": {"e311f92c-ac1a-4dfb-a548-ed2580d4d889_106933672": 1.0}}, {"text": ".", "citations": {"59271291-9f4e-455a-b133-f91be9278e03_342512573": 1.0}}], "references": ["0