{"metadata": {"team_id": "attract", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1029", "run_id": "attract-biological"}, "responses": [{"text": "The science fiction genre has evolved over time, influenced by technological advancements, social movements, and diverse voices.", "citations": {"01c44cda-9c26-4674-815e-de91cca921c4_209737677": 1.0}}, {"text": "The genre has become more diverse, influenced by literary prizes and representing a wide range of geographical and linguistic fields.", "citations": {"01c44cda-9c26-4674-815e-de91cca921c4_209737677": 1.0}}, {"text": "Science fiction literature has evolved through four eras, shaped by authors like H.G. Wells, Jules Verne, and Isaac Asimov.", "citations": {"313a3381-4790-45a2-8734-d595fd2ee46a_38674691": 1.0}}, {"text": "H.G. Wells, a science fiction pioneer, wrote influential novels like \"The Time Machine\" and \"The War of the Worlds\" that explored time travel, technology, and social issues.", "citations": {"3d319f9a-69dd-4ae0-aa70-9a2ebdc0bdea_174201959": 1.0}}, {"text": "The science fiction genre has been influenced by authors from diverse backgrounds, bringing new perspectives and ideas.", "citations": {"764901a5-ae9e-4bb0-be99-00e9fcaa1a8b_389925305": 1.0}}, {"text": "Frankenstein is considered the first true science fiction novel, and The Blazing World is considered the first from the 17th century.", "citations": {"8dffe6e3-b2e0-4574-97ae-d3a72b383e10_533797018": 1.0}}, {"text": "Isaac Asimov's works introduced the concepts of psychohistory in Foundation and the laws of robotics in I, Robot.", "citations": {"8dffe6e3-b2e0-4574-97ae-d3a72b383e10_533797018": 1.0}}, {"text": "China's science fiction industry has developed rapidly, gaining worldwide popularity, and reached 87.75 billion yuan in revenue in 2022.", "citations": {"abaa0015-a46d-424f-9c06-e6df34a0b588_865359249": 1.0}}, {"text": "Science fiction has undergone significant changes over time, influenced by technological advancements and societal shifts.", "citations": {"8b0ef215-1d52-43a4-9ba0-15215b7f661c_150233956": 1.0}}, {"text": "Contemporary science fiction features technical and stylistic innovations, including narrative experimentation and predictions of scientific consequences.", "citations": {"8b0ef215-1d52-43a4-9ba0-15215b7f661c_150233956": 1.0}}, {"text": "Authors like Kazuo Ishiguro and Ursula K. Le Guin have written works combining science fiction with other genres, reflecting its evolution.", "citations": {"925467ab-7e77-4a0f-b127-d20919e07315_817963162": 1.0}}, {"text": "Contemporary science fiction reflects the influence of earlier authors like HG Wells, as well as newer diverse voices, including women and people of color.", "citations": {"b189e16e-b1b0-4531-898b-22bc44ca457e_717111571": 1.0}}, {"text": "Authors like Nnedi Okorafor, Diana Wynne Jones, and Liu Cixin have made significant contributions to science fiction, exploring new themes and ideas.", "citations": {"b189e16e-b1b0-4531-898b-22bc44ca457e_717111571": 1.0, "b2e0f030-a95e-438f-85de-d2027480e1dd_703489344": 0.5}}, {"text": "Diverse authors significantly impact science fiction development by bringing new ideas and perspectives, making it more relatable and realistic.", "citations": {"01c44cda-9c26-4674-815e-de91cca921c4_209737677": 1.0, "8b4f4c1e-487c-4250-846e-31739ce65460_1048251213": 0.5}}], "references": ["925467ab-7e77-4a0f-b127-d20919e07315_817963162", "8dffe6e3-b2e0-4574-97ae-d3a72b383e10_533797018", "8b0ef215-1d52-43a4-9ba0-15215b7f661c_150233956", "8b4f4c1e-487c-4250-846e-31739ce65460_1048251213", "3d319f9a-69dd-4ae0-aa70-9a2ebdc0bdea_174201959", "313a3381-4790-45a2-8734-d595fd2ee46a_38674691", "01c44cda-9c26-4674-815e-de91cca921c4_209737677", "abaa0015-a46d-424f-9c06-e6df34a0b588_865359249", "764901a5-ae9e-4bb0-be99-00e9fcaa1a8b_389925305", "b189e16e-b1b0-4531-898b-22bc44ca457e_717111571", "b2e0f030-a95e-438f-85de-d2027480e1dd_703489344"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "attract", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1030", "run_id": "attract-biological"}, "responses": [{"text": "The science fiction genre has undergone significant changes and evolution over time, with various factors influencing its development, including the rise of new authors from diverse backgrounds.", "citations": {"40905120-1cf6-49fc-a73d-e415e5ce057f_387896979": 1.0}}, {"text": "The genre has historically lacked diversity, with only 8 out of 100 top sci-fi films featuring a person of color as the lead character in 2014, implying an inability to imagine a future with people of color.", "citations": {"8b4f4c1e-487c-4250-846e-31739ce65460_1048251213": 1.0}}, {"text": "However, in recent years, there has been an increase in diverse representation, with major franchises like Marvel and Star Wars including better racial diversity, paving the way for more inclusive storytelling.", "citations": {"8b4f4c1e-487c-4250-846e-31739ce65460_1048251213": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Hugo Award, which is the highest honor in science fiction, has also played a significant role in promoting diversity and inclusivity, with winners including authors from diverse backgrounds and identities.", "citations": {"40905120-1cf6-49fc-a73d-e415e5ce057f_387896979": 1.0}}, {"text": "Chinese science fiction, in particular, has flourished, with authors like Liu Cixin winning the Hugo Award for Best Novel in 2015, and Chinese female writers thriving in the genre, despite limited feminist expression in China.", "citations": {"40905120-1cf6-49fc-a73d-e415e5ce057f_387896979": 1.0}}, {"text": "The internet has removed barriers to writing for non-male authors, allowing for a more diverse range of voices in the science fiction genre, and providing a platform for women and queer talents to develop their writing skills.", "citations": {"40905120-1cf6-49fc-a73d-e415e5ce057f_387896979": 1.0}}, {"text": "The number of women writers in science fiction has increased in recent years in China, with a wider and more diverse audience for the genre, and independent publishers have played a crucial role in promoting underrepresented authors.", "citations": {"40905120-1cf6-49fc-a73d-e415e5ce057f_387896979": 1.0}}, {"text": "The science fiction genre has become more diverse and inclusive, with authors from diverse backgrounds making significant contributions, such as Nnedi Okorafor, whose Binti is a Hugo-award-winning Africanfuturistic science fiction horror story.", "citations": {"8dffe6e3-b2e0-4574-97ae-d3a72b383e10_533797018": 1.0}}, {"text": "The genre has also been influenced by authors who incorporate elements of ethnography and intertextuality into their works, and has become more global, with authors from different countries and cultures contributing to its development.", "citations": {"925467ab-7e77-4a0f-b127-d20919e07315_817963162": 1.0}}, {"text": "The impact of diverse authors on modern science fiction has been significant, enriching the genre and expanding its possibilities, and the future of science fiction looks promising, with new authors and voices emerging, and the genre continuing to evolve and adapt to changing times.", "citations": {"abe25c6f-ed4b-4ed5-84c4-f2614014733d_259481418": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Hugo Awards have recognized the work of underrepresented authors, including women and people of color, and have helped to promote diversity and inclusivity in the genre, with a record number of non-English speaking members participating in the 2023 awards.", "citations": {"77e87d04-1f0d-4b66-a0fd-5021dbab0777_447906512": 1.0}}, {"text": "Overall, the science fiction genre has undergone significant changes and evolution over time, with a growing focus on diversity, representation, and inclusivity, and the impact of diverse authors has been significant, enriching the genre and expanding its possibilities.", "citations": {"40905120-1cf6-49fc-a73d-e415e5ce057f_387896979": 1.0}}, {"text": "The genre continues to evolve, with new authors and voices emerging, and the future of science fiction looks promising, with a growing focus on diversity, representation, and inclusivity.", "citations": {"abe25c6f-ed4b-4ed5-84c4-f2614014733d_259481418": 1.0}}, {"text": "The science fiction community has implemented various initiatives to address the historical lack of diversity and representation in the genre, including inviting diverse speculative fiction submissions and launching new imprints for speculative fiction.", "citations": {"0f5a153d-c7b1-4b79-8b82-752e8d8fbd25_640346825": 1.0}}, {"text": "These initiatives have helped to promote diversity and inclusivity in the genre, and have provided opportunities for underrepresented authors to publish their work and reach a wider audience.", "citations": {"21bf354d-f8ba-4002-a234-4dec5f8b44d4_685175235": 1.0}}, {"text": "The impact of independent publishers and online platforms on promoting diversity and inclusivity in science fiction has been significant, with many underrepresented authors achieving success and gaining recognition through these channels.", "citations": {"21bf354d-f8ba-4002-a234-4dec5f8b44d4_685175235": 1.0}}, {"text": "Social media has also played a significant role in promoting underrepresented authors and connecting them with readers, providing a platform for them to share their work and build their audience.", "citations": {"6de506f0-ae99-4cee-a0e2-061b86711562_245162032": 1.0}}, {"text": "Overall, the science fiction genre has become more diverse and inclusive, with a wider range of voices and perspectives being represented, and the impact of diverse authors has been significant, enriching the genre and expanding its possibilities.", "citations": {"40905120-1cf6-49fc-a73d-e415e5ce057f_387896979": 1.0}}, {"text": ".", "citations": {"01c44cda-9c26-4674-815e-de91cca921c4_209737677": 1.0}}, {"text": ".", "citations": {"097f6709-e578-43b2-9ab7-cc079b48699e_405676515": 1.0}}, {"text": ".", "citations": {"1af7c5c0-2cd8-4ccb-ae8a-3d495406430b_509519304": 1.0