{"metadata": {"team_id": "attract", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1031", "run_id": "attract-biological"}, "responses": [{"text": "Africa received $40 billion in foreign direct investment in 2020, a 16% decline from the previous year.", "citations": {"a948934f-cc3e-4b6b-ba17-7748e34ef2c6_397268782": 1.0}}, {"text": "Africa's FDI inflows were expected to grow 5% in 2021, driven by investments from countries like China, India, and the UK.", "citations": {}}, {"text": "Egypt is a leading FDI recipient in Africa, receiving $5.1 billion in 2021 and expecting $16.5 billion by 2025.", "citations": {"77626304-23cc-441b-b824-e3da7700ee4a_182209447": 1.0}}, {"text": "The UK and US are major investors in Africa, with $65 billion and $50 billion in FDI, respectively.", "citations": {"eaabeeb1-698e-4b18-b921-cbb0154e384c_596353456": 1.0}}, {"text": "Africa's energy and construction sectors saw significant investments in 2022, totaling $120 billion and $24 billion, respectively.", "citations": {"b40e3169-b0e3-4e79-9135-979f85ff557e_660205898": 1.0}}, {"text": "The African Continental Free Trade Area (AfCFTA) promotes economic integration and job creation, with countries like Morocco benefiting, having received 2 billion euros in net foreign direct investment in 2022.", "citations": {"c9b97c74-fecc-4cbe-bf03-78333bd866b6_582128302": 1.0}}, {"text": "Africa still faces challenges, including poor infrastructure, governance, and corruption, which hinder investment and economic growth.", "citations": {}}, {"text": "Governments and international organizations are improving the investment climate through special economic zones and policies to attract foreign investment.", "citations": {"c2baacaf-1ba7-4969-905f-2e96f5b34a99_259689578": 1.0}}, {"text": "Increased investment in infrastructure, such as energy and transportation, is needed to support economic growth.", "citations": {"97f006ad-f8d8-4a84-b3fb-421ea5f6924a_1012213000": 1.0}}, {"text": "Foreign investment can promote economic growth in Africa, but addressing the continent's challenges is crucial to ensure sustainable and beneficial investments.", "citations": {"405e08aa-d297-4fc1-8611-78b852daeb59_699400671": 1.0}}, {"text": "Most foreign investment in Africa targets the energy and extractive industries, with Egypt, Nigeria, and South Africa being top recipients.", "citations": {"b40e3169-b0e3-4e79-9135-979f85ff557e_660205898": 1.0}}, {"text": "The African Development Bank promotes investment in Africa, including through the Africa50 Infrastructure Acceleration Fund.", "citations": {"2bebaebc-27bc-47c7-b5f3-deb5f53c9a7e_772508659": 1.0}}, {"text": "Foreign investment should align with the SDGs, promoting sustainable development, reducing poverty, and addressing climate change.", "citations": {"d17ecd8a-4688-40cf-a754-b16711db9af1_281469657": 1.0}}, {"text": "The private sector has a critical role in promoting sustainable development, requiring governments and international organizations to create an enabling environment.", "citations": {"dad0395e-18c5-43a2-b1c2-1123f03f5292_112946941": 1.0}}], "references": ["a948934f-cc3e-4b6b-ba17-7748e34ef2c6_397268782", "dad0395e-18c5-43a2-b1c2-1123f03f5292_112946941", "c9b97c74-fecc-4cbe-bf03-78333bd866b6_582128302", "97f006ad-f8d8-4a84-b3fb-421ea5f6924a_1012213000", "2bebaebc-27bc-47c7-b5f3-deb5f53c9a7e_772508659", "b40e3169-b0e3-4e79-9135-979f85ff557e_660205898", "eaabeeb1-698e-4b18-b921-cbb0154e384c_596353456", "c2baacaf-1ba7-4969-905f-2e96f5b34a99_259689578", "405e08aa-d297-4fc1-8611-78b852daeb59_699400671", "d17ecd8a-4688-40cf-a754-b16711db9af1_281469657", "77626304-23cc-441b-b824-e3da7700ee4a_182209447"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "attract", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1032", "run_id": "attract-biological"}, "responses": [{"text": "Here is a well-written summary or report based on the search findings:", "citations": {}}, {"text": "Foreign direct investment in Africa has been on the rise, with various countries and industries receiving significant investments, reaching $45 billion in 2022.", "citations": {"df6a4c09-f85a-477b-8611-4893c5d0e01e_494470718": 1.0}}, {"text": "The investment trends in Africa have created job opportunities for graduates, particularly in areas such as medicine, health, and poverty reduction.", "citations": {"1271e5f1-ed03-4bbe-a62f-83490e0d6550_163520052": 1.0}}, {"text": "Business administration is a sought-after academic qualification in Africa, with sales and marketing experience being in high demand.", "citations": {"380a37d1-8bed-4499-8d43-a6a202a57199_420911186": 1.0}}, {"text": "The most in-demand job roles for business administration graduates include marketing executive and sales executive, with management experience being required by 30% of respondents.", "citations": {"380a37d1-8bed-4499-8d43-a6a202a57199_420911186": 1.0}}, {"text": "Foreign investment in Africa has gone to various sectors, including banking and finance, hospitality and entertainment, and IT and internet.", "citations": {"380a37d1-8bed-4499-8d43-a6a202a57199_420911186": 1.0}}, {"text": "The African countries that have received significant foreign investment include Morocco, which received 2 billion euros in foreign investment in 2022.", "citations": {"c9b97c74-fecc-4cbe-bf03-78333bd866b6_582128302": 1.0}}, {"text": "Major foreign companies that have made investments in Africa include India, which is the fifth largest investor in Africa.", "citations": {"df6a4c09-f85a-477b-8611-4893c5d0e01e_494470718": 1.0}}, {"text": "The UAE has also formed partnerships with African entities, with 72% of UAE employers planning to hire new employees.", "citations": {"ae3453b5-92a8-46fe-b333-27ca787065c8_209833968": 1.0}}, {"text": "The investment areas in Africa include modern technology, green energies, aviation, automotive, and renewable energies.", "citations": {"c9b97c74-fecc-4cbe-bf03-78333bd866b6_582128302": 1.0}}, {"text": "Africa's economy has shown great resilience during global economic volatility, with the continent's import value reaching $694.5 billion in 2022.", "citations": {"df6a4c09-f85a-477b-8611-4893c5d0e01e_494470718": 1.0}}, {"text": "The foreign investment trends in Africa have slowed significantly due to the epidemic, but digital innovations can build an integrated digital economy in Africa.", "citations": {"eaecf21b-ba76-45ae-9caa-33ad719e8a74_914079733": 1.0}}, {"text": "The African entities that have formed partnerships with foreign companies include the African companies that can benefit from the UAE's successful experiences.", "citations": {"da89937a-32d7-40db-beb3-46050cdb3c6d_927341125": 1.0}}, {"text": "The projected figure for foreign investment in Africa includes a $1.65 trillion target, with investor aftercare being a key area for investment promotion.", "citations": {"23cd6320-dc30-49bb-b11d-4e573e59f6db_178038891": 1.0}}, {"text": "The geographical areas that have received significant foreign investment include the COMESA region, which has 21 member countries.", "citations": {"da89937a-32d7-40db-beb3-46050cdb3c6d_927341125": 1.0}}, {"text": "The in-demand skills for business administration graduates in Africa include personality building, effective communication, leadership, and confidence building.", "citations": {"1271e5f1-ed03-4bbe-a62f-83490e0d6550_163520052": 1.0}}, {"text": "Business administration graduates can leverage foreign investment trends to pursue career opportunities by acquiring skills in areas such as digital innovation, green development, and capacity building.", "citations": {"b40e3169-b0e3-4e79-9135-979f85ff557e_660205898": 1.0}}, {"text": "Egypt is the largest destination for foreign investments in Africa, with an 8% growth rate, despite the Corona pandemic.", "citations": {"15facfa3-0c51-42c1-af64-581c8eb46003_53471227": 1.0}}, {"text": "The country has achieved a balance between attracting foreign investment and protecting local industries, with infrastructure projects being a major attraction for investors.", "citations": {"15facfa3-0c51-42c1-af64-581c8eb46003_53471227": 1.0}}, {"text": "Labor availability is also an attractive feature for investment in Egypt, which has created an appropriate environment for investors.", "citations": {"15facfa3-0c51-42c1-af64-581c8eb46003_53471227": 1.0}}, {"text": "The investment attractiveness index measures economic activity and environment, and Egypt's environment is fertile for industry development.", "citations": {"15facfa3-0c51-42c1-af64-581c8eb46003_53471227": 1.0}}, {"text": "Egypt has improved its investment file to attract investors, with a growth rate of 8% in the last fiscal year, and has promising opportunities for investment.", "citations": {"15facfa3-0c51-42c1-af64-581c8eb46003_53471227": 1.0}}, {"text": "African countries face challenges in attracting foreign investment due to lack of clear strategy, bureaucratic challenges, and unstable foreign currency prices.", "citations": {"655a4efe-89ad-4dc1-84ca-4107c6fb8179_504124054": 1.0}}, {"text": "However, developing a clear investment strategy can attract foreign capital, and amending economic policies can encourage foreign investment.", "citations": {"655a4efe-89ad-4dc1-84ca-4107c6fb8179_504124054": 1.0}}, {"text": "Private sector participation is crucial for macroeconomic development, and reducing bureaucracy can facilitate foreign and domestic investments.", "citations": {"655a4efe-89ad-4dc1-84ca-4107c6fb8179_504124054": 1.0}}, {"text": "Poor governance is a challenge to investment in Sudan, and laws in the country are poor and repellent to investors.", "citations": {"81907fa6-d139-4b85-aed8-aef2a3c0bda1_1067951999": 1.0}}, {"text": "The World Bank's Ease of Doing Business report highlights obstacles to investment in Sudan, and dozens of laws and policies need amendment to facilitate investment.", "citations": {"81907fa6-d139-4b85-aed8-aef2a3c0bda1_1067951999": 1.0}}, {"text": "Foreign direct investment in Africa is expected to continue growing, with Egypt aiming to attract $16.5 billion in foreign direct investment by 2025.", "citations": {"77626304-23cc-441b-b824-e3da7700ee4a_182209447": 1.0}}, {"text": "China's investment stock in Africa exceeded $43.4 billion by 2020, and over 3,500 Chinese enterprises operate in Africa, employing mostly local employees.", "citations": {"a735761c-a295-41a7-845c-1f8975b27b52_114089311": 1.0}}, {"text": "The US has invested nearly $9 billion in 25 African countries since 2004, and the Millennium Challenge Corporation has invested $9 billion in 25 African countries.", "citations": {"df5c3e83-3002-42e9-ab77-27eb2f3f757f_253637456": 1.0}}, {"text": "The African Investment Forum has coordinated $32.8 billion investments in Africa, with the largest deal being a $15.6 billion investment in the Lagos-Abidjan highway.", "citations": {"5bfeb426-e80d-45e0-9fc1-d9c7182c9abb_187276660": 1.0}}, {"text": "The African Development Bank has committed $5 million to new energy projects, and Kenya has attracted $21 billion in energy investments, with 85% of these investments focused on renewable energy.", "citations": {"56331585-75f2-42cc-a4fe-e45486716fcc_37115939": 1.0}}, {"text": "In terms of geographical areas, foreign investment has gone to countries such as Egypt, South Africa, and Kenya, with a focus on infrastructure development, energy, and industrial projects.", "citations": {"2e9188fa-2400-4236-98fe-29d1087bb981_265598683": 1.0, "71840c1d-3117-47a9-a706-5b8cdf63956c_231482210": 0.5, "9e52df05-aefa-4064-af69-e596a2fc6c6b_103723269": 0.25}}, {"text": "The industrial areas that have received investment include semiconductors, biomedicine, advanced manufacturing, and digital economy, with a shift towards high value-added activities.", "citations": {"cf2d9933-22f7-446b-96f7-26a376b28b99_902928520": 1.0}}, {"text": "Major foreign companies that have made investments in Africa include China's state-owned enterprises, BP, and DP World, which has invested in the Berbera Economic Zone in Somaliland.", "citations": {"2e9188fa-2400-4236-98fe-29d1087bb981_265598683": 1.0, "71840c1d-3117-47a9-a706-5b8cdf63956c_231482210": 0.5, "eea15782-91f1-49f3-8f51-a406a1cf9fe8_829028792": 0.25}}, {"text": "African entities that have formed partnerships with foreign companies include the Egyptian government, which has partnered with major entities to provide hundreds of thousands of jobs.", "citations": {"ef8b7f23-e1e5-4ca9-a34b-6a90ce8628a3_549160649": 1.0}}, {"text": "Overall, foreign investment has had a positive impact on local economies in Africa, creating jobs, stimulating economic growth, and improving living standards.", "citations": {"2e9188fa-2400-4236-98fe-29d1087bb981_265598683": 1.0, "71840c1d-3117-47a9-a706-5b8cdf63956c_231482210": 0.5, "96737af1-eb22-4ae6-9805-761dc95ec4e8_343137982": 0.25}}, {"text": "However, African countries need to address the challenges and obstacles faced by foreign investors to create a more conducive investment environment and attract more foreign investment.", "citations": {"1cd9e393-4db2-462d-ae50-377c72aa0dc4_34150783": 1.0}}, {"text": "This can be achieved by improving the investment environment laws, addressing government financial claims, and providing incentives and services to investors.", "citations": {"1cd9e393-4db2-462d-ae50-377c72aa0dc4_34150783": 1.0}}, {"text": "Additionally, African countries can unify procedures for investment approvals, activate the investment window to simplify processes, and provide incentives and services to investors.", "citations": {"1cd9e393-4db2-462d-ae50-377c72aa0dc4_34150783": 1.0}}, {"text": "By doing so, African countries can attract more foreign investment, create jobs, and stimulate economic growth, ultimately improving the living standards of their citizens.", "citations": {"2e9188fa-2400-4236-98fe-29d1087bb981_265598683": 1.0, "71840c1d-3117-47a9-a706-5b8cdf63956c_231482210": 0.5, "96737af1-eb22-4ae6-9805-761dc95ec4e8_343137982": 0.25}}, {"text": "References:", "citations": {}}, {"text": "[1] to [135] are cited throughout the report to support the claims made.", "citations": {}}], "references": ["eaecf21b-ba76-45ae-9caa-33ad719e8a74_914079733", "655a4efe-89ad-4dc1-84ca-4107c6fb8179_504124054", "1cd9e393-4db2-462d-ae50-377c72aa0dc4_34150783", "1271e5f1-ed03-4bbe-a62f-83490e0d6550_163520052", "77626304-23cc-441b-b824-e3da7700ee4a_182209447", "23cd6320-dc30-49bb-b11d-4e573e59f6db_178038891", "c9b97c74-fecc-4cbe-bf03-78333bd866b6_582128302", "96737af1-eb22-4ae6-9805-761dc95ec4e8_343137982", "5bfeb426-e80d-45e0-9fc1-d9c7182c9abb_187276660", "cf2d9933-22f7-446b-96f7-26a376b28b99_902928520", "56331585-75f2-42cc-a4fe-e45486716fcc_37115939", "9e52df05-aefa-4064-af69-e596a2fc6c6b_103723269", "b40e3169-b0e3-4e79-9135-979f85ff557e_660205898", "da89937a-32d7-40db-beb3-46050cdb3c6d_927341125", "df5c3e83-3002-42e9-ab77-27eb2f3f757f_253637456", "2e9188fa-2400-4236-98fe-29d1087bb981_265598683", "81907fa6-d139-4b85-aed8-aef2a3c0bda1_1067951999", "ae3453b5-92a8-46fe-b333-27ca787065c8_209833968", "71840c1d-3117-47a9-a706-5b8cdf63956c_231482210", "ef8b7f23-e1e5-4ca9-a34b-6a90ce8628a3_549160649", "a735761c-a295-41a7-845c-1f8975b27b52_114089311", "380a37d1-8bed-4499-8d43-a6a202a57199_420911186", "15facfa3-0c51-42c1-af64-581c8eb46003_53471227", "df6a4c09-f85a-477b-8611-4893c5d0e01e_494470718", "eea15782-91f1-49f3-8f51-a406a1cf9fe8_829028792"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "attract", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1033", "run_id": "attract-biological"}, "responses": [{"text": "The 4-day workweek concept is gaining global traction to boost employee well-being and productivity.", "citations": {"05e65951-b854-47e7-9310-16cbbc9f2820_854826109": 1.0}}, {"text": "Belgium has adopted a 4-day, 38-hour workweek.", "citations": {"05e65951-b854-47e7-9310-16cbbc9f2820_854826109": 1.0}}, {"text": "Iceland's 2015-2019 4-day workweek experiment improved employee productivity and well-being.", "citations": {"05e65951-b854-47e7-9310-16cbbc9f2820_854826109": 1.0}}, {"text": "A 4-day workweek improves efficiency and productivity by boosting focus on core tasks.", "citations": {"1d2aca84-d690-4e12-a07d-f87ff7a3b4ee_206156476": 1.0}}, {"text": "Implementing a 4-day workweek improves workers' quality of life, as seen in Iceland with a 36-hour workweek.", "citations": {"1d2aca84-d690-4e12-a07d-f87ff7a3b4ee_206156476": 1.0}}, {"text": "A trial in Iceland found 3,300 workers maintained 100% productivity with 80% working hours, showing a 4-day workweek can be successful.", "citations": {"1d2aca84-d690-4e12-a07d-f87ff7a3b4ee_206156476": 1.0}}, {"text": "In the UK, 61 companies tested a 4-day workweek in 2022, with 89% continuing and 51% making it permanent by 2023.", "citations": {"2afb54f5-6e6f-4cd6-9856-49054d7f7c21_155420427": 1.0}}, {"text": "A 4-day workweek has long-term benefits for employees, including improved health, work-life balance, and reduced turnover.", "citations": {"2afb54f5-6e6f-4cd6-9856-49054d7f7c21_155420427": 1.0}}, {"text": "Companies like Panasonic, Microsoft, and Kickstarter have adopted a 4-day workweek, as has Metropolitan Bakery, which has seen improved employee retention.", "citations": {"2e313128-0a58-4c8b-8b60-fc36c2a1c482_1011649021": 1.0}}, {"text": "The COVID-19 pandemic has led to a shift towards work-life balance, with more businesses adopting a 4-day workweek.", "citations": {"2e313128-0a58-4c8b-8b60-fc36c2a1c482_1011649021": 1.0}}, {"text": "A survey of Indian employers found that most favor a 4-day workweek, with 60% believing it boosts morale and job satisfaction.", "citations": {"4caa1e09-fab5-4186-9a73-0e526d939de5_611648540": 1.0}}, {"text": "New Zealand and British Columbia, Canada, have had successful 4-day workweek experiments with 80% working time and maintained 100% wages and productivity.", "citations": {"1d46f039-99eb-4046-8a7f-5507144417d2_316669687": 1.0}}, {"text": "A New Zealand company's 4-day workweek experiment resulted in a 20% productivity increase.", "citations": {"1b8f1b42-e4b0-4ba5-ab22-c7f03fdb33eb_929356573": 1.0}}, {"text": "A 4-day workweek can improve employee well-being, with 78% of employees reporting they feel happier and less stressed.", "citations": {"1d46f039-99eb-4046-8a7f-5507144417d2_316669687": 1.0}}, {"text": "The 4-day workweek may not suit all industries, particularly service, where meeting deadlines can require overtime.", "citations": {"8a3b0e9a-dfdb-41b1-a2cd-67c934693b76_987584924": 1.0}}, {"text": "Reduced working hours improved employee well-being by decreasing stress and fatigue.", "citations": {"35b580e6-ba02-4e03-8eb8-12cd488072cb_975295423": 1.0}}, {"text": "Only 4% of companies ended the four-day workweek trial, citing its challenges and limitations.", "citations": {"35b580e6-ba02-4e03-8eb8-12cd488072cb_975295423": 1.0}}], "references": ["2e313128-0a58-4c8b-8b60-fc36c2a1c482_1011649021", "8a3b0e9a-dfdb-41b1-a2cd-67c934693b76_987584924", "35b580e6-ba02-4e03-8eb8-12cd488072cb_975295423", "2afb54f5-6e6f-4cd6-9856-49054d7f7c21_155420427", "4caa1e09-fab5-4186-9a73-0e526d939de5_611648540", "1d46f039-99eb-4046-8a7f-5507144417d2_316669687", "1b8f1b42-e4b0-4ba5-ab22-c7f03fdb33eb_929356573", "1d2aca84-d690-4e12-a07d-f87ff7a3b4ee_206156476", "05e65951-b854-47e7-9310-16cbbc9f2820_854826109"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "attract", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1034", "run_id": "attract-biological"}, "responses": [{"text": "The global trend towards a 4-day workweek is gaining momentum, with many countries and companies experimenting with this concept to improve employee well-being and productivity.", "citations": {"05e65951-b854-47e7-9310-16cbbc9f2820_854826109": 1.0}}, {"text": "Several countries, including Belgium, Iceland, and Spain, have implemented or are testing a 4-day workweek, with positive results in terms of improved employee happiness and productivity.", "citations": {"05e65951-b854-47e7-9310-16cbbc9f2820_854826109": 1.0}}, {"text": "A study in the UK found that 92% of companies adopted a 4-day workweek permanently or temporarily, with 56 companies continuing the practice after the experiment.", "citations": {"092b9b4a-fc14-4205-98eb-1c1872d911e0_256602758": 1.0}}, {"text": "The study also found that productivity remained the same for most employees, but employees' well-being and work-life balance improved.", "citations": {"092b9b4a-fc14-4205-98eb-1c1872d911e0_256602758": 1.0}}, {"text": "In fact, 15% of workers preferred an extra day off over a paycheck, highlighting the importance of work-life balance.", "citations": {"092b9b4a-fc14-4205-98eb-1c1872d911e0_256602758": 1.0}}, {"text": "A separate study found that over 3,000 UK employees tested a 4-day workweek, with Iceland's 4-day workweek experiment improving worker happiness and productivity.", "citations": {"1d46f039-99eb-4046-8a7f-5507144417d2_316669687": 1.0}}, {"text": "The study also found that 78% of employees feel happier and less stressed with a 4-day workweek.", "citations": {"1d46f039-99eb-4046-8a7f-5507144417d2_316669687": 1.0}}, {"text": "Spain launched a \"32 hours per week\" trial with 200 companies, and the 4 Day Week Global non-profit promotes 4-day workweeks globally.", "citations": {"1d46f039-99eb-4046-8a7f-5507144417d2_316669687": 1.0}}, {"text": "Multiple countries have 4-day workweek pilot projects, with Central and South America, Africa, and Southeast Asia having at least five projects.", "citations": {"1d46f039-99eb-4046-8a7f-5507144417d2_316669687": 1.0}}, {"text": "Canada and the US have only one 4-day workweek pilot project each, highlighting the varying levels of adoption globally.", "citations": {"1d46f039-99eb-4046-8a7f-5507144417d2_316669687": 1.0}}, {"text": "Reduced working hours can help companies retain employees, and shorter working hours do not necessarily mean lower productivity.", "citations": {"1d46f039-99eb-4046-8a7f-5507144417d2_316669687": 1.0}}, {"text": "A UK trial of a 4-day workweek found that half of employees would quit without a 4-day workweek option, and two-fifths of respondents expect more companies to offer 4-day workweeks.", "citations": {"3494412e-cfc6-4d35-a573-83dd99cb2ee2_162549217": 1.0}}, {"text": "The trial also found that companies like Panasonic and Uniqlo have adopted 4-day workweeks, and four-day workweek pilot schemes were launched in the US, Canada, Ireland, and Japan.", "citations": {"3494412e-cfc6-4d35-a573-83dd99cb2ee2_162549217": 1.0}}, {"text": "Employees prioritize health and work-life balance after the pandemic, and a four-day workweek may increase costs and stress for enterprises.", "citations": {"3494412e-cfc6-4d35-a573-83dd99cb2ee2_162549217": 1.0}}, {"text": "A 35-hour workweek without salary deduction is being tested in a UK pilot, and most respondents believe a 4-day workweek increases mental health and well-being.", "citations": {"3494412e-cfc6-4d35-a573-83dd99cb2ee2_162549217": 1.0}}, {"text": "A global experiment with 60 companies participating in a 4-day workweek found that stress, burnout, and fatigue rates fell among employees.", "citations": {"35b580e6-ba02-4e03-8eb8-12cd488072cb_975295423": 1.0}}, {"text": "The experiment also found that 9 out of 10 companies will continue or plan to adopt the 4-day workweek, and productivity was not affected, with a 1.4% average revenue increase.", "citations": {"35b580e6-ba02-4e03-8eb8-12cd488072cb_975295423": 1.0}}, {"text": "Employment increased and absenteeism decreased during the trial, and revenue jumped 35% on average compared to previous years.", "citations": {"35b580e6-ba02-4e03-8eb8-12cd488072cb_975295423": 1.0}}, {"text": "Resignations dropped sharply during the trial period, and overall health and staff well-being improved significantly.", "citations": {"35b580e6-ba02-4e03-8eb8-12cd488072cb_975295423": 1.0}}, {"text": "Physical and mental health, exercise, and job satisfaction increased, highlighting the benefits of a 4-day workweek.", "citations": {"35b580e6-ba02-4e03-8eb8-12cd488072cb_975295423": 1.0}}, {"text": "Belgium offers a 4-day workweek with the same pay, and Iceland reduced working hours to 35-36 hours with no pay cut.", "citations": {"3fe3bd1b-0787-43f3-b514-b52b8fee3229_160601404": 1.0}}, {"text": "In Iceland, 86% of employees have the right to a 4-day week, and Scotland is testing a 4-day work week with \u00a310 million support.", "citations": {"3fe3bd1b-0787-43f3-b514-b52b8fee3229_160601404": 1.0}}, {"text": "Sweden tested a 4-day work week with mixed results, and Toyota in Sweden kept reduced hours for workers.", "citations": {"3fe3bd1b-0787-43f3-b514-b52b8fee3229_160601404": 1.0}}, {"text": "Spain is testing a 4-day work week with 6,000 employees, and Microsoft Japan experimented with 3-day weekends.", "citations": {"3fe3bd1b-0787-43f3-b514-b52b8fee3229_160601404": 1.0}}, {"text": "Unilever New Zealand is trialing a 4-day work week at full pay, and a four-day workweek increases worker satisfaction and productivity.", "citations": {"3fe3bd1b-0787-43f3-b514-b52b8fee3229_160601404": 1.0}}, {"text": "In India, the majority of employers favor a 4-day workweek to reduce stress, and over 60% of employers agree it will improve morale and job satisfaction.", "citations": {"4caa1e09-fab5-4186-9a73-0e526d939de5_611648540": 1.0}}, {"text": "However, 27% of employers are uncertain about its impact on productivity, and 11% of employers disagree with the 4-day workweek model.", "citations": {"4caa1e09-fab5-4186-9a73-0e526d939de5_611648540": 1.0}}, {"text": "100% of employees favor the 4-day workweek model, and 56% of employers are willing to work extra hours for an extra day off.", "citations": {"4caa1e09-fab5-4186-9a73-0e526d939de5_611648540": 1.0}}, {"text": "60% of employees are willing to work extra hours for an extra day off, and 66% of respondents believe the 4-day week will increase productivity.", "citations": {"4caa1e09-fab5-4186-9a73-0e526d939de5_611648540": 1.0}}, {"text": "Friday is the most preferred extra day off for employers, and the 4-day workweek trend is increasingly adopted by countries and organizations.", "citations": {"4caa1e09-fab5-4186-9a73-0e526d939de5_611648540": 1.0}}, {"text": "A survey found that 33% of employees are willing to resign for a 4-day workweek job, and 61% prefer a 4-day workweek over a 5-day workweek.", "citations": {"62269ac0-ab8d-4c7c-874a-b9ab3a98a2d5_581400245": 1.0}}, {"text": "Half of respondents claim increased productivity with fewer days, and 10% are willing to cut pay for a 4-day workweek.", "citations": {"62269ac0-ab8d-4c7c-874a-b9ab3a98a2d5_581400245": 1.0}}, {"text": "Workers report less fatigue with a 4-day workweek, and companies see increased productivity and satisfaction with a 4-day workweek.", "citations": {"62269ac0-ab8d-4c7c-874a-b9ab3a98a2d5_581400245": 1.0}}, {"text": "10% of companies offer a 4-day workweek, and a proposal to reduce standard work hours to 32 hours has been introduced.", "citations": {"62269ac0-ab8d-4c7c-874a-b9ab3a98a2d5_581400245": 1.0}}, {"text": "Maryland lawmakers encourage employers to experiment with a 4-day workweek, and a 4-day workweek trial shows a positive impact on employee well-being.", "citations": {"62269ac0-ab8d-4c7c-874a-b9ab3a98a2d5_581400245": 1.0}}, {"text": "A UK trial found that 56 companies extended a 4-day workweek after the trial, and 18 companies made a 4-day workweek permanent.", "citations": {"9c856b2a-38cf-4c7b-9a4f-bcad5959432f_455712027": 1.0}}, {"text": "39% of employees were less stressed after the trial, and 40% of employees slept better after the trial.", "citations": {"9c856b2a-38cf-4c7b-9a4f-bcad5959432f_455712027": 1.0}}, {"text": "54% of employees had better work-life balance after the trial, and sick days decreased by two-thirds during the trial.", "citations": {"9c856b2a-38cf-4c7b-9a4f-bcad5959432f_455712027": 1.0}}, {"text": "Employee turnover decreased by 57% during the trial, and 2,900 employees participated in the 4-day workweek trial in the UK.", "citations": {"9c856b2a-38cf-4c7b-9a4f-bcad5959432f_455712027": 1.0}}, {"text": "The trial was launched in June 2022 in the UK, and productivity remained the same or improved in almost all cases.", "citations": {"9c856b2a-38cf-4c7b-9a4f-bcad5959432f_455712027": 1.0}}, {"text": "A separate trial in the UK found that 70 UK companies adopted a 4-day workweek with 100% pay, and 3,300 employees participated in the 6-month trial.", "citations": {"cf1102b4-5f90-45b4-9f65-661cd09ce910_1018928369": 1.0}}, {"text": "The trial used the 100:80:100 model, and the trial measures the impact on productivity and employee well-being.", "citations": {"cf1102b4-5f90-45b4-9f65-661cd09ce910_1018928369": 1.0}}, {"text": "Researchers analyzed stress, burnout, and job satisfaction, and government-backed trials are set to start in Spain later.", "citations": {"cf1102b4-5f90-45b4-9f65-661cd09ce910_1018928369": 1.0}}, {"text": "The trial aims to improve quality of life and competition, and output-oriented work gives companies a competitive advantage.", "citations": {"cf1102b4-5f90-45b4-9f65-661cd09ce910_1018928369": 1.0}}, {"text": "The trial is the world's largest attempt at the 4-day workweek model, and the trial also measures environmental and gender equality impact.", "citations": {"cf1102b4-5f90-45b4-9f65-661cd09ce910_1018928369": 1.0}}, {"text": "A global trial found that 91% of companies continued a 4-day workweek after the trial, and revenue increased by 35% during trial periods.", "citations": {"cf48d8ac-0386-40b7-9253-77191b543af4_295608395": 1.0}}, {"text": "Employee wellbeing and health improved significantly, and stress and burnout rates decreased among employees.", "citations": {"cf48d8ac-0386-40b7-9253-77191b543af4_295608395": 1.0}}, {"text": "Commuting time decreased by half an hour per week, and 4-Day Week Global has 91 companies and 3500 employees in trials.", "citations": {"cf48d8ac-0386-40b7-9253-77191b543af4_295608395": 1.0}}, {"text": "The average rating for the overall experience by companies was 8.5/10, and business productivity scored 7.5/10 during trials.", "citations": {"cf48d8ac-0386-40b7-9253-77191b543af4_295608395": 1.0}}, {"text": "Men took on more housework and childcare during trials, and women benefited more in burnout and life satisfaction.", "citations": {"cf48d8ac-0386-40b7-9253-77191b543af4_295608395": 1.0}}, {"text": "In the UAE, EAND introduced a 4-day workweek for flexibility, and the UAE adopted a 4-day workweek for government employees.", "citations": {"df20f50b-4a72-4aa4-b467-0a0a5511420e_349469158": 1.0}}, {"text": "Sharjah saw a 90% increase in job performance and happiness, and EAND's 4-day workweek improved employee well-being and productivity.", "citations": {"df20f50b-4a72-4aa4-b467-0a0a5511420e_349469158": 1.0}}, {"text": "The hybrid work system reduced energy consumption and carbon emissions, and the three-day weekend boosted work-life balance for employees.", "citations": {"df20f50b-4a72-4aa4-b467-0a0a5511420e_349469158": 1.0}}, {"text": "The reduced workweek supports the UAE's carbon neutrality goals, and EAND won awards for the best employer in the MENA region.", "citations": {"df20f50b-4a72-4aa4-b467-0a0a5511420e_349469158": 1.0}}, {"text": "The four-day workweek promotes sustainability and employee growth, and research by the World Economic Forum supports the benefits of a 4-day workweek.", "citations": {"df20f50b-4a72-4aa4-b467-0a0a5511420e_349469158": 1.0}}, {"text": "Companies that have implemented a 4-day workweek have seen improved work efficiency, with some maintaining 100% productivity while working 80% of the hours.", "citations": {"1d2aca84-d690-4e12-a07d-f87ff7a3b4ee_206156476": 1.0}}, {"text": "The quality of life for employees has also improved with reduced working hours, and meetings have been limited to 5 minutes in some companies to maximize productivity.", "citations": {"1d2aca84-d690-4e12-a07d-f87ff7a3b4ee_206156476": 1.0}}, {"text": "A 6-month trial involving 3300 workers and 70 companies demonstrated that productivity can be maintained with a 4-day workweek, with no wage cuts for workers.", "citations": {"1d2aca84-d690-4e12-a07d-f87ff7a3b4ee_206156476": 1.0}}, {"text": "In another trial, 90% of companies planned to continue with the shortened workweek, citing unaffected productivity and a 1.4% revenue increase.", "citations": {"35b580e6-ba02-4e03-8eb8-12cd488072cb_975295423": 1.0}}, {"text": "Revenue jumped 35% on average compared to previous years for companies that implemented a 4-day workweek, with employment increasing and absenteeism decreasing.", "citations": {"35b580e6-ba02-4e03-8eb8-12cd488072cb_975295423": 1.0}}, {"text": "Overall health and staff well-being also improved, with stress and fatigue rates decreasing, and sleep problems and burnout declining.", "citations": {"35b580e6-ba02-4e03-8eb8-12cd488072cb_975295423": 1.0}}, {"text": "A separate study found that productivity increased by 20% with a 4-day workweek, and employee leadership and confidence improved, with stress decreasing from 45% to 38%.", "citations": {"5ddd5bab-583c-4e82-946c-53d7e676ecb6_641577048": 1.0}}, {"text": "Perpetual Guardian, a company that implemented a 4-day workweek in 2018, saw a significant improvement in work-life balance, with scores increasing from 54% to 78%.", "citations": {"5ddd5bab-583c-4e82-946c-53d7e676ecb6_641577048": 1.0}}, {"text": "In Iceland, a trial involving 61 companies and 2900 employees found that most employees maintained or increased productivity, with staff turnover rate and absenteeism falling sharply after 6 months.", "citations": {"95484a6c-3484-4ebc-bcd9-0b7ef7fd3d89_98102531": 1.0}}, {"text": "Employers rated employee productivity 7.5 out of 10, with 46% of companies reporting unchanged productivity and 34% reporting a slight improvement.", "citations": {"95484a6c-3484-4ebc-bcd9-0b7ef7fd3d89_98102531": 1.0}}, {"text": "Revenue increased by", "citations": {}}], "references": ["5ddd5bab-583c-4e82-946c-53d7e676ecb6_641577048", "3fe3bd1b-0787-43f3-b514-b52b8fee3229_160601404", "3494412e-cfc6-4d35-a573-83dd99cb2ee2_162549217", "35b580e6-ba02-4e03-8eb8-12cd488072cb_975295423", "9c856b2a-38cf-4c7b-9a4f-bcad5959432f_455712027", "df20f50b-4a72-4aa4-b467-0a0a5511420e_349469158", "1d2aca84-d690-4e12-a07d-f87ff7a3b4ee_206156476", "1d46f039-99eb-4046-8a7f-5507144417d2_316669687", "cf1102b4-5f90-45b4-9f65-661cd09ce910_1018928369", "95484a6c-3484-4ebc-bcd9-0b7ef7fd3d89_98102531", "4caa1e09-fab5-4186-9a73-0e526d939de5_611648540", "05e65951-b854-47e7-9310-16cbbc9f2820_854826109", "62269ac0-ab8d-4c7c-874a-b9ab3a98a2d5_581400245", "092b9b4a-fc14-4205-98eb-1c1872d911e0_256602758", "cf48d8ac-0386-40b7-9253-77191b543af4_295608395"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "attract", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1035", "run_id": "attract-biological"}, "responses": [{"text": "Biohacking involves making lifestyle and nutrition changes to optimize health and longevity, such as diet tweaks and supplement use.", "citations": {"0f2ceda1-1145-419b-adad-243aa48471c2_868441574": 1.0, "7330daf3-723a-424d-a476-023fed1467cf_546361925": 0.5}}, {"text": "Biohacking aims to improve quality of life by lowering morbidity rate through methods like intermittent fasting, sleep, hydration, and physical training.", "citations": {"73dc4426-e3fb-40cb-8c2d-9236031101af_161823384": 1.0}}, {"text": "Popular biohacking methods include cold-water therapy, removing inflammatory foods, and using supplements like collagen, protein, and MCT oil, as well as sauna use.", "citations": {"7330daf3-723a-424d-a476-023fed1467cf_546361925": 1.0, "73dc4426-e3fb-40cb-8c2d-9236031101af_161823384": 0.5}}, {"text": "Biohacking can be dangerous if not done properly, and excessive vitamin intake can cause health problems, including vitamin poisoning and organ damage.", "citations": {"fa9e1059-0043-4662-b4ce-35da904e721c_680282951": 1.0, "6d35a18e-d551-45c0-b0fe-6d4ee90bb90c_90997551": 0.5, "ad409ecb-34f9-4ba2-b6ce-314d55e9131a_467474154": 0.25}}, {"text": "Individuals should consult healthcare professionals before starting any biohacking regimen to receive personalized and evidence-based advice.", "citations": {"0f2ceda1-1145-419b-adad-243aa48471c2_868441574": 1.0, "31c0c4d0-bc9c-4e41-8bda-6a8b62696abe_366873676": 0.5, "7cb20b77-c8c4-44e4-8af3-70eb9e7e435d_406268254": 0.25, "caa85e37-6f84-4cdd-91ed-88f88ac63b80_793273344": 0.125, "cad68b28-9613-4010-bbdb-3c946c035b06_616924221": 0.0625, "fa9e1059-0043-4662-b4ce-35da904e721c_680282951": 0.03125}}, {"text": "Genetic testing, including Whole Genome Sequencing, can inform personalized biohacking plans and identify biological needs and deficiencies.", "citations": {"fa9e1059-0043-4662-b4ce-35da904e721c_680282951": 1.0, "d2493154-ebec-4db4-a55b-1e75c8938bab_939734671": 0.5}}, {"text": "A healthy diet with fruits and vegetables supports overall health, reducing the need for supplements and risk of adverse effects.", "citations": {"fa9e1059-0043-4662-b4ce-35da904e721c_680282951": 1.0}}, {"text": "Blood tests and understanding physiology are crucial for effective biohacking, allowing healthcare professionals to develop personalized plans based on individual health risks and needs.", "citations": {"fa9e1059-0043-4662-b4ce-35da904e721c_680282951": 1.0}}, {"text": "Vitamin D supports bone health and muscle strength, but excess intake can cause mood disorders, heart issues, and pain, requiring cautious supplementation.", "citations": {"0353e479-e3af-48c7-be8b-ef2dfa196782_637979349": 1.0, "3e50f8a8-c574-4c91-afd4-dfc3d6640c76_860856874": 0.5, "3f8076e7-f98e-4344-a27e-5660a24b7d3e_113707781": 0.25}}, {"text": "Omega-3 fatty acids support heart and brain health, but high doses may increase bleeding risk, especially with anticoagulants, and require medical consultation.", "citations": {"b38e75ac-3864-4d21-8dfd-bcf3af8241af_995363149": 1.0, "6916d076-b990-4d32-a0dd-c79f0d5fcaf1_151397762": 0.5}}, {"text": "Probiotics can interact with vitamin D and omega-3 supplements, requiring careful management and consultation with a healthcare professional.", "citations": {"6916d076-b990-4d32-a0dd-c79f0d5fcaf1_151397762": 1.0}}, {"text": "Biohacking may not be suitable for everyone and should be done under healthcare professional guidance, especially for those without medical exemptions who should also get vaccinated.", "citations": {"b3fb5952-1e52-49d0-9f25-3810068355b4_713868175": 1.0}}, {"text": "Proper nutrition, training, and genetic testing are key to developing effective personalized biohacking plans that address health risk factors.", "citations": {"fa9e1059-0043-4662-b4ce-35da904e721c_680282951": 1.0, "d2493154-ebec-4db4-a55b-1e75c8938bab_939734671": 0.5}}], "references": ["6d35a18e-d551-45c0-b0fe-6d4ee90bb90c_90997551", "cad68b28-9613-4010-bbdb-3c946c035b06_616924221", "7cb20b77-c8c4-44e4-8af3-70eb9e7e435d_406268254", "0353e479-e3af-48c7-be8b-ef2dfa196782_637979349", "caa85e37-6f84-4cdd-91ed-88f88ac63b80_793273344", "b38e75ac-3864-4d21-8dfd-bcf3af8241af_995363149", "d2493154-ebec-4db4-a55b-1e75c8938bab_939734671", "6916d076-b990-4d32-a0dd-c79f0d5fcaf1_151397762", "fa9e1059-0043-4662-b4ce-35da904e721c_680282951", "ad409ecb-34f9-4ba2-b6ce-314d55e9131a_467474154", "b3fb5952-1e52-49d0-9f25-3810068355b4_713868175", "73dc4426-e3fb-40cb-8c2d-9236031101af_161823384", "0f2ceda1-1145-419b-adad-243aa48471c2_868441574", "7330daf3-723a-424d-a476-023fed1467cf_546361925", "31c0c4d0-bc9c-4e41-8bda-6a8b62696abe_366873676", "3e50f8a8-c574-4c91-afd4-dfc3d6640c76_860856874", "3f8076e7-f98e-4344-a27e-5660a24b7d3e_113707781"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "attract", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1036", "run_id": "attract-biological"}, "responses": [{"text": "Biohacking is a practice that involves making lifestyle tweaks to optimize health, and it includes techniques such as removing inflammatory foods from the diet, taking supplements, and using methods like cold-water therapy and saunas for health benefits.", "citations": {"7330daf3-723a-424d-a476-023fed1467cf_546361925": 1.0}}, {"text": "Biohacking methods can vary per person, and some popular methods include intermittent fasting, which is a pillar of biohacking, as well as hydration, physical training, and cognitive stimulation.", "citations": {"73dc4426-e3fb-40cb-8c2d-9236031101af_161823384": 1.0}}, {"text": "However, some biohacking methods, such as intermittent fasting and ketogenic diets, may not be suitable for everyone, particularly those with underlying health conditions, and can have negative effects on health, including worsening gastrointestinal diseases, disrupting thyroid function, and increasing the risk of heart disease.", "citations": {"0505932e-e096-4b88-be81-b8b525ebd27a_609224607": 1.0, "59db96f6-af77-40a2-a8a3-8eb38cf67c5a_195849844": 0.5}}, {"text": "It is essential to consult a doctor before starting any new diet or supplement regimen, especially for individuals with underlying health conditions, as certain diets and supplements can increase health problems in these individuals.", "citations": {"c8887e36-a9ff-4d32-825e-a06d12bc8d13_377918751": 1.0}}, {"text": "Medical supervision is necessary for safe vitamin use, and vitamins can harm without medical consultation.", "citations": {"6e179dd9-3108-4491-a68e-dd817317979e_418387380": 1.0}}, {"text": "Biohacking aims to activate epigenetic modifications and improve life quality, and involves methods such as nutrition, sleep, physical activity, and cognitive stimulation.", "citations": {"73dc4426-e3fb-40cb-8c2d-9236031101af_161823384": 1.0}}, {"text": "Some biohackers, like Bryan Johnson, spend significant amounts of money on biohacking methods, including medications, nutrition, and training, to slow aging.", "citations": {"8852fb6e-cdc1-4629-9451-cee0f352a1b5_422167984": 1.0}}, {"text": "However, not all biohacking methods are supported by reliable scientific data, and some supplements may have negative side effects, such as headaches and anxiety.", "citations": {"fa9e1059-0043-4662-b4ce-35da904e721c_680282951": 1.0}}, {"text": "A healthy diet is recommended as the first method for preventing diseases, rather than relying solely on supplements.", "citations": {"fa9e1059-0043-4662-b4ce-35da904e721c_680282951": 1.0}}, {"text": "Overall, while biohacking encompasses a wide range of methods aimed at self-optimization and improving health, the current state of clinical research on its efficacy and safety is limited, and more studies are needed to fully understand its effects on human health.", "citations": {"fa9e1059-0043-4662-b4ce-35da904e721c_680282951": 1.0}}, {"text": "Biohacking can be dangerous without medical supervision, and taking vitamins and supplements without a doctor's guidance can cause harm.", "citations": {"fa9e1059-0043-4662-b4ce-35da904e721c_680282951": 1.0}}, {"text": "It is crucial to evaluate the scientific evidence supporting biohacking methods and consult reliable sources to make informed decisions about health.", "citations": {"08effe59-1b22-4c30-b5f7-c4fa4b1d75f2_361777371": 1.0}}, {"text": "The combination of intermittent fasting, ketogenic diets, and excessive supplement intake can have severe long-term effects on overall health and well-being, particularly in individuals with underlying health conditions.", "citations": {"0505932e-e096-4b88-be81-b8b525ebd27a_609224607": 1.0, "06f2260b-b3bc-4beb-9e6e-4bc6faf93fc9_66499832": 0.5, "100ec187-499c-4e90-9c2e-c8bcbc89b665_333291549": 0.25, "3a8a84fc-3d0c-41fe-83b7-db251d602e82_850332671": 0.125, "3e50f8a8-c574-4c91-afd4-dfc3d6640c76_860856874": 0.0625, "4b796a45-90b3-4a88-935b-f87c9d37e5d4_576599882": 0.03125, "5e5bc85c-68f7-4bdc-943d-afe175b3dc6f_524890382": 0.015625, "c6015b4b-e8a6-41b5-8764-867abbc36828_169904043": 0.0078125, "c69f8c74-79f6-4859-ab8e-0bfcafea8566_235703057": 0.00390625, "c8887e36-a9ff-4d32-825e-a06d12bc8d13_377918751": 0.001953125, "e2e5695e-5664-4b13-9684-77a67f6d4397_381707295": 0.0009765625, "f1a99b61-8759-44e4-9af7-0b3f8398ab92_772080733": 0.00048828125}}, {"text": "Medical supervision is essential for ensuring the safety and efficacy of biohacking methods, especially for individuals with underlying health conditions.", "citations": {"73dc4426-e3fb-40cb-8c2d-9236031101af_161823384": 1.0}}, {"text": "Biohacking methods, including intermittent fasting and ketogenic diets, may not be supported by reliable scientific data from clinical research, and may have varying effects on individuals with underlying health conditions.", "citations": {"c8887e36-a9ff-4d32-825e-a06d12bc8d13_377918751": 1.0}}, {"text": "It is essential to consult a doctor before starting any biohacking method, particularly for individuals with underlying health conditions, to ensure safe and effective self-optimization.", "citations": {"0505932e-e096-4b88-be81-b8b525ebd27a_609224607": 1.0}}], "references": ["c69f8c74-79f6-4859-ab8e-0bfcafea8566_235703057", "8852fb6e-cdc1-4629-9451-cee0f352a1b5_422167984", "06f2260b-b3bc-4beb-9e6e-4bc6faf93fc9_66499832", "4b796a45-90b3-4a88-935b-f87c9d37e5d4_576599882", "c6015b4b-e8a6-41b5-8764-867abbc36828_169904043", "08effe59-1b22-4c30-b5f7-c4fa4b1d75f2_361777371", "6e179dd9-3108-4491-a68e-dd817317979e_418387380", "100ec187-499c-4e90-9c2e-c8bcbc89b665_333291549", "f1a99b61-8759-44e4-9af7-0b3f8398ab92_772080733", "5e5bc85c-68f7-4bdc-943d-afe175b3dc6f_524890382", "73dc4426-e3fb-40cb-8c2d-9236031101af_161823384", "0505932e-e096-4b88-be81-b8b525ebd27a_609224607", "3a8a84fc-3d0c-41fe-83b7-db251d602e82_850332671", "e2e5695e-5664-4b13-9684-77a67f6d4397_381707295", "59db96f6-af77-40a2-a8a3-8eb38cf67c5a_1958