{"metadata": {"team_id": "attract", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1037", "run_id": "attract-biological"}, "responses": [{"text": "The Turkish government's 2020 decision to reconvert Hagia Sophia into a mosque was widely criticized as a politically motivated move by President Erdogan.", "citations": {"36db8615-aa07-4391-a3f5-098dba27f295_1069312408": 1.0}}, {"text": "UNESCO criticized the reconversion of Hagia Sophia to a mosque as biased and political.", "citations": {"3886289d-abc9-433e-9ed3-f3bd8c9a9f7d_513279190": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Greek Orthodox Church and Prime Minister criticized the conversion, calling it offensive to history.", "citations": {"6520a8e4-2d97-4c78-8f05-4f048241b9f6_105665812": 1.0}}, {"text": "The US, Greece, and Russia criticized Turkey's decision to convert Hagia Sophia into a mosque, citing concerns over its cultural and historical significance.", "citations": {"a8d17c9c-d219-4c0f-b2b9-f79c754a6d8c_960510274": 1.0}}, {"text": "Pope Francis and the Ecumenical Patriarch criticized the reconversion of Hagia Sophia into a mosque.", "citations": {"a8d17c9c-d219-4c0f-b2b9-f79c754a6d8c_960510274": 1.0}}, {"text": "Erdogan's conversion of Hagia Sophia was seen as a move to strengthen his conservative base and distract from economic issues.", "citations": {"d766c719-43c0-4423-80e6-89c1f9dc9d52_954300905": 1.0}}, {"text": "The international community criticized Turkey's reconversion of Hagia Sophia as an internal affair.", "citations": {"a8d17c9c-d219-4c0f-b2b9-f79c754a6d8c_960510274": 1.0}}, {"text": "Turkey dismissed UNESCO's criticism as biased, with Erdogan calling the decision democratic.", "citations": {"36db8615-aa07-4391-a3f5-098dba27f295_1069312408": 1.0}}, {"text": "The reconversion of Hagia Sophia to a mosque was praised by Muslims, but criticized by countries seeking to protect Byzantine monuments.", "citations": {"d766c719-43c0-4423-80e6-89c1f9dc9d52_954300905": 1.0}}, {"text": "Hagia Sophia's mosaics of Jesus and Mary were covered and entrance fees reintroduced after the reconversion.", "citations": {"76e3d61c-e991-43a2-8ebe-637114089506_291378229": 1.0}}, {"text": "A Turkish court ruled the 1934 conversion of Hagia Sophia into a museum was illegal, allowing Erdogan to decree it a mosque.", "citations": {"a8d17c9c-d219-4c0f-b2b9-f79c754a6d8c_960510274": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Greek Orthodox Church and other Orthodox Christian institutions worldwide condemned the decision to convert Hagia Sophia into a mosque.", "citations": {"76e3d61c-e991-43a2-8ebe-637114089506_291378229": 1.0}}, {"text": "As a tour guide in Istanbul, be prepared to address questions about the Hagia Sophia's conversion in a respectful and informative manner.", "citations": {"97d76ff6-1c05-45d5-ba89-88ccc0122e21_491069692": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tour guides use earphones and separate entrances for worshippers and tourists to minimize disruptions.", "citations": {"97d76ff6-1c05-45d5-ba89-88ccc0122e21_491069692": 1.0}}, {"text": "The entrance fee for foreign tourists was reintroduced in 2024 to preserve cultural assets and monuments.", "citations": {"97d76ff6-1c05-45d5-ba89-88ccc0122e21_491069692": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tour guides can promote a positive experience for Hagia Sophia visitors by providing respectful and informative guidance.", "citations": {"f81149b2-9efa-411c-b8fa-ed1ba6062f6f_619383984": 1.0}}], "references": ["6520a8e4-2d97-4c78-8f05-4f048241b9f6_105665812", "a8d17c9c-d219-4c0f-b2b9-f79c754a6d8c_960510274", "d766c719-43c0-4423-80e6-89c1f9dc9d52_954300905", "f81149b2-9efa-411c-b8fa-ed1ba6062f6f_619383984", "36db8615-aa07-4391-a3f5-098dba27f295_1069312408", "76e3d61c-e991-43a2-8ebe-637114089506_291378229", "3886289d-abc9-433e-9ed3-f3bd8c9a9f7d_513279190", "97d76ff6-1c05-45d5-ba89-88ccc0122e21_491069692"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "attract", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1038", "run_id": "attract-biological"}, "responses": [{"text": "The 2020 conversion of Hagia Sophia into a mosque sparked controversy and criticism from countries like Greece, the US, Russia, and UNESCO.", "citations": {"a8d17c9c-d219-4c0f-b2b9-f79c754a6d8c_960510274": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Turkish court's decision to overturn the 1934 ministerial decision converting Hagia Sophia into a museum marked a major change in Istanbul's history, challenged by President Erdogan.", "citations": {"36db8615-aa07-4391-a3f5-098dba27f295_1069312408": 1.0}}, {"text": "Hagia Sophia now charges foreign tourists \u20ac25 to enter, while Turkish citizens can enter for free for worship.", "citations": {"5f313598-c9ac-40a3-8bae-106d6564ae87_210914181": 1.0}}, {"text": "The entrance fee for foreign tourists is expected to significantly impact Istanbul's tourism industry, leading to higher prices due to the weak lira.", "citations": {"6f38cb1a-e23d-4640-b32d-e60c213671a8_857153029": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tour guides must adapt to new rules, including using earphones for guided tours outside the mosque.", "citations": {"97d76ff6-1c05-45d5-ba89-88ccc0122e21_491069692": 1.0}}, {"text": "The new rules include separate entrances and information in 16 languages to improve coexistence between visitors and worshippers at Hagia Sophia.", "citations": {"f81149b2-9efa-411c-b8fa-ed1ba6062f6f_619383984": 1.0}}, {"text": "The conversion of Hagia Sophia into a mosque has caused damage, including fragments falling from the dome and harm to the Imperial Gate and marble floors.", "citations": {"9ba1561a-fc64-4cc3-b0ee-218d2b7a3e8d_609947018": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Turkish government has begun restoration work on Hagia Sophia.", "citations": {"9ba1561a-fc64-4cc3-b0ee-218d2b7a3e8d_609947018": 1.0}}, {"text": "Hagia Sophia's visitor management policy regulates density and improves the visitor experience.", "citations": {"f81149b2-9efa-411c-b8fa-