ia an app and regain some museum function.", "citations": {"f81149b2-9efa-411c-b8fa-ed1ba6062f6f_619383984": 1.0}}, {"text": "The conversion of Hagia Sophia into a mosque has sparked international controversy, with criticism from UNESCO, Greece, the US, and others.", "citations": {"a8d17c9c-d219-4c0f-b2b9-f79c754a6d8c_960510274": 1.0}}, {"text": "Erdogan's decision to convert Hagia Sophia was criticized as a political move to gain support and maintain power amidst economic issues.", "citations": {"dc7d1e14-9026-4142-8352-b56898791c5a_838665307": 1.0}}, {"text": "The conversion of Hagia Sophia has been praised by Muslims as a restoration of its historical and cultural significance.", "citations": {"d766c719-43c0-4423-80e6-89c1f9dc9d52_954300905": 1.0}}, {"text": "The conversion has been criticized for potentially restricting access and limiting other faiths' influence through a reimposed entrance fee.", "citations": {"3886289d-abc9-433e-9ed3-f3bd8c9a9f7d_513279190": 1.0}}, {"text": "The international community has criticized the conversion decision, citing its potential to undermine the site's cultural and historical significance.", "citations": {"97d76ff6-1c05-45d5-ba89-88ccc0122e21_491069692": 1.0}}, {"text": "The UNESCO Foundation criticized the conversion decision, citing a lack of consultation and potential harm to the site's cultural heritage.", "citations": {"97d76ff6-1c05-45d5-ba89-88ccc0122e21_491069692": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Greek Orthodox Church has condemned Hagia Sophia's conversion, citing its historical significance.", "citations": {"97d76ff6-1c05-45d5-ba89-88ccc0122e21_491069692": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Turkish Tourism Minister aims to balance the site's religious and cultural significance for worshippers and tourists.", "citations": {"97d76ff6-1c05-45d5-ba89-88ccc0122e21_491069692": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tourist entry fees were abolished and then reinstated in 2024, amid ongoing controversy over the site.", "citations": {"97d76ff6-1c05-45d5-ba89-88ccc0122e2