{"metadata": {"team_id": "attract", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1039", "run_id": "attract-biological"}, "responses": [{"text": "The Turkish President Erdogan's 2020 decision to reconvert the Hagia Sophia into a mosque has sparked global criticism and debate.", "citations": {"36db8615-aa07-4391-a3f5-098dba27f295_1069312408": 1.0}}, {"text": "The decision has been criticized for prioritizing the Islamic past over other faiths.", "citations": {"76e3d61c-e991-43a2-8ebe-637114089506_291378229": 1.0}}, {"text": "Figurative artwork, including mosaics of Jesus and Mary, are covered in Hagia Sophia as they are forbidden in Islamic prayer sites.", "citations": {"76e3d61c-e991-43a2-8ebe-637114089506_291378229": 1.0}}, {"text": "Turkey has reintroduced an entrance fee for Hagia Sophia and faced criticism over its caretaking of the site.", "citations": {"76e3d61c-e991-43a2-8ebe-637114089506_291378229": 1.0}}, {"text": "The conversion of Hagia Sophia into a mosque has sparked international criticism from countries including Greece and the US.", "citations": {"76e3d61c-e991-43a2-8ebe-637114089506_291378229": 1.0}}, {"text": "UNESCO criticized the decision, citing a lack of consultation and concern for the site's cultural heritage.", "citations": {"97d76ff6-1c05-45d5-ba89-88ccc0122e21_491069692": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Pope and Orthodox Patriarch have expressed disapproval over Hagia Sophia's conversion into a mosque.", "citations": {"a8d17c9c-d219-4c0f-b2b9-f79c754a6d8c_960510274": 1.0}}, {"text": "Erdogan's decision to convert Hagia Sophia into a mosque is seen as a political move to distract from economic issues and promote Islamization.", "citations": {"dc7d1e14-9026-4142-8352-b56898791c5a_838665307": 1.0}}, {"text": "Erdogan's motivation was driven by a desire to reconnect with the Ottoman past and promote Islamic heritage.", "citations": {"aca9fced-3a95-40a8-82a7-3da41f775387_904412472": 1.0}}, {"text": "The American Council has called for Christian worship in Hagia Sophia, threatening a European Court of Human Rights lawsuit if denied.", "citations": {"78791118-f9c5-4ecd-b7a2-e57dcecfb197_751571096": 1.0}}, {"text": "Erdogan's decision to convert Hagia Sophia to a mosque aimed to appease conservative Anatolia voters.", "citations": {"78791118-f9c5-4ecd-b7a2-e57dcecfb197_751571096": 1.0}}, {"text": "Erdogan's actions undermined Turkey's secular status, aiming to apply Islamic laws.", "citations": {"dc7d1e14-9026-4142-8352-b56898791c5a_838665307": 1.0}}], "references": ["97d76ff6-1c05-45d5-ba89-88ccc0122e21_491069692", "aca9fced-3a95-40a8-82a7-3da41f775387_904412472", "78791118-f9c5-4ecd-b7a2-e57dcecfb197_751571096", "dc7d1e14-9026-4142-8352-b56898791c5a_838665307", "a8d17c9c-d219-4c0f-b2b9-f79c754a6d8c_960510274", "76e3d61c-e991-43a2-8ebe-637114089506_291378229", "36db8615-aa07-4391-a3f5-098dba27f295_1069312408"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "attract", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1040", "run_id": "attract-biological"}, "responses": [{"text": "The 2020 conversion of Hagia Sophia into a mosque has been highly controversial.", "citations": {"36db8615-aa07-4391-a3f5-098dba27f295_1069312408": 1.0}}, {"text": "Turkish President Erdogan made the decision, which has been seen as a move to appeal to his conservative base and promote a neo-Ottoman ideology.", "citations": {"78791118-f9c5-4ecd-b7a2-e57dcecfb197_751571096": 1.0}}, {"text": "The conversion has been criticized by the Greek Orthodox Church, UNESCO, and other organizations due to concerns over cultural heritage and religious freedom.", "citations": {"76e3d61c-e991-43a2-8ebe-637114089506_291378229": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Turkish government defended its decision as a matter of national sovereignty, with the site remaining open to visitors.", "citations": {"97d76ff6-1c05-45d5-ba89-88ccc0122e21_491069692": 1.0}}, {"text": "The conversion has sparked concerns over preserving the site's historic mosaics and artwork, which are forbidden in mosques.", "citations": {"76e3d61c-e991-43a2-8ebe-637114089506_291378229": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Turkish government has introduced measures, including separate entrances and earphones, to manage the site.", "citations": {"97d76ff6-1c05-45d5-ba89-88ccc0122e21_491069692": 1.0}}, {"text": "The reconversion of Hagia Sophia into a mosque has been popular among some Turks, attracting over 21 million visitors.", "citations": {"9ba1561a-fc64-4cc3-b0ee-218d2b7a3e8d_609947018": 1.0}}, {"text": "The conversion has raised concerns about democracy and the rule of law in Turkey, key EU membership criteria.", "citations": {"a4541930-bdd4-4c2c-aecc-f835cb26d5a7_175833066": 1.0}}, {"text": "The EU has imposed sanctions on Turkey over its democratic and human rights record.", "citations": {"a4541930-bdd4-4c2c-aecc-f835cb26d5a7_175833066": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Pope and the Orthodox Patriarch have criticized Turkey's decision to convert Hagia Sophia.", "citations": {"a8d17c9c-d219-4c0f-b2b9-f79c754a6d8c_960510274": 1.0}}, {"text": "Hagia Sophia's conversion is seen as a symbol of Erdogan's push for Islamic laws and a distraction from Turkey's economic problems.", "citations": {"dc7d1e14-9026-4142-8352-b56898791c5a_838665307": 1.0}}, {"text": "The conversion has significant implications for Turkey's secularism, international relations, and EU accession bid.", "citations": {"dc7d1e14-9026-4142-8352-b56898791c5a_838665307": 1.0}}, {"text": "The EU wants closer ties with Turkey, but only if it respects democracy and human rights.", "citations": {"b86b7294-f878-4d6d-8625-a4e352b03537_323238589": 1.0}}, {"text": "Hagia Sophia's conversion has sparked debate over cultural heritage and religious beliefs.", "citations": {"6520a8e4-2d97-4c78-8f05-4f048241b9f6_105665812": 1.0}}, {"text": "Turkey has introduced an entrance fee for foreign tourists, sparking controversy.", "citations": {"7c91a665-2672-4d9b-8eae-3ec3168be312_904357446": 1.0}}, {"text": "The fee aims to preserve cultural assets, but critics see it as a barrier to access for non-affiliated visitors.", "citations": {"3886289d-abc9-433e-9ed3-f3bd8c9a9f7d_513279190": 1.0}}, {"text": "The conversion of Hagia Sophia may deter visitors from other faiths or backgrounds, impacting tourism.", "citations": {"3886289d-abc9-433e-9ed3-f3bd8c9a9f7d_513279190": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Turkish government has implemented measures to regulate visitor access, including separate entrances for worshippers and tourists.", "citations": {"97d76ff6-1c05-45d5-ba89-88ccc0122e21_491069692": 1.0}}, {"text": "The site's restoration work is underway.", "citations": {"9ba1561a-fc64-4cc3-b0ee-218d2b7a3e8d_609947018": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Turkish government introduced a visitor management plan to improve visit quality and safety.", "citations": {"9ba1561a-fc64-4cc3-b0ee-218d2b7a3e8d_609947018": 1.0}}, {"text": "The plan includes regulating visitor density and providing information in 16 languages through an app.", "citations": {"f81149b2-9efa-411c-b8fa-ed1ba6062f6f_619383984": 1.0}}, {"text": "The conversion of Hagia Sophia has significant implications for Turkish citizens, especially minority religious groups.", "citations": {"78791118-f9c5-4ecd-b7a2-e57dcecfb197_751571096": 1.0}}, {"text": "Erdogan's decision aims to promote Islamic heritage and divert attention from economic issues.", "citations": {"dc7d1e14-9026-4142-8352-b56898791c5a_838665307": 1.0}}, {"text": "The conversion has sparked concerns about preserving cultural heritage and the site's UNESCO World Heritage Site status.", "citations": {"97d76ff6-1c05-45d5-ba89-88ccc0122e21_491069692": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Turkish government aims to make historical monuments available and promote cultural heritage and education.", "citations": {"9dd219f6-2d94-4cd6-a905-bbd3c87a161b_427727559": 1.0}}, {"text": "The conversion of Hagia Sophia has been criticized for prioritizing Islamic heritage over other cultural layers.", "citations": {"76e3d61c-e991-43a2-8ebe-637114089506_291378229": 1.0}}, {"text": "The decision challenges Turkey's secularism, a founding principle established by Ataturk.", "citations": {"6cc81e0c-77b8-45c0-a4a5-f73053c6a66b_384253108": 1.0}}, {"text": "The conversion of Hagia Sophia may marginalize Turkish citizens from minority religious backgrounds.", "citations": {"78791118-f9c5-4ecd-b7a2-e57dcecfb197_751571096": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Turkish government has introduced measures in Istanbul to promote social cohesion among Roma people, including coordination centers and social housing projects.", "citations": {"55c17ed5-a5df-445e-ba6d-dac77c0cd678_960737863": 1.0}}, {"text": "The government has announced an action plan to improve Roma living conditions, including free vocational training.", "citations": {"55c17ed5-a5df-445e-ba6d-dac77c0cd678_960737863": 1.0}}, {"text": "Hagia Sophia's conversion has sparked debate about Turkey's secularism and interna