{"metadata": {"team_id": "attract", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1087", "run_id": "attract-biological"}, "responses": [{"text": "The India-Russia relationship has evolved under Modi and Putin, focusing on defense cooperation.", "citations": {"18a87794-ba47-4d33-a1b5-bf97307dd44b_224507163": 1.0}}, {"text": "India and Russia have a Special and Privileged Strategic Partnership, with Russia as India's largest military equipment supplier.", "citations": {"18a87794-ba47-4d33-a1b5-bf97307dd44b_224507163": 1.0}}, {"text": "Russia's growing alignment with China raises concerns for India as it balances relations with both nations.", "citations": {"18a87794-ba47-4d33-a1b5-bf97307dd44b_224507163": 1.0}}, {"text": "India is balancing its Western ties and strategic partnership with Russia to counter a rising China.", "citations": {"18a87794-ba47-4d33-a1b5-bf97307dd44b_224507163": 1.0}}, {"text": "The US has threatened India with sanctions over Russian arms purchases.", "citations": {"18a87794-ba47-4d33-a1b5-bf97307dd44b_224507163": 1.0}}, {"text": "India continues to buy military equipment from Russia, including the S-400 missile system.", "citations": {"18a87794-ba47-4d33-a1b5-bf97307dd44b_224507163": 1.0}}, {"text": "India signed a $5.43 billion contract for S-400 systems with Russia on October 5, 2018.", "citations": {"04bd8ba0-4fc2-4dd7-a544-9e34b4c0e090_643794131": 1.0}}, {"text": "The contract includes five S-400 regimental sets for India, significantly enhancing its air defense.", "citations": {"04bd8ba0-4fc2-4dd7-a544-9e34b4c0e090_643794131": 1.0}}, {"text": "India and Russia have agreed to jointly produce Russian weapons in India, worth $14 billion.", "citations": {"7eafb352-b81a-4ae4-9ba4-5bb8f62e5004_446141041": 1.0}}, {"text": "India and Russia have signed a contract to produce 600,000 Kalashnikov AK-203 rifles in India.", "citations": {"444b7693-fde3-4855-b61b-664ca618ee75_17439284": 1.0}}, {"text": "The AK-203 rifle production will replace the Indian Army's outdated INSAS and AK-47 rifles.", "citations": {"ab699ba2-ae28-4b5d-8ed5-f8734322b34e_230228015": 1.0}}, {"text": "India's rivalry with China has impacted its relationship with Russia, as both seek to counterbalance China's influence.", "citations": {"7eafb352-b81a-4ae4-9ba4-5bb8f62e5004_446141041": 1.0}}, {"text": "The SCO provides a platform for India and Russia to discuss regional security and counter-terrorism.", "citations": {"34b0ff67-5a89-4e84-9fd8-70879a4b95fe_466360854": 1.0}}, {"text": "Russia's technology transfer has enabled India to locally produce armor-piercing Mango tank ammunition.", "citations": {"70a0e55b-dade-4d81-9884-0b74e6fa4d20_1053785220": 1.0}}, {"text": "Brahmos Aerospace, a Russia-India joint venture, produces hypersonic cruise missiles like the BrahMos, with a 400-kilometer range.", "citations": {"5b579959-3276-480a-b5eb-8890578a0031_63342284": 1.0}}, {"text": "A $30 billion bilateral trade goal by 2025 has been set, with a focus on technology transfer and local military equipment production.", "citations": {"d67e54cc-62da-447c-ae1b-48796fdb0f91_766762719": 1.0}}, {"text": "The US may impose CAATSA sanctions on India for buying Russian military equipment, despite their strategic partnership.", "citations": {"5ff37da5-ece0-401a-b369-aa2bc1a1928d_484996419": 1.0}}, {"text": "US senators have urged President Biden to drop sanctions on India's S-400 purchase due to the partnership's strategic importance.", "citations": {"45d5a8a2-0ac9-49cf-880a-347299c9f78a_617089955": 1.0}}, {"text": "India has not joined Western sanctions against Russia and has abstained from key UN votes on Ukraine.", "citations": {"7acde05f-c404-4c73-957c-462fd22b941a_238175874": 1.0}}, {"text": "India relies on Russia for various defense technologies and has doubled its investment in their joint defense research.", "citations": {"7acde05f-c404-4c73-957c-462fd22b941a_238175874": 1.0}}, {"text": "Russia's military cooperation with India remains unaffected by Western sanctions.", "citations": {"7e16e2a5-2626-410c-a485-8976d57fd736_137627831": 1.0}}, {"text": "US sanctions have led to the use of national currencies in Russia-India military contracts, replacing the dollar.", "citations": {"7eafb352-b81a-4ae4-9ba4-5bb8f62e5004_446141041": 1.0}}], "references": ["7e16e2a5-2626-410c-a485-8976d57fd736_137627831", "5b579959-3276-480a-b5eb-8890578a0031_63342284", "7eafb352-b81a-4ae4-9ba4-5bb8f62e5004_446141041", "d67e54cc-62da-447c-ae1b-48796fdb0f91_766762719", "18a87794-ba47-4d33-a1b5-bf97307dd44b_224507163", "5ff37da5-ece0-401a-b369-aa2bc1a1928d_484996419", "34b0ff67-5a89-4e84-9fd8-70879a4b95fe_466360854", "70a0e55b-dade-4d81-9884-0b74e6fa4d20_1053785220", "45d5a8a2-0ac9-49cf-880a-347299c9f78a_617089955", "444b7693-fde3-4855-b61b-664ca618ee75_17439284", "7acde05f-c404-4c73-957c-462fd22b941a_238175874", "04bd8ba0-4fc2-4dd7-a544-9e34b4c0e090_643794131", "ab699ba2-ae28-4b5d-8ed5-f8734322b34e_230228015"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "attract", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1088", "run_id": "attract-biological"}, "responses": [{"text": "The India-Russia relationship has evolved significantly under Prime Minister Modi and President Putin, with a focus on strengthening strategic partnerships and cooperation in various areas, including defense, trade, and energy.", "citations": {"9796598e-e5cd-4b19-8665-f50cecfea01d_371231430": 1.0}}, {"text": "The two countries have signed 28 cooperation agreements, including a 10-year military cooperation agreement, which outlines the specific milestones and deliverables for their military cooperation.", "citations": {"5e5bc85c-68f7-4bdc-943d-afe175b3dc6f_946376914": 1.0}}, {"text": "India and Russia have a long-standing cooperation in the defense sector, with Russia being one of India's largest suppliers of military equipment.", "citations": {"7eafb352-b81a-4ae4-9ba4-5bb8f62e5004_446141041": 1.0}}, {"text": "The partnership between India and Russia has been driven by their mutual interest in countering China's rise, with Russia providing military aid to India during the Indo-Chinese conflict.", "citations": {"be74de86-73ec-47a2-96c6-4ce8554abeea_61414336": 1.0}}, {"text": "India's arsenal is mostly Soviet or Russian-made, and the country sees China's rise as the biggest threat in its neighborhood.", "citations": {"d86b51c7-48e9-4704-8e20-dc18188ddba7_467282408": 1.0}}, {"text": "The India-Russia partnership has been further strengthened by their cooperation in the defense sector, with India and Russia signing a 10-year military cooperation agreement.", "citations": {"d67e54cc-62da-447c-ae1b-48796fdb0f91_766762719": 1.0}}, {"text": "The agreement includes the joint development and production of weapons and equipment, with a focus on air defense systems, such as the S-400.", "citations": {"444b7693-fde3-4855-b61b-664ca618ee75_17439284": 1.0, "5e5bc85c-68f7-4bdc-943d-afe175b3dc6f_946376914": 0.5}}, {"text": "The India-Russia relationship has been affected by India's rivalry with China, with India seeking to balance its Russia-India relations with its concerns over China.", "citations": {"bcf52928-88ba-48e9-b06b-3cf4b746206c_116105857": 1.0}}, {"text": "Despite this, Russia respects India's policy of strategic autonomy, allowing India to maintain its independence in its diplomatic relations.", "citations": {"9796598e-e5cd-4b19-8665-f50cecfea01d_371231430": 1.0}}, {"text": "The US has attempted to influence India's relationship with Russia, including through the imposition of CAATSA sanctions, but India has maintained its commitment to its bilateral relationship with Russia.", "citations": {"21ed01ca-807c-44ff-a30d-2f665ef65e50_383211104": 1.0}}, {"text": "The India-Russia partnership has significant implications for regional security in South and Central Asia, with the potential to counterbalance China's growing influence in the region and promote strategic stability.", "citations": {"9536aa48-cd0a-4b0b-a5e7-61de61666f18_608899839": 1.0}}, {"text": "The partnership has also led to cooperation on issues such as counter-terrorism and non-proliferation, with India and Russia discussing the need to combat radicalization and terrorism in the region.", "citations": {"14dd83c6-319f-4e6b-9150-c5bc6365b253_422699259": 1.0}}, {"text": "The India-Russia partnership has also been driven by economic interests, with the two countries aiming to reach $30 billion in bilateral trade by 2025 and cooperating on energy projects, including the development of the International North South Transport Corridor (INSTC).", "citations": {"792e3539-8d3e-404d-925f-2d2e14af8105_958547503": 1.0}}, {"text": "Overall, the India-Russia partnership has the potential to promote regional security and stability in South and Central Asia, while also advancing India's strategic interests and countering China's growing influence in the region.", "citations": {"d67e54cc-62da-447c-ae1b-48796fdb0f91_766762719": 1.0}}, {"text": "The partnership between India and Russia is expected to continue, with plans to reach $30 billion in bilateral trade by 2025, and the extension of the military-technical cooperation agreement until 2031.", "citations": {"d67e54cc-62da-447c-ae1b-48796fdb0f91_766762719": 1.0}}, {"text": "The India-Russia relationship has been described as a \"special and privileged strategic partnership\" with the two countries signing 28 cooperation agreements.", "citations": {"5e5bc85c-68f7-4bdc-943d-afe175b3dc6f_946376914": 1.0}}, {"text": "The India-Russia trade has exceeded $50 billion, with Russia being India's biggest oil supplier.", "citations": {"9796598e-e5cd-4b19-8665-f50cecfea01d_371231430": 1.0}}, {"text": "India has resisted US pressure to condemn Russia over Ukraine, and has played a key role in G20 negotiations on Ukraine.", "citations": {"9796598e-e5cd-4b19-8665-f50cecfea01d_371231430": 1.0}}, {"text": "Russia respects India's strategic autonomy policy, and India is a member of the Quad and supports the Indo-Pacific concept.", "citations": {"9796598e-e5cd-4b19-8665-f50cecfea01d_371231430": 1.0}}, {"text": "However, Russia has reservations about the Quad and the Indo-Pacific concept, and has predicted a long transition to global multipolarity.", "citations": {"9796598e-e5cd-4b19-8665-f50cecfea01d_371231430": 1.0, "97daf82f-aea0-42bb-9be4-ded4e00e11c8_1315789": 0.5}}, {"text": "The India-Russia partnership may counter China's rise in the Indo-Pacific, and India can counter China with the support of the Quad nations.", "citations": {"e0e9e763-4a35-4495-a973-3728d90bca4d_688458791": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Quad aims to prevent a Ukraine-like situation in the Indo-Pacific, and the US and India relationship may be affected by the Ukraine crisis.", "citations": {"e25f5d65-cb99-4a14-99ae-94b1ec53b55a_528957036": 1.0}}, {"text": "India's position on Russia differs from other Quad members, and India has abstained from voting against Russia in the UN.", "citations": {"e25f5d65-cb99-4a14-99ae-94b1ec53b55a_528957036": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Quad's move to create an \"Asia version of NATO\" is challenging, and India's cooperation is crucial for the Quad's success.", "citations": {"e25f5d65-cb99-4a14-99ae-94b1ec53b55a_528957036": 1.0}}, {"text": "The India-Russia partnership has the potential to impact the regional dynamics of the Indo-Pacific, particularly in relation to the Quad and ASEAN.", "citations": {"18de596d-601d-4044-9f4c-7c5cff4aae60_194889417": 1.0, "2927bf36-4d7f-45bc-849a-ee751f4594b2_799837689": 0.5, "2e47f6de-c623-4fa5-afb0-4499b919cd32_122940881": 0.25, "5e5bc85c-68f7-4bdc-943d-afe175b3dc6f_946376914": 0.125, "7cc7f997-dea4-4d74-9fe1-bbe50d61fa36_811871792": 0.0625, "9796598e-e5cd-4b19-8665-f50cecfea01d_371231430": 0.03125, "97daf82f-aea0-42bb-9be4-ded4e00e11c8_1315789": 0.015625, "b202839b-57a1-4572-8d4c-98b58f4d368a_322378829": 0.0078125, "bfe1ae52-7587-4bc4-a85c-692dbebacda0_354766711": 0.00390625, "e0e9e763-4a35-4495-a973-3728d90bca4d_688458791": 0.001953125, "e25f5d65-cb99-4a14-99ae-94b1ec53b55a_528957036": 0.0009765625, "ec46af38-2b9f-47aa-a181-c7bf634854e8_196930128": 0.00048828125}}, {"text": "The Quad aims to build a secure and prosperous Indo-Pacific region, and ASEAN has expressed support for the Quad's objectives.", "citations": {"bfe1ae52-7587-4bc4-a85c-692dbebacda0_354766711": 1.0}}, {"text": "The India-Russia partnership may play a crucial role in shaping the regional dynamics of the Indo-Pacific, and its impact will depend on various factors, including the actions of other countries and organizations in the region.", "citations": {"18de596d-601d-4044-9f4c-7c5cff4aae60_194889417": 1.0, "2927bf36-4d7f-45bc-849a-ee751f4594b2_799837689": 0.5, "2e47f6de-c623-4fa5-afb0-4499b919cd32_122940881": 0.25, "5e5bc85c-68f7-4bdc-943d-afe175b3dc6f_946376914": 0.125, "7cc7f997-dea4-4d74-9fe1-bbe50d61fa36_811871792": 0.0625, "9796598e-e5cd-4b19-8665-f50cecfea01d_371231430": 0.03125, "97daf82f-aea0-42bb-9be4-ded4e00e11c8_1315789": 0.015625, "b202